  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Ingwalo ezimbili, olukaLukha lolweMisebenzi, zingwalo ezimbili zomsebenzi munye (bona Imisebenzi ukuze uthole isingeniso esijulileyo seMisebenzi). Bonke bakhuluma udaba lwendlela uNkulunkulu anxusa ngayo abantu bako-Israyeli lezinye izizwe ukuthi zilandele uJesu. Encwadini yakuqala udaba lumayelana lokuya eJerusalema lapho okulensika yamaJuda. Kweyesibili, uhambo lokusuka eJerusalema kuyiwa kwamanye amazwe, iphetha ngoPhawuli etshumayela ngombuso weNkosi eRoma, isigodlo sombuso.</para>
  <para style="ip">ULukha uchasisa imbali yakhe <char style="qt">komkhulu ohloniphekayo uTheyofelasi,</char> ongabe wayeyisikhulu seRoma. Amabhuku akhe agcwele ngolwazi olwalugcinwe nguLukha olugoqela incwadi, inkulumo, ingoma, amatikiti okuhambisa, incwadi zokuhambisa, incwadi zokuthonisiswa kwamacala kanye lembali. Umlandu kaLukha ngowokutshengisa ukugcwaliseka kwecebo likaNkulunkulu lokuletha ukukhanya kwakhe emhlabeni kusetshenziswa abantu bako-Israyeli. Abalandeli bakaJesu bokuqala bavuma lokhu kubizwa bahamba betshumayeza ukunqoba kukaJesu enqoba isono lokufa emazweni wonke.</para>
  <para style="ip">Encwadini yakhe yakuqala uLukha ulandisa ngendaba kaJesu yena uyifake yaba yizahluko ezintathu.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Eyokuqala, uJesu utshumayela eseGalile, indawo esenyakatho kwe-Israyeli.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Okulandelayo, uthatha uhambo olude lokuya eJerusalema lapho wamukela abantu endleleni iNkosi ebusa ngayo njalo ubabuza ngendlela abazwisisa ngayo umbuso.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Okwesithathu, uLukha ulandisa ngendlela uJesu anikela ngayo impilo yakhe eJerusalema lokuvuka kwakhe kwabafileyo ukuze kubonakaliswe ukuthi uyiNkosi yako-Israyeli njalo eyiNkosi yeqiniso umhlaba wonke.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="LUK 1"/>
  <para style="s1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 1:1"/>Banengi asebazimisela ukuqoqa umlando wezinto esezigcwalisekile phakathi kwethu, <verse eid="LUK 1:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 1:2"/>njengokwedluliselwa kwazo kithi yilabo ababekhona ekuqaleni bengabafakazi lezinceku zelizwi. <verse eid="LUK 1:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 1:3"/>Ngakho-ke, njengoba mina ngokwami sengichwayisisile konke kusukela ekuqaleni, lami ngikubone kufanele ukuthi ngikulobele umlando oqondileyo, komkhulu ohloniphekayo uTheyofelasi <verse eid="LUK 1:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 1:4"/>ukuze wazi iqiniso lezinto lezo ozifundisiweyo.<verse eid="LUK 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubikwa Kokuzalwa KukaJohane UMbhaphathizi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 1:5"/>Ngesikhathi sikaHerodi inkosi yaseJudiya kwakulomphristi okwakuthiwa nguZakhariya, owaye ngowesigaba sika-Abhija, umkakhe u-Elizabethi laye wayengowosendo luka-Aroni. <verse eid="LUK 1:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 1:6"/>Bobabili babelungile emehlweni kaNkulunkulu beyilandela yonke imilayo leziqondiso zeNkosi bengasoleki. <verse eid="LUK 1:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 1:7"/>Kodwa babengelabantwana ngoba u-Elizabethi wayeyinyumba njalo bobabili basebeluphele.<verse eid="LUK 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 1:8"/>Kwenzakala ukuthi isigaba sikaZakhariya siyiso esasimiselwe umsebenzi wethempeli ngalesosikhathi, <verse eid="LUK 1:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 1:9"/>wadliwa yinkatho ngokomkhuba wobuphristi, ukuthi angene ethempelini leNkosi ayetshisa impepha. <verse eid="LUK 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 1:10"/>Kwathi isikhathi sokutshisa impepha sesifikile, wonke amakholwa ayebuthene lapho ayekhuleka ephandle.<verse eid="LUK 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 1:11"/>Kwasekubonakala kuye ingilosi yeNkosi imi ngakwesokunene kwe-alithari lempepha. <verse eid="LUK 1:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 1:12"/>UZakhariya wathi eyibona wethuka wesaba kakhulu. <verse eid="LUK 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 1:13"/>Kodwa ingilosi yathi kuye, “Ungesabi, Zakhariya; umkhuleko wakho usuzwakele. Umkakho u-Elizabethi uzakuzalela indodana kufanele uyinike ibizo elithiwa nguJohane. <verse eid="LUK 1:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 1:14"/>Uzakuba yintokozo lenjabulo kuwe njalo abanengi bazathokoza ngenxa yokuzalwa kwakhe, <verse eid="LUK 1:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 1:15"/>ngoba uzakuba mkhulu emehlweni eNkosi. Kakumelanga anathe iwayini lanini loba yini ebilisiweyo enathwayo, njalo uzagcwaliswa ngoMoya oNgcwele kusukela ekuzalweni kwakhe. <verse eid="LUK 1:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 1:16"/>Uzaletha abantu bako-Israyeli abanengi eNkosini uNkulunkulu wabo. <verse eid="LUK 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 1:17"/>Uzahamba phambili kweNkosi ngomoya langamandla ka-Elija, ukuguqulela inhliziyo zaboyise ebantwaneni babo labayiziqholo elwazini lwabalungileyo, ukuqondisa abantu abalungiselelwe iNkosi.”<verse eid="LUK 1:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 1:18"/>UZakhariya wabuza ingilosi wathi, “Ngingaba leqiniso lakho njani lokho? Sengilixhegu njalo lomkami useluphele.”<verse eid="LUK 1:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 1:19"/>Ingilosi yaphendula yathi, “NginguGabhuriyeli mina. Ngima phambi kukaNkulunkulu, ngithunywe ukuzokhuluma lawe ngikutshela ngalezi izindaba ezinhle. <verse eid="LUK 1:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 1:20"/>Okwamanje uzakuba yisimungulu wehluleke ukukhuluma kuze kufike lolosuku okuzakwenzakala ngalo lokhu, ngoba kawuzange uwakholwe amazwi ami, wona azagcwaliseka ngesikhathi sawo esifaneleyo.”<verse eid="LUK 1:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 1:21"/>Sonke lesisikhathi abantu babelokhu bemlindele uZakhariya sebemangele ukuthi kungani wayethethe isikhathi eside kangako ethempelini. <verse eid="LUK 1:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 1:22"/>Waphuma esesehluleka ukukhuluma labo. Babona ukuthi wayebone umbono ethempelini ngoba wayelokhu eqhweba ngezandla, kodwa esehluleka ukukhuluma.<verse eid="LUK 1:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 1:23"/>Izopha lakhe seliphelile wabuyela ekhaya. <verse eid="LUK 1:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 1:24"/>Ngemva kwalokhu umkakhe u-Elizabethi wazithwala wasezifihla okwezinyanga ezinhlanu, <verse eid="LUK 1:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 1:25"/>esithi, “INkosi ingenzele lokhu. Kulezi insuku ilutshengisile uthando Lwayo yasusa ihlazo lami ebantwini.”<verse eid="LUK 1:25"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubikwa Kokuzalwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 1:26"/>Ngenyanga yesithupha yokuzithwala kuka-Elizabethi, uNkulunkulu wathuma ingilosi uGabhuriyeli eNazaretha, idolobho elaliseGalile, <verse eid="LUK 1:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 1:27"/>ukuya entombini egcweleyo eyayithembise ukutshada lendoda eyayithiwa nguJosefa, owesizukulwane sikaDavida. Ibizo lentombi egcweleyo le kwakunguMariya. <verse eid="LUK 1:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 1:28"/>Ingilosi yaya kuye yathi, “Sabona wena othole umusa kakhulukazi INkosi ilawe.”<verse eid="LUK 1:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 1:29"/>Amazwi ayo amhlupha kakhulu uMariya wamangala ukuthi kanti kwakuyikubingelela bani lokhu. <verse eid="LUK 1:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 1:30"/>Kodwa ingilosi yathi kuye, “Ungesabi Mariya, uthole umusa kuNkulunkulu. <verse eid="LUK 1:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 1:31"/>Uzakhulelwa ubelethe indodana, uyethe ibizo uthi nguJesu. <verse eid="LUK 1:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 1:32"/>Uzaba ngumuntu omkhulu abizwe ngokuthi yiNdodana yoPhezukonke. INkosi uNkulunkulu izamupha isihlalo sikayise uDavida, <verse eid="LUK 1:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 1:33"/>njalo uzabusa phezu kwendlu kaJakhobe laphakade; umbuso wakhe kawuyikuphela.”<verse eid="LUK 1:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 1:34"/>UMariya wayibuza ingilosi wathi, “Lokho kuzakwenzakala njani njengoba mina ngimsulwa ngingayazi indoda?”<verse eid="LUK 1:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 1:35"/>Ingilosi yaphendula yathi, “UMoya oNgcwele uzakwehlela phezu kwakho, lamandla akhe oPhezukonke azakusibekela. Ngakho ongcwele ozazalwa uzathiwa yiNdodana kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="LUK 1:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 1:36"/>Lo-Elizabethi isihlobo sakho uzakuba lomntwana ekuluphaleni kwakhe, yena okwakuthiwa yinyumba usesenyangeni yakhe yesithupha. <verse eid="LUK 1:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 1:37"/>Ngoba kakukho okwehlulayo kuNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="LUK 1:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 1:38"/>UMariya waphendula wathi, “Ngiyincekukazi yeNkosi. Kakwenzeke kimi njengoba utshilo.” Ingilosi yasisuka kuye.<verse eid="LUK 1:38"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UMariya Wethekelela U-Elizabethi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 1:39"/>Ngalesosikhathi uMariya waphanga wenza amalungiselelo waya edolobheni elizweni lamaqaqa eJudiya, <verse eid="LUK 1:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 1:40"/>lapho angena khona emzini kaZakhariya wabingelela u-Elizabethi. <verse eid="LUK 1:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 1:41"/>Kwathi u-Elizabethi esizwa ukubingelela kukaMariya, umntwana weqa esiswini sakhe, u-Elizabethi wagcwala ngoMoya oNgcwele. <verse eid="LUK 1:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 1:42"/>Wakhuluma ngelizwi eliphezulu wathi, “Ubusisiwe wena phakathi kwabesifazane, njalo ubusisiwe umntwana ozamzala! <verse eid="LUK 1:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 1:43"/>Kodwa kungani ngithole umusa ongaka mina, ukuba ngethekelelwe ngunina weNkosi yami? <verse eid="LUK 1:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 1:44"/>Ngonele ukuzwa ukubingelela kwakho, umntwana osesiswini sami weqa ngentokozo. <verse eid="LUK 1:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 1:45"/>Ubusisiwe lowo osekholiwe ukuthi lokho iNkosi ethe kuzakwenzeka kuye kuzagcwaliseka!”<verse eid="LUK 1:45"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ingoma KaMariya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 1:46"/>UMariya wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 1:46">“Umphefumulo wami uyayidumisa iNkosi<verse eid="LUK 1:46"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 1:47"/>lomoya wami uyathokoza kuNkulunkulu uMsindisi wami,<verse eid="LUK 1:47"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 1:48"/>ngoba ukunanzile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:48">ukuzehlisa kwencekukazi yakhe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 1:48">Kusukela manje zonke izizukulwane zizakuthi ngibusisiwe,<verse eid="LUK 1:48"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 1:49"/>ngoba uSomandla ungenzele izinto ezinkulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:49">lingcwele ibizo lakhe.<verse eid="LUK 1:49"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 1:50"/>Isihawu sakhe sifinyelela kulabo abamesabayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:50">kulandela isizukulwane ngesizukulwane.<verse eid="LUK 1:50"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 1:51"/>Uyenzile imisebenzi emikhulu ngengalo yakhe:</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:51">ubachithizile labo abaziqakisa ngemicabango yezinhliziyo zabo.<verse eid="LUK 1:51"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 1:52"/>Uwethule amakhosi ezihlalweni zawo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:52">kodwa wabaphakamisa abantukazana.<verse eid="LUK 1:52"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="LUK 1:53"/>Ubasuthisile abalambileyo ngezinto ezinhle,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:53">kodwa abanothileyo ubaxotshe bengaphathanga lutho.<verse eid="LUK 1:53"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="54" style="v" sid="LUK 1:54"/>Uyisizile inceku yakhe u-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:54">wakhumbula ukuba lesihawu<verse eid="LUK 1:54"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="LUK 1:55"/>ku-Abhrahama lezizukulwane zakhe laphakade,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:55">njengoba wakutsho kubokhokho bethu.”<verse eid="LUK 1:55"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="56" style="v" sid="LUK 1:56"/>UMariya wahlala lo-Elizabethi izinyanga ezazingaba ntathu wasebuyela ekhaya.<verse eid="LUK 1:56"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuzalwa KukaJohane UMbhaphathizi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="LUK 1:57"/>Kwathi isikhathi sika-Elizabethi sesiphelele esokubeletha wazala indodana. <verse eid="LUK 1:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="LUK 1:58"/>Omakhelwane bakhe lezihlobo bezwa ukuthi iNkosi yayimzwele isihawu esikhulu bathokoza kanye laye.<verse eid="LUK 1:58"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="59" style="v" sid="LUK 1:59"/>Ngosuku lwesificaminwembili beza ukuzasoka umntwana, bafuna ukuthi bamethe ibizo likayise uZakhariya, <verse eid="LUK 1:59"/><verse number="60" style="v" sid="LUK 1:60"/>kodwa unina wala wathi, “Hatshi! Kathiwe nguJohane.”<verse eid="LUK 1:60"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="61" style="v" sid="LUK 1:61"/>Bathi kuye, “Kakho ebantwini bakini olebizo lelo.”<verse eid="LUK 1:61"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v" sid="LUK 1:62"/>Bakhuluma ngezandla kuyise bedinga ukuthi yena uthanda ukuthi umntwana aphiwe liphi ibizo. <verse eid="LUK 1:62"/><verse number="63" style="v" sid="LUK 1:63"/>Wacela isibhebhedu sokulobela, wamangalisa wonke umuntu ngoba waloba ukuthi, “Ibizo lakhe nguJohane.” <verse eid="LUK 1:63"/><verse number="64" style="v" sid="LUK 1:64"/>Masinyane umlomo wakhe wavuleka lolimi lwakhe lwatshwaphuluka, waqalisa ukukhuluma edumisa uNkulunkulu. <verse eid="LUK 1:64"/><verse number="65" style="v" sid="LUK 1:65"/>Omakhelwane bonke bamangala kakhulu, kwathi elizweni lonke lamaqaqa eJudiya abantu babekhuluma ngalezizinto. <verse eid="LUK 1:65"/><verse number="66" style="v" sid="LUK 1:66"/>Wonke owezwayo ngalokho wamangala ebuza esithi, “Kambe uzakuba yini umntwana lo?” Ngoba isandla seNkosi sasilaye.<verse eid="LUK 1:66"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ingoma KaZakhariya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="67" style="v" sid="LUK 1:67"/>Uyise uZakhariya wagcwala ngoMoya oNgcwele waphrofitha wathi:<verse eid="LUK 1:67"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="68" style="v" sid="LUK 1:68"/>“Udumo kalube seNkosini, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:68">ngoba ubuyile ukuzahlenga abantu bakhe.<verse eid="LUK 1:68"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="69" style="v" sid="LUK 1:69"/>Iluphakamisile uphondo lwensindiso yethu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:69">endlini yenceku yayo uDavida<verse eid="LUK 1:69"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="70" style="v" sid="LUK 1:70"/>(njengoba yatsho ngabaphrofethi bayo abangcwele ekadeni),<verse eid="LUK 1:70"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="71" style="v" sid="LUK 1:71"/>ukusindiswa ezitheni zethu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:71">lesandleni sabo bonke abasizondayo,<verse eid="LUK 1:71"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="72" style="v" sid="LUK 1:72"/>ukuze atshengise isihawu kubokhokho bethu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:72">lokukhumbula isivumelwano sakhe esingcwele,<verse eid="LUK 1:72"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="73" style="v" sid="LUK 1:73"/>isifungo asifunga kubaba wethu u-Abhrahama:<verse eid="LUK 1:73"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="74" style="v" sid="LUK 1:74"/>ukusikhulula esandleni sezitha zethu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:74">size siyikhonze singelakwesaba<verse eid="LUK 1:74"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="75" style="v" sid="LUK 1:75"/>ngobungcwele langokulunga phambi kwayo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:75">ngazozonke insuku zethu.<verse eid="LUK 1:75"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="76" style="v" sid="LUK 1:76"/>Wena mntanami, uzathiwa ungumphrofethi woPhezukonke;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:76">ngoba uzahamba phambili kweNkosi uyilungisele indlela,<verse eid="LUK 1:76"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="77" style="v" sid="LUK 1:77"/>ukunika abantu bayo ukwazi insindiso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:77">ngokuthethelelwa kwezono zabo,<verse eid="LUK 1:77"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="78" style="v" sid="LUK 1:78"/>ngenxa yomusa kaNkulunkulu wethu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:78">ilanga liphuma lize kithi livela ezulwini,<verse eid="LUK 1:78"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="79" style="v" sid="LUK 1:79"/>likhanyise kulabo abahlezi ebumnyameni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 1:79">lasethunzini lokufa,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 1:79">ukukhokhelela inyawo zethu endleleni yokuthula.”<verse eid="LUK 1:79"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="80" style="v" sid="LUK 1:80"/>Umntwana wakhula waqina emoyeni; waphila enkangala waze wavela obala ku-Israyeli.<verse eid="LUK 1:80"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="LUK 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuzalwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 2:1"/>Ngalezonsuku uKhesari Agastasi wakhupha isimemezelo sokuthi abantu babalwe kulolonke ilizwe lombuso wamaRoma. <verse eid="LUK 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 2:2"/>(Lokhu kwakuyikubalwa kwabantu kokuqala okwenzakala uKhwirinu engumbusi wase-Asiriya.) <verse eid="LUK 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 2:3"/>Wonke umuntu waya edolobheni lakibo wayabhalisa.<verse eid="LUK 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 2:4"/>UJosefa laye wahamba esuka edolobheni leNazaretha eseGalile waya eJudiya, eBhethilehema idolobho likaDavida, ngoba wayengowendlu losendo lukaDavida. <verse eid="LUK 2:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 2:5"/>Waya khona ukuyabhalisa eloMariya, owayesethembise ukwendela kuye, esekhulelwe. <verse eid="LUK 2:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 2:6"/>Bathi bekhonale safika isikhathi sokubelethwa komntwana, <verse eid="LUK 2:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 2:7"/>wazibula ngendodana. Wayigoqela ngamalembu, wayilalisa emkolweni wokudlela izifuyo ngoba babengelandawo endlini yezihambi.<verse eid="LUK 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abelusi Lezingilosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 2:8"/>Kwakulabelusi ababehlala emlageni eduze kwalapho, belinda imihlambi yabo yezimvu ebusuku. <verse eid="LUK 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 2:9"/>Ingilosi yeNkosi yabonakala kubo, inkazimulo yeNkosi yakhanya ibazingelezile, ngakho besaba kakhulu. <verse eid="LUK 2:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 2:10"/>Kodwa ingilosi yathi kubo, “Lingesabi. Ngizolitshela izindaba ezinhle ezizaletha intokozo enkulu ebantwini bonke. <verse eid="LUK 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 2:11"/>Lamuhla lizalelwe uMsindisi emzini kaDavida; unguKhristu iNkosi. <verse eid="LUK 2:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 2:12"/>Lokhu kuzakuba yisibonakaliso kini: Lizathola umntwana egoqelwe ngamalembu elele emkolweni.”<verse eid="LUK 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 2:13"/>Masinyane kwaqhamuka ixuku lebandla lasezulwini lengilosi lidumisa uNkulunkulu lisithi,<verse eid="LUK 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 2:14"/>“Udumo kuNkulunkulu emazulwini aphezulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 2:14">lokuthula emhlabeni kulabo abathole umusa kuye.”<verse eid="LUK 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 2:15"/>Kwathi izingilosi sezibatshiyile zabuyela ezulwini, abelusi bakhulumisana bathi, “Kasihambeni siye eBhethilehema siyobona into le esiyenzakele, iNkosi esisitshele ngayo.”<verse eid="LUK 2:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 2:16"/>Bahle basuka ngokuphangisa, bafica uMariya loJosefa losane olwalulele emkolweni wokudlela izifuyo. <verse eid="LUK 2:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 2:17"/>Bathi sebembonile umntwana, batshela abanengi ngalokho ababekutshelwe mayelana lomntwana lo, <verse eid="LUK 2:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 2:18"/>kwathi bonke abalizwayo bamangaliswa yilokho abakuzwa ngabelusi. <verse eid="LUK 2:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 2:19"/>Kodwa uMariya wazenza igugu zonke lezizinto wazishicilela enhliziyweni yakhe. <verse eid="LUK 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 2:20"/>Abelusi babuyela, bedumisa njalo bebabaza uNkulunkulu ngezinto zonke ababezizwile njalo bazibona, zaba yikho kanye ababekutsheliwe.<verse eid="LUK 2:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 2:21"/>Ngosuku lwesificaminwembili, sekuyisikhathi sokuthi asokwe, wethiwa ibizo elithi nguJesu, ibizo ayelithiwe yingilosi engakabunjwa esiswini.<verse eid="LUK 2:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uyethulwa EThempelini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 2:22"/>Kwathi lapho sesiphelile isikhathi sabo sokuhlanjululwa ngokomthetho kaMosi, uJosefa loMariya bamusa eJerusalema ukuyamnikela eNkosini <verse eid="LUK 2:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 2:23"/>(njengokulotshiweyo eMthethweni weNkosi ukuthi, “Lonke izibulo lesilisa kumele linikelwe eNkosini”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.23 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 13.2, 12</char></note>), <verse eid="LUK 2:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 2:24"/>njalo kwenziwe umhlatshelo kulandelwa lokho okutshiwo nguMthetho weNkosi othi: “amajuba amabili loba inkwilimba ezisesezincane ezimbili.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.24 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ULevi 12.8</char></note><verse eid="LUK 2:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 2:25"/>Kwakukhona eJerusalema indoda eyayithiwa nguSimiyoni, yayilungile njalo ikholwa. Yayilindele ukududuzwa kuka-Israyeli, njalo uMoya oNgcwele wawuphezu kwayo. <verse eid="LUK 2:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 2:26"/>Kwakwambuliwe kuye nguMoya oNgcwele ukuthi wayengayikufa engakaboni uKhristu weNkosi. <verse eid="LUK 2:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 2:27"/>Waholwa nguMoya wangena emagumeni ethempeli. Kwathi abazali sebemlethile umntwana uJesu ukumenzela lokho okwakufunwa ngumkhuba woMthetho, <verse eid="LUK 2:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 2:28"/>uSimiyoni wamgona ngezingalo zakhe wadumisa uNkulunkulu esithi:<verse eid="LUK 2:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 2:29"/>“Thixo, Nkosi, njengoba wavele wathembisa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 2:29">manje-ke iyekele ihambe ngokuthula inceku yakho.<verse eid="LUK 2:29"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 2:30"/>Ngoba amehlo ami aseyibonile insindiso yakho,<verse eid="LUK 2:30"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 2:31"/>oyilungisileyo phambi kwezizwe zonke,<verse eid="LUK 2:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 2:32"/>ukukhanya kokwambulela abeZizwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 2:32">lokwenkazimulo yabantu bakho bako-Israyeli.”<verse eid="LUK 2:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 2:33"/>Oyise lonina womntwana bamangala kakhulu ngalokho okwakukhulunywa ngaye. <verse eid="LUK 2:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 2:34"/>USimiyoni wasebabusisa, wathi kuMariya unina: “Umntwana lo umiselwe ukuwa lokuvuka kwabanengi ko-Israyeli, lokuba yisibonakaliso esizagconwa, <verse eid="LUK 2:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 2:35"/>ukwenzela ukuthi imicabango yabanengi ivele obala. Njalo inkemba izawugwaza umphefumulo wakho lawe.”<verse eid="LUK 2:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 2:36"/>Kwakukhona njalo umphrofethikazi, u-Ana, indodakazi kaFanuweli, owesizwana sika-Asheri. Wayesemdala kakhulu: wayephile lomkakhe okweminyaka eyisikhombisa ngemva kokwenda kwakhe, <verse eid="LUK 2:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 2:37"/>wasesiba ngumfelokazi waze waba leminyaka engamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lane. Kazange lanini asuke ethempelini kodwa wayekhonza ubusuku lemini, ezila njalo ekhuleka. <verse eid="LUK 2:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 2:38"/>Wabuya kubo ngalesosikhathi wabonga kuNkulunkulu, wakhuluma ngomntwana kubo bonke ababelindele ukuhlengwa kweJerusalema.<verse eid="LUK 2:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 2:39"/>Kwathi lapho uJosefa loMariya sebekwenzile konke okwakufuneka ngoMthetho weNkosi babuyela eGalile, edolobheni lakibo elaseNazaretha. <verse eid="LUK 2:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 2:40"/>Umntwana wakhula, waqina; wagcwala inhlakanipho, njalo umusa kaNkulunkulu waba phezu kwakhe.<verse eid="LUK 2:40"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umfana UJesu EseThempelini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 2:41"/>Iminyaka yonke abazali bakhe baya eJerusalema belanda uMkhosi wePhasika. <verse eid="LUK 2:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 2:42"/>Kwathi eseleminyaka elitshumi lambili baya emkhosini njengenjayelo. <verse eid="LUK 2:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 2:43"/>Kwathi uMkhosi usuphelile, abazali bakhe sebebuyela ekhaya, umfana uJesu wasala eJerusalema, kodwa bona belibele. <verse eid="LUK 2:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 2:44"/>Bazihambela ilanga lonke bona becabanga ukuthi ukhona edwendweni lwabo. Basebeqalisa ukumdinga phakathi kwezihlobo zabo labangane. <verse eid="LUK 2:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 2:45"/>Bathi sebemswele babuyela eJerusalema bayamdinga. <verse eid="LUK 2:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 2:46"/>Ngemva kwensuku ezintathu bamfumana emagumeni ethempeli ehlezi phakathi kwabafundisi elalele njalo ebabuza imibuzo. <verse eid="LUK 2:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 2:47"/>Wonke umuntu owamuzwayo wamangala ngokuzwisisa kwakhe kanye lempendulo zakhe. <verse eid="LUK 2:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 2:48"/>Abazali bakhe bathi bembona bamangala kakhulu. Unina wathi kuye, “Ndodana, kungani usinqinekisa kangaka? Uyihlo lami besesikhathazekile sikudinga.”<verse eid="LUK 2:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 2:49"/>Yena wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Belivele lingidingelani kanti? Belingazi yini ukuthi bekumele ngibe sendlini kaBaba?”</char> <verse eid="LUK 2:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 2:50"/>Kodwa kabazwisisanga lokho ayekutsho kubo.<verse eid="LUK 2:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 2:51"/>Wasehamba labo eNazaretha wahlala ebalalela. Kodwa unina wazenza igugu zonke lezi izinto enhliziyweni yakhe. <verse eid="LUK 2:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 2:52"/>UJesu wakhula ngenhlakanipho, langomzimba langokuthandwa nguNkulunkulu labantu.<verse eid="LUK 2:52"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="LUK 3"/>
  <para style="s1">UJohane UMbhaphathizi Ulungisa Indlela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 3:1"/>Ngomnyaka wetshumi lanhlanu wokubusa kukaThibheriyasi Khesari ngesikhathi uPhontiyasi Philathu engumbusi eJudiya, uHerodi engumbusi eGalile, umfowabo uFiliphu engumbusi wase-Ithuriya leThrakhonithi, njalo loLisaniya engumbusi wase-Abhilene <verse eid="LUK 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 3:2"/>ngesikhathi leso u-Anasi loKhayifasi bengabaphristi abakhulu, kwafika ilizwi likaNkulunkulu kuJohane indodana kaZakhariya esenkangala. <verse eid="LUK 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 3:3"/>Wawuhamba wonke umango waseJodani, etshumayela ubhaphathizo lokuphenduka ukuze izono zithethelelwe. <verse eid="LUK 3:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 3:4"/>Njengoba kulotshiwe encwadini yamazwi ka-Isaya umphrofethi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 3:4">“Ilizwi lalowo omemezayo enkangala,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 3:4">‘Lungisani indlela kaThixo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 3:4">yenzani indlela zakhe ziqonde.<verse eid="LUK 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 3:5"/>Zonke izigodi zizagcwaliswa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 3:5">izintaba zonke lamaqaqa kuzakwehliselwa phansi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 3:5">Izindlela zonke ezimazombe zizaqonda,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 3:5">izindlela ezimakhilikithi zizakuba butshelezi.<verse eid="LUK 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 3:6"/>Abantu bonke bazayibona insindiso kaNkulunkulu.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 40.3-5</char></note>”<verse eid="LUK 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 3:7"/>UJohane wathi emaxukwini abantu ababuya ukuzobhaphathizwa nguye, “Lina nzalo yezinyoka! Lilimukiswe ngubani ukuthi libalekele ulaka oluzayo na? <verse eid="LUK 3:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 3:8"/>Thelani izithelo ezihambelana lokuphenduka. Njalo lingaqali ukuzitshela ukuthi, ‘Silo-Abhrahama ongubaba wethu.’ Ngoba ngilitshela ukuthi kuwonala amatshe uNkulunkulu angamenzela u-Abhrahama abantwana. <verse eid="LUK 3:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 3:9"/>Ihloka selivele selisezimpandeni zezihlahla, njalo zonke izihlahla ezingatheli izithelo ezilungileyo zizaganyulwa, ziphoselwe emlilweni.”<verse eid="LUK 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 3:10"/>Abantu bambuza bathi, “Pho kumele senzeni?”<verse eid="LUK 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 3:11"/>UJohane waphendula wathi, “Leyondoda elamajazi amabili kayimuphe ongelalo elinye lalowo olokudla kenze njalo.”<verse eid="LUK 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 3:12"/>Labathelisi labo beza ukuzabhaphathizwa. Babuza bathi, “Mfundisi, kumele senzeni?”<verse eid="LUK 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 3:13"/>Wabatshela wathi, “Lingathelisi ledlulise okufunekayo.”<verse eid="LUK 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 3:14"/>Abanye abebutho bambuza bathi, “Thina-ke senzeni?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 3:14">Waphendula wathi, “Lingancindezeli ukuthi liphiwe imali njalo lingabeki muntu umlandu wamanga njalo lisuthiseke ngomholo wenu.”<verse eid="LUK 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 3:15"/>Abantu babehlezi belindele njalo bonke babezibuza ezinhliziyweni zabo ingabe uJohane wayenguye yini uKhristu. <verse eid="LUK 3:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 3:16"/>UJohane wabaphendula bonke wathi, “Mina ngilibhaphathiza ngamanzi. Kodwa yena olamandla kulami uyeza, akungilingananga ukuthukulula imichilo yamanyathela akhe. Uzalibhaphathiza ngoMoya oNgcwele langomlilo. <verse eid="LUK 3:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 3:17"/>Isitsha sakhe sokwela sisesandleni sakhe ukuba athanyele isiza sakhe njalo abuthele amabele akhe esiphaleni, kodwa uzatshisa amakhoba ngomlilo ongacitshekiyo.” <verse eid="LUK 3:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 3:18"/>Waphinda walaya abantu ngamanye amazwi amanengi njalo watshumayela kubo ivangeli.<verse eid="LUK 3:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 3:19"/>Kodwa kwathi uJohane esekhuze uHerodi umbusi ngenxa kaHerodiyasi, umkamfowabo, langezinye izinto ezimbi ayezenzile, <verse eid="LUK 3:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 3:20"/>uHerodi wakuhlanganisa lokhu konke: Wamvalela uJohane entolongweni.<verse eid="LUK 3:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubhaphathizwa KukaJesu Lembali Yosendo Lwakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 3:21"/>Kwathi bonke abantu bebhaphathizwa, loJesu laye wabhaphathizwa. Wathi ekhuleka izulu lavuleka <verse eid="LUK 3:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 3:22"/>uMoya oNgcwele wehlela kuye elesimo sejuba. Kweza ilizwi livela ezulwini lathi: “Wena uyiNdodana yami engiyithandayo; ngiyathokoza kakhulu ngawe.”<verse eid="LUK 3:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 3:23"/>UJesu wayeseleminyaka engaba ngamatshumi amathathu eqalisa umsebenzi wakhe wokutshumayela. Kwakukhunjulwa ukuthi uyindodana kaJosefa,</para>
  <para style="b" vid="LUK 3:23"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:23">indodana kaHeli, <verse eid="LUK 3:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 3:24"/>indodana kaMathathi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:24">indodana kaLevi, indodana kaMeliki,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:24">indodana kaJanayi, indodana kaJosefa,<verse eid="LUK 3:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 3:25"/>indodana kaMathathiyasi, indodana ka-Amosi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:25">indodana kaNahumi, indodana ka-Esili,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:25">indodana kaNagayi, <verse eid="LUK 3:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 3:26"/>indodana kaMahathi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:26">indodana kaMathathiyasi, indodana kaSemeyini,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:26">indodana kaJoseki, indodana kaJoda,<verse eid="LUK 3:26"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 3:27"/>indodana kaJohanani, indodana kaResa,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:27">indodana kaZerubhabheli, indodana kaSheyalithiyeli,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:27">indodana kaNeri, <verse eid="LUK 3:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 3:28"/>indodana kaMeliki,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:28">indodana ka-Adi, indodana kaKhosamu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:28">indodana ka-Elimadami, indodana ka-Eri,<verse eid="LUK 3:28"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 3:29"/>indodana kaJoshuwa, indodana ka-Eliyezeri,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:29">indodana kaJorimu, indodana kaMathathi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:29">indodana kaLevi, <verse eid="LUK 3:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 3:30"/>indodana kaSimiyoni,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:30">indodana kaJuda, indodana kaJosefa,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:30">indodana kaJonami, indodana ka-Eliyakhimu,<verse eid="LUK 3:30"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 3:31"/>indodana kaMeleya, indodana kaMena,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:31">indodana kaMathatha, indodana kaNathani,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:31">indodana kaDavida, <verse eid="LUK 3:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 3:32"/>indodana kaJese,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:32">indodana ka-Obhedi, indodana kaBhowazi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:32">indodana kaSalimoni, indodana kaNashoni,<verse eid="LUK 3:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 3:33"/>indodana ka-Aminadabi, indodana kaRamu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:33">indodana kaHezironi, indodana kaPherezi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:33">indodana kaJuda, <verse eid="LUK 3:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 3:34"/>indodana kaJakhobe,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:34">indodana ka-Isaka, indodana ka-Abhrahama,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:34">indodana kaThera, indodana kaNahori,<verse eid="LUK 3:34"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 3:35"/>indodana kaSerugi, indodana kaRewu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:35">indodana kaPhelegi, indodana ka-Ebha,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:35">indodana kaShela, <verse eid="LUK 3:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 3:36"/>indodana kaKhayinani,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:36">indodana ka-Ariphazadi, indodana kaShemu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:36">indodana kaNowa, indodana kaLameki,<verse eid="LUK 3:36"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 3:37"/>indodana kaMethusela, indodana ka-Enoki,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:37">indodana kaJaredi, indodana kaMahalaleli,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:37">indodana kaKhenani, <verse eid="LUK 3:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 3:38"/>indodana ka-Enoshi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:38">indodana kaSethi, indodana ka-Adamu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 3:38">indodana kaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="LUK 3:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="LUK 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukulingwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 4:1"/>UJesu egcwele uMoya oNgcwele wasuka evela eJodani wasekhokhelwa nguMoya wamusa enkangala, <verse eid="LUK 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 4:2"/>lapho alingwa khona nguSathane okwensuku ezingamatshumi amane. Kadlanga lutho ngalezonsuku, ekupheleni kwazo, wayeselambile.<verse eid="LUK 4:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 4:3"/>USathane wathi kuye, “Nxa uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu, tshela ilitshe leli ukuthi liphenduke libe yisinkwa.”<verse eid="LUK 4:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 4:4"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kulotshiwe ukuthi: ‘Umuntu kaphili ngesinkwa kuphela.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 8.3</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="LUK 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 4:5"/>USathane wamholela endaweni ephakemeyo wamtshengisa ngesikhathi esifitshane yonke imibuso yomhlaba. <verse eid="LUK 4:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 4:6"/>Wasesithi kuye, “Ngizakunika amandla lenkazimulo yayo yonke ngoba kuphiwe mina njalo ngingapha loba ngubani engifuna ukumupha. <verse eid="LUK 4:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 4:7"/>Ungangikhonza konke kuzakuba ngokwakho.”<verse eid="LUK 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 4:8"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kulotshiwe ukuthi: ‘Khonza iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho njalo usebenzele yena yedwa.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 6.13</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="LUK 4:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 4:9"/>USathane wamholela eJerusalema wayamisa engqongeni yethempeli. Wathi kuye “Nxa uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu, ziphosele phansi usuka lapha. <verse eid="LUK 4:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 4:10"/>Kalokho kulotshiwe ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 4:10">‘Uzayala izingilosi zakhe ngawe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 4:10">ukuthi zikulondoloze ngokunanzelela;<verse eid="LUK 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 4:11"/>zizakuphakamisa ezandleni zazo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 4:11">ukuze ungatshayeki ngonyawo lwakho elitsheni.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 91.11-12</char></note>”<verse eid="LUK 4:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 4:12"/>UJesu waphendula wathi <char style="wj">“Kuthiwa khona, ‘Ungayilingi iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 6.16</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="LUK 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 4:13"/>Kwathi uSathane eseqedile ukumlinga konke wamtshiya walindela ukuzamlinga njalo ngesinye isikhathi.<verse eid="LUK 4:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uyaliwa ENazaretha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 4:14"/>UJesu wabuyela eGalile elamandla kaMoya, izindaba ngaye zanda kuwo wonke umango. <verse eid="LUK 4:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 4:15"/>Wafundisa emasinagogweni abo, abantu bonke bamdumisa.<verse eid="LUK 4:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 4:16"/>Waya eNazaretha lapho akhulela khona kwathi ngeSabatha waya esinagogweni njengenjayelo yakhe. Wasukuma wabala. <verse eid="LUK 4:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 4:17"/>Umqulu womphrofethi u-Isaya wedluliselwa kuye. Wawutshombulula wafumana indawo okulotshwe khona kwathiwa:<verse eid="LUK 4:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 4:18"/>
    <char style="wj">“Umoya kaThixo uphezu kwami,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 4:18">
    <char style="wj">ngoba uThixo ungigcobile ukuba</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 4:18">
    <char style="wj">ngitshumayele izindaba ezinhle kwabampofu.</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 4:18">
    <char style="wj">Ungithumile ukuba ngimemezele ukukhululwa kwabathunjiweyo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 4:18">
    <char style="wj">lokusiliswa kweziphofu ukuthi zibone,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 4:18">
    <char style="wj">ukukhululwa kwabancindezelweyo,</char><verse eid="LUK 4:18"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 4:19"/>
    <char style="wj">lokumemezela umnyaka womusa kaThixo.”</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">4.19 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 61.1-2</char>
    </note><verse eid="LUK 4:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 4:20"/>Wasewugoqa, wawubuyisela esikhonzini sebandla, wahlala phansi. Amehlo abo bonke esinagogweni athi nhlo kuye, <verse eid="LUK 4:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 4:21"/>waseqalisa ngokuthi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lamhla umbhalo usugcwalisekile lizizwela.”</char><verse eid="LUK 4:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 4:22"/>Bonke bakhuluma kuhle ngaye bemangaliswa ngamazwi amnandi ayephuma emlonyeni wakhe. Babuzana besithi, “Kanti lo kasindodana kaJosefa na?”<verse eid="LUK 4:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 4:23"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngeqiniso lizasitsho kimi lesi isaga esithi: ‘Nyanga, zelaphe! Yenza lapha edolobheni lakini lokho esizwa kuthiwa wakwenza eKhaphenawume.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 4:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 4:24"/>Waqhubeka wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiqinisile ngithi kakulamphrofethi oyamukelekayo edolobheni lakibo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 4:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 4:25"/><char style="wj">Ngiyaqinisa kini ukuthi babebanengi abafelokazi ko-Israyeli ngesikhathi sika-Elija, lapho umkhathi wavaleka okweminyaka emithathu elengxenye kwaba lendlala enzima elizweni lonke.</char> <verse eid="LUK 4:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 4:26"/><char style="wj">Kodwa u-Elija kazange athunywe lakoyedwa wabo, ngaphandle komfelokazi waseZarefathi emangweni waseSidoni.</char> <verse eid="LUK 4:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 4:27"/><char style="wj">Babebanengi ko-Israyeli ababelobulephero ngesikhathi sika-Elisha umphrofethi, kodwa munye kuphela phakathi kwabo owahlanjululwayo, uNamani waseSiriya.”</char><verse eid="LUK 4:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 4:28"/>Bonke abantu ababesesinagogweni bathi bekuzwa lokhu bathukuthela kakhulu. <verse eid="LUK 4:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 4:29"/>Basukuma, bamtshovela phandle kwedolobho bamusa eliweni loqaqa okwakwakhelwe kulo idolobho beqonde ukumsunduzela phansi edongeni. <verse eid="LUK 4:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 4:30"/>Kodwa wasuka wahamba wadabula phakathi kwexuku labantu.<verse eid="LUK 4:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhupha Umoya Omubi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 4:31"/>Wasesiya eKhaphenawume, idolobho elaliseGalile, kwathi ngeSabatha wafundisa abantu. <verse eid="LUK 4:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 4:32"/>Bamangaliswa yikufundisa kwakhe ngoba intshumayelo yakhe yayilesisindo.<verse eid="LUK 4:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 4:33"/>Esinagogweni lapho kwakulendoda eyayiphethwe lidimoni, umoya ongcolileyo. Yaklabalala ngelizwi layo lonke yathi, <verse eid="LUK 4:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 4:34"/>“Hamba khatshana! Ufunani kithi, Jesu waseNazaretha? Ulande ukuza sibhubhisa na? Ngiyakwazi ukuthi ungubani, ungoNgcwele kaNkulunkulu!”<verse eid="LUK 4:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 4:35"/>UJesu wamkhuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Thula! Phuma kuye!”</char> Idimoni layilahla phansi indoda phambi kwabo bonke laphuma lingayilimazanga indoda.<verse eid="LUK 4:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 4:36"/>Bonke abantu bamangala kakhulu bakhulumisana besithi, “Yikufundisa bani lokhu? Ulaya imimoya emibi ngegunya langamandla layo iphume!” <verse eid="LUK 4:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 4:37"/>Zamemetheka izindaba ngaye kuwo wonke umango walapho.<verse eid="LUK 4:37"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uphilisa Abanengi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 4:38"/>UJesu wasuka esinagogweni waya emzini kaSimoni. Uninazala kaSimoni wayegula ebanjwe ngumkhuhlane woqhuqho onzima basebecela uJesu ukuthi amsize. <verse eid="LUK 4:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 4:39"/>Wasekhothamela kuye wakhuza umkhuhlane lowo wahle waphuma kuye. Yena wathi lothu, waqalisa ukubaphakela.<verse eid="LUK 4:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 4:40"/>Kwathi ilanga selitshona abantu baletha kuJesu bonke ababe lemikhuhlane eyehlukeneyo, wabasilisa ngokubeka izandla phezu kwalowo lalowo ngamunye. <verse eid="LUK 4:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 4:41"/>Phezu kwalokho amadimoni aphuma kwabanengi ememeza esithi, “Wena uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu!” Kodwa wawakhuza kazawavumela ukuthi akhulume ngoba ayemazi ukuthi unguKhristu.<verse eid="LUK 4:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 4:42"/>Emadabukakusa uJesu wasuka waya endaweni ethuleyo. Abantu babemdinga bathi sebefike lapho ayekhona, bazama ukumvimba ukuthi angabatshiyi. <verse eid="LUK 4:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 4:43"/>Kodwa wathi, <char style="wj">“Kumele ngitshumayele izindaba ezinhle zombuso kaNkulunkulu kwamanye amadolobho, ngoba yikho engakulandayo.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 4:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 4:44"/>Waqhubeka etshumayela emasinagogweni aseJudiya.<verse eid="LUK 4:44"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="LUK 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukubizwa Kwabafundi Bokuqala</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 5:1"/>Ngelinye ilanga uJesu emi eduze kweChibi laseGenezaretha abantu beminyezelana kuye belalela ilizwi likaNkulunkulu, <verse eid="LUK 5:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 5:2"/>wabona ekhunjini lechibi izikepe ezimbili zitshiywe khonapho ngabagoli benhlanzi ababegezisa omambule babo. <verse eid="LUK 5:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 5:3"/>Wangena kwesinye isikepe esasingesikaSimoni, wamcela ukuthi akathi gudlu asuke kancane okhunjini. Wasehlala phansi wafundisa abantu ehlezi esikepeni.<verse eid="LUK 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 5:4"/>Eseqedile ukukhuluma wathi kuSimoni, <char style="wj">“Gwedla ungene enzikini uphosele omambule bakho ukuze ubambe inhlanzi.”</char><verse eid="LUK 5:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 5:5"/>USimoni waphendula wathi, “Nkosi, sisebenze gadalala ubusuku bonke, kodwa kasibambanga lutho. Kodwa njengoba usitsho njalo ngizabehlisa omambule.”<verse eid="LUK 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 5:6"/>Kwathi sebenze njalo babamba inhlanzi ezaba zinengi kwaze kwaqalisa ukudabuka omambule. <verse eid="LUK 5:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 5:7"/>Basebebiza abakhula babo kwesinye isikepe ukuthi bazobelekelela. Beza abakhula babo kwesinye isikepe ukuthi bazobelekelela. Beza bazigcwalisa zombili izikepe zathi phamu zaze zaqalisa ukutshona.<verse eid="LUK 5:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 5:8"/>Kwathi uSimoni Phethro ekubona lokhu wazilahla phansi phambi kukaJesu wathi, “Suka kimi, Nkosi; ngingumuntu oyisoni!” <verse eid="LUK 5:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 5:9"/>Ngoba yena labakhula bakhe babemangele ngenhlanzi ababezibambile, <verse eid="LUK 5:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 5:10"/>kwamangalisa njalo uJakhobe loJohane amadodana kaZebhediya, ababe phathisana loSimoni.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 5:10">UJesu wasesithi kuSimoni, <char style="wj">“Ungesabi; kusukela manje usuzagola abantu.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 5:11"/>Basebedonsela izikepe zabo okhunjini batshiya konke bamlandela.<verse eid="LUK 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Indoda Eyayilobulephero</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 5:12"/>Kwathi uJesu ekwelinye lamadolobho kweza indoda eyayigcwele ubulephero. Yathi ibona uJesu yathi mbo phansi ngobuso yamncenga yathi, “Nkosi, nxa uthanda ungangihlambulula.”<verse eid="LUK 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 5:13"/>UJesu welula isandla sakhe wayithinta indoda leyo. Wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyathanda. Hlambuluka!”</char> Masinyane nje ubulephero bahle baphela.<verse eid="LUK 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 5:14"/>UJesu waseyilaya wathi, <char style="wj">“Ungatsheli muntu kodwa hamba uyeziveza kumphristi ubusunikela umhlatshelo wokuhlanjululwa kwakho owamiswa nguMosi ukuze kube yibufakazi kubo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 5:15"/>Kodwa udumo lwakhe lwanda ngamandla, yikho amaxuku abantu eza ukuzamuzwa lokusiliswa emikhuhlaneni yabo. <verse eid="LUK 5:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 5:16"/>Kodwa kanengi uJesu wayesithi nyelele ayesithela ezindaweni ezithuleyo ayekhuleka.<verse eid="LUK 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Umuntu Owome Umhlubulo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 5:17"/>Ngelinye ilanga elokhu efundisa, kwakuhlezi khonapho abaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho ababephuma emizini yonke yaseGalile abanye bevela eJudiya laseJerusalema. Amandla eNkosi ayekhona kuye ukuze asilise abagulayo. <verse eid="LUK 5:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 5:18"/>Kwafika amanye amadoda ethwele indoda eyayome umhlubulo ngecansi efuna ukungena laye endlini ambeke phambi kukaJesu. <verse eid="LUK 5:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 5:19"/>Athi esehlulekile ngenxa yokuminyana kwabantu, akhwela ephahleni, amehlisela phansi ngesikhala amuthi qithi phakathi laphakathi kwabantu phambi kukaJesu.<verse eid="LUK 5:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 5:20"/>Kwathi uJesu ebona ukholo lwawo wathi, <char style="wj">“Mngane, izono zakho sezithethelelwe.”</char><verse eid="LUK 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 5:21"/>AbaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho bakhonona bathi, “Ungubani yena lo umuntu okhuluma ehlambaza na? Ngubani ongathethelela izono ngaphandle kukaNkulunkulu kuphela?”<verse eid="LUK 5:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 5:22"/>UJesu wayekwazi abakucabangayo wasebuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungani linakana izinto ezinje ezinhliziyweni zenu?</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 5:23"/><char style="wj">Yikuphi okulula: ukuthi, ‘Izono zakho sezithethelelwe,’ loba ukuthi, ‘Sukuma uhambe’?</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 5:24"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ukuze lazi ukuthi iNdodana yoMuntu ilamandla okuthethelela izono emhlabeni.”</char> Wasesithi kuyo indoda eyome umhlubulo, <char style="wj">“Sukuma, thatha icansi lakho uhambe uye ekhaya.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 5:25"/>Masinyane wathi lothu phambi kwabo, wabutha ayekade elele phezu kwakho waya ekhaya edumisa uNkulunkulu. <verse eid="LUK 5:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 5:26"/>Wonke umuntu wamangala, badumisa uNkulunkulu. Bamangala kakhulu bathi, “Lamuhla sibone izimanga.”<verse eid="LUK 5:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubizwa KukaLevi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 5:27"/>Ngemva kwalokhu uJesu waphuma wasebona umthelisi owayethiwa nguLevi ehlezi endaweni yakhe yokuthelisa. UJesu wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Ngilandela,”</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 5:28"/>uLevi wasukuma watshiya konke wamlandela.<verse eid="LUK 5:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 5:29"/>ULevi wasesenzela uJesu idili elikhulu endlini yakhe kukhona ixuku labathelisi labanye besidla labo. <verse eid="LUK 5:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 5:30"/>Kodwa abaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho abeqembu labo basola kubafundi bakhe bathi, “Lenzelani ukudla linathe labathelisi kanye lezoni na?”<verse eid="LUK 5:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 5:31"/>UJesu wabaphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kakusibo abaphilayo abaswela umelaphi, kodwa ngabagulayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 5:32"/><char style="wj">Kangilandanga ukubiza abulungileyo, kodwa ukubiza izoni ukuba ziphenduke.”</char><verse eid="LUK 5:32"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ubuzwa Ngokuzila</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 5:33"/>Bathi kuye, “Abafundi bakaJohane bazila kanengi bekhuleka njalo labafundi babaFarisi labo benza njalo, kodwa abakho bahlala besidla, benatha.”<verse eid="LUK 5:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 5:34"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungenzeka yini ukuzilisa izethekeli zomyeni emthimbeni umyeni eseselazo na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 5:35"/><char style="wj">Kodwa sizafika isikhathi lapho umyeni ezasuswa kuzo; zizazila ngalezonsuku.”</char><verse eid="LUK 5:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 5:36"/>Wabatshela umzekeliso lo: <char style="wj">“Kakho odabula isichibi esigqokweni esitsha asithungele esigqokweni esidala. Angenzenjalo, uzakuba esesidabule isigqoko esitsha, ikanti isichibi sesitsha kasiyikufanela esidala.</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 5:37"/><char style="wj">Njalo kakho othela iwayini elitsha emigodleni yezikhumba emidala. Angenza njalo iwayini elitsha lizaziqhekeza izikhumba iwayini livuze kuthi lemigodla yezikhumba leyo ihle yonakale.</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 5:38"/><char style="wj">Hatshi, iwayini elitsha lithelwa emigodleni yezikhumba emitsha.</char> <verse eid="LUK 5:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 5:39"/><char style="wj">Njalo kakho othi eseqale wanatha iwayini elidala afune elitsha, ngoba uthi, ‘Elidala lingcono.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 5:39"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="LUK 6"/>
  <para style="s1">INkosi YeSabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 6:1"/>Ngelinye iSabatha uJesu wayedabula emasimini alamabele, abafundi bakhe basebekhwebula izikhwebu zamabele, bakha bazihlikihlela ezandleni, badla inhlamvu zakhona. <verse eid="LUK 6:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 6:2"/>Abanye abaFarisi babuza bathi, “Kungani lisenza okungaphandle komthetho ngeSabatha na?”<verse eid="LUK 6:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 6:3"/>UJesu wabaphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kalifundanga yini okwenziwa nguDavida lapho yena labakhula bakhe sebelambile?</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 6:4"/><char style="wj">Wangena endlini kaNkulunkulu wathatha isinkwa esingcwelisiweyo wadla lokho umthetho owawusithi kudliwe ngabaphristi kuphela. Futhi okunye wakupha abakhula bakhe.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 6:5"/>UJesu wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“INdodana yoMuntu iyiNkosi yeSabatha.”</char><verse eid="LUK 6:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 6:6"/>Ngelinye iSabatha waya esinagogweni wafundisa, khonapho kulendoda elesandla sokudla esitshwabheneyo. <verse eid="LUK 6:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 6:7"/>AbaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho babedinga izaba lokubeka uJesu icala, yikho bamlinda ukubona ingabe wayezasilisa ngeSabatha. <verse eid="LUK 6:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 6:8"/>Kodwa uJesu wakwazi ababekucabanga, wasesithi endodeni yesandla esitshwabheneyo, <char style="wj">“Sukuma ume phambi kwabantu bonke.”</char> Lakanye yasukuma yema khonapho.<verse eid="LUK 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 6:9"/>UJesu wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngiyalibuza, kuyini okusemthethweni ngeSabatha: ukwenza okuhle loba ukwenza okubi, ukusindisa impilo kumbe ukuyibhubhisa?”</char><verse eid="LUK 6:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 6:10"/>Wabakhangela wababhoda bonke, wasesithi endodeni leyo, <char style="wj">“Yelula isandla sakho.”</char> Yenza njalo, isandla sayo sasiliswa ngokupheleleyo. <verse eid="LUK 6:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 6:11"/>Kodwa bazonda babheda basebecebisana ukuthi benzeni ngoJesu.<verse eid="LUK 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">AbaPostoli Abalitshumi Lambili</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 6:12"/>Ngelinye ilanga uJesu waphuma waya ewatheni lwentaba esiya khuleka, waba khonale ubusuku bonke ekhuleka kuNkulunkulu. <verse eid="LUK 6:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 6:13"/>Kwathi sokusile wasebiza abafundi bakhe wakhetha kubo abalitshumi lambili, wasebaphawula ngokuthi ngabapostoli:<verse eid="LUK 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 6:14"/>uSimoni (owambiza ngokuthi Phethro), lomfowabo u-Andreya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 6:14">uJakhobe,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 6:14">uJohane,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 6:14">uFiliphu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 6:14">uBhatholomewu,<verse eid="LUK 6:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 6:15"/>uMatewu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 6:15">uThomasi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 6:15">uJakhobe umfoka-Alifewu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 6:15">uSimoni owayethiwa ngumZilothi,<verse eid="LUK 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 6:16"/>uJudasi umfokaJakhobe</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="LUK 6:16">loJudasi Iskariyothi, owaba ngumthengisi.<verse eid="LUK 6:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izibusiso Lezixwayiso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 6:17"/>Wehla labo bema esigcawini. Kwakubuthene ixuku elikhulu elabafundi bakhe njalo kulabantu abanengi bevela kulolonke elaseJudiya, leJerusalema lasemakhunjini olwandle eThire leSidoni, <verse eid="LUK 6:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 6:18"/>ababeze ukuzamuzwa lokuzakwelatshwa izifo zabo. Labo ababehlutshwa yimimoya emibi basiliswa, <verse eid="LUK 6:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 6:19"/>bonke abantu bazama ukumthinta ngoba amandla ayephuma kuye ayebasilisa bonke.<verse eid="LUK 6:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 6:20"/>Wakhangela abafundi bakhe wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 6:20">
    <char style="wj">“Libusisiwe lina elimpofu,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:20">
    <char style="wj">ngoba umbuso kaNkulunkulu ngowenu.</char><verse eid="LUK 6:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 6:21"/>
    <char style="wj">Libusisiwe lina elilambileyo manje,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:21">
    <char style="wj">ngoba lizasuthiswa.</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 6:21">
    <char style="wj">Libusisiwe lina elililayo manje,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:21">
    <char style="wj">ngoba lizahleka.</char><verse eid="LUK 6:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 6:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Libusisiwe lina nxa abantu belizonda,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:22">
    <char style="wj">nxa belibandlulula njalo belichothoza,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:22">
    <char style="wj">bephika ibizo lenu besithi lingcolile,</char></para>
  <para style="q3" vid="LUK 6:22">
    <char style="wj">ngenxa yeNdodana yoMuntu.</char><verse eid="LUK 6:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 6:23"/>
    <char style="wj">Thokozani ngalolosuku liqolotshe ngokuthokoza ngoba mkhulu umvuzo wenu ezulwini. Ngoba yiyo indlela okhokho babo abaphatha ngayo abaphrofethi.</char><verse eid="LUK 6:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 6:24"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa maye kini lina elinothileyo,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:24">
    <char style="wj">ngoba livele selikwamukele ukuhlala kuhle kwenu.</char><verse eid="LUK 6:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 6:25"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini lina elidla kamnandi manje,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:25">
    <char style="wj">ngoba lizalamba.</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 6:25">
    <char style="wj">Maye kini lina elihlekayo manje,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:25">
    <char style="wj">ngoba lizakhala lilile.</char><verse eid="LUK 6:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 6:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini nxa bonke abantu belincoma,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:26">
    <char style="wj">ngoba yiyo indlela okhokho benu</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 6:26">
    <char style="wj">abaphatha ngayo abaphrofethi bamanga.”</char><verse eid="LUK 6:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthanda Izitha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 6:27"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kodwa ngiyalitshela lina elingizwayo, ngithi: Thandani izitha zenu, lenze okuhle kwabalizondayo,</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 6:28"/><char style="wj">libusise labo abaliqalekisayo, libakhulekele labo abalihlukuluzayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 6:29"/><char style="wj">Umuntu angakutshaya esihlathini, muphe esinye. Umuntu angakwemuka ijazi lakho ungamaleli ukuthatha leyembe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 6:30"/><char style="wj">Phanini loba ngubani ocela kini, njalo nxa umuntu ethatha ulutho lwakho ungaluthonisi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 6:31"/><char style="wj">Yenza kwabanye lokho ofuna ukuthi bakwenze kuwe.</char><verse eid="LUK 6:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 6:32"/>
    <char style="wj">Nxa lithanda labo abalithandayo kuphela, lizazuzani kulokho? Lezoni lazo ziyabathanda abazithandayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 6:33"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa lisenza okuhle kulabo abalungileyo kini, lizazuzani kulokho? Lezoni ziyakwenza lokho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 6:34"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa liseboleka labo elizazuza imbadalo kubo, lizazuzani kulokho? Lezoni ziboleka izoni zilindele ukubhadalwa ngokugcweleyo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 6:35"/><char style="wj">Kodwa thandani izitha zenu, lizenzele okuhle, njalo lizeboleke lingalindeli lutho kuzo. Lapho-ke umvuzo wenu uzakuba mkhulu, njalo lizakuba ngamadodana akhe oPhezukonke, ngoba ulomusa kwabangabongiyo labayizigangi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 6:36"/><char style="wj">Wobani lesihawu njengoYihlo olesihawu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 6:36"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwahlulela Abanye</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 6:37"/>
    <char style="wj">“Lingahluleli ukuze lani lingahlulelwa. Lingamlahli omunye ukuze lani lingalahlwa. Thethelelani ukuze lani lithethelelwe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 6:38"/><char style="wj">Phanini, lani lizaphiwa. Kuzathiwa qithi kini kugcwaliswe phamu, kwagqitshwa, kwakhuhluzwa kwaze kwaphuphuma. Ngoba ngesilinganiso elisisebenzisayo, lani lizalinganiselwa ngaso.”</char><verse eid="LUK 6:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 6:39"/>Waphinde wabatshela umzekeliso lo, <char style="wj">“Isiphofu kambe singakhokhela isiphofu na? Kazizukuwela emgodini zombili na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 6:40"/><char style="wj">Umfundi ungaphansi kombalisi wakhe, kodwa wonke osefundiswe ngokupheleleyo usenjengombalisi wakhe.</char><verse eid="LUK 6:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 6:41"/>
    <char style="wj">Kungani ukhangela uvava lokhuni oluselihlweni lomfowenu, unganqinekeli ukhuni olukwelakho ilihlo na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 6:42"/><char style="wj">Ungatsho kanjani kumfowenu ukuthi, ‘Mfowethu, wothi ngikukhuphe uvava oluselihlweni lakho,’ kodwa wena usehluleka ukubona ukhuni oluselihlweni lakho na? Wena mzenzisi, qala ukhuphe ukhuni oluselihlweni lakho ukuze ubone kuhle nxa usukhupha uvava oluselihlweni lomfowenu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 6:42"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isihlahla Lezithelo Zaso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 6:43"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kakulasihlahla esihle esithela izithelo ezimbi njalo lesihlahla esibi kasitheli izithelo ezinhle.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 6:44"/><char style="wj">Isihlahla sinye ngasinye saziwa ngezithelo zaso. Abantu kabakhi umkhiwa ezihlahleni zameva loba amagrebisi esingeni.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 6:45"/><char style="wj">Umuntu olungileyo uveza izinto ezinhle eziphuma kokuhle okugcinwe enhliziyweni yakhe, njalo lomuntu omubi uphihliza ububi obugcinwe enhliziyweni yakhe. Ngoba umlomo ukhuluma lokho okuphuphuma enhliziyweni.”</char><verse eid="LUK 6:45"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Omakhi Abahlakaniphileyo Labayiziwula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 6:46"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kungani lingibiza lisithi, ‘Nkosi, Nkosi,’ kodwa lingakwenzi engikutshoyo?</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 6:47"/><char style="wj">Lowo oza kimi ezwe amazwi ami akwenze akutshoyo, ngizalitshela ukuthi unjengani.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 6:48"/><char style="wj">Unjengendoda eyakha indlu, yagebha yatshona phansi, yasibeka isisekelo sayo phezu kwedwala. Kwathi kufika isikhukhula, isiphepho sayitshaya indlu, kodwa asaze sayizamazamisa, ngoba yayakhiwe kuhle.</char> <verse eid="LUK 6:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 6:49"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lowo owezwayo amazwi ami, kodwa angakwenzi akutshoyo, unjengomuntu owakha indlu emhlabathini kungelasisekelo. Umsinga wonela ukuyitshaya leyondlu, yabhidlika yaphela du.”</char><verse eid="LUK 6:49"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="LUK 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukholo Lwenduna Yekhulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 7:1"/>Kwathi uJesu eseqedile ukukhuluma konke lokhu abantu labo besizwa wayangena eKhaphenawume. <verse eid="LUK 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 7:2"/>Khonapho inceku yenduna yekhulu eyayiligugu kakhulu enkosini yayo, yayigula isibangwa lezibi. <verse eid="LUK 7:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 7:3"/>Induna yekhulu yezwa ngoJesu yathuma kuye abanye abadala bamaJuda icela ukuba eze azosilisa inceku yayo. <verse eid="LUK 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 7:4"/>Bafika kuJesu bamncenga kakhulu bathi, “Indoda le ifanele ukuthi uyenzele lokhu, <verse eid="LUK 7:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 7:5"/>ngoba iyasithanda isizwe sakithi njalo yiyo eyakha isinagogu yethu.” <verse eid="LUK 7:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 7:6"/>Ngakho uJesu wahamba labo.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 7:6">Wayengasekhatshana lendlu lapho induna yekhulu yathuma abangane bayo ukuyakuthi kuye, “Nkosi, ungazihluphi, akungifanelanga mina ukuthi ungene ngaphansi kophahla lwami. <verse eid="LUK 7:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 7:7"/>Yikho okwenze ngazibona ngingafanele ukuthi ngize kuwe. Kodwa tshono ilizwi nje inceku yami izasila. <verse eid="LUK 7:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 7:8"/>Ngoba mina ngokwami ngingumuntu ongaphansi komthetho, ngilamabutho angaphansi kwami. Lo ngimtshela ngithi, ‘Hamba,’ ahambe; ngithi kuloyana, ‘Buya,’ lakanye abuye. Ngithi encekwini yami, ‘Yenza lokhu,’ ikwenze.”<verse eid="LUK 7:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 7:9"/>UJesu wathi ekuzwa lokhu wamangala ngaye, wasephendukela exukwini labantu ababemlandela wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyalitshela, kangikaluboni ukholo olukhulu kangaka kanye lako-Israyeli.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 7:10"/>Abantu ababethunyiwe babuyela endlini bafica inceku isiziphilela.<verse eid="LUK 7:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uvusa Indodana Yomfelokazi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 7:11"/>Kungakabi yisikhathi eside ngemva kwalokhu, uJesu waya edolobheni okwakuthiwa yiNayini, abafundi bakhe kanye lexuku labantu elikhulu babehamba laye. <verse eid="LUK 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 7:12"/>Wathi esebanga entubeni yedolobho, khonapho umuntu ofileyo wayethwelwe ekhutshelwa ngaphandle. Indodana eyiyo yodwa kunina njalo unina engumfelokazi. Ixuku elikhulu labantu bedolobheni lalilaye. <verse eid="LUK 7:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 7:13"/>Kwathi uJesu embona umfelokazi, wamhawukela wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Ungakhali.”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 7:14"/>Wasesondela wathinta ithala elalilesidumbu, kwathi labo ababelithwele bema mpo. Wathi, <char style="wj">“Jaha, ngithi kuwe, vuka!”</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 7:15"/>Indoda efileyo yavuka yahlala, yasikhuluma, uJesu wayinika unina.<verse eid="LUK 7:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 7:16"/>Bonke bamangala kakhulu badumisa uNkulunkulu. Bathi, “Umphrofethi omkhulu usevelile phakathi kwethu. UNkulunkulu usefikile ukuzasiza abantu bakhe.” <verse eid="LUK 7:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 7:17"/>Udumo lukaJesu lwamemetheka kulolonke elaseJudiya lemangweni wakhona.<verse eid="LUK 7:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu LoJohane UMbhaphathizi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 7:18"/>Abafundi bakaJohane bamtshela ngazozonke lezizinto. Wabiza ababili babo <verse eid="LUK 7:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 7:19"/>wabathuma eNkosini ukuyabuza ukuthi, “Unguye yini ozayo, kumbe silindele omunye?”<verse eid="LUK 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 7:20"/>Amadoda lawo athi efika kuJesu athi, “UJohane uMbhaphathizi usithumile kuwe ukuthi sizobuza sithi, ‘Unguye yini ozayo kumbe silindele omunye’?”<verse eid="LUK 7:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 7:21"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJesu wasilisa abanengi ababelezifo, lemikhuhlane lemimoya emibi, wazivula amehlo iziphofu ezinengi. <verse eid="LUK 7:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 7:22"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Buyelani liyebikela uJohane lokhu elikubonayo lelikuzwayo ukuthi iziphofu zenziwa zibone, abaqhugezelayo bayahamba, abalobulephero bayahlanjululwa, izacuthe ziyezwa, abafileyo bayavuswa, levangeli liyatshunyayelwa kubayanga.</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 7:23"/><char style="wj">Ubusisiwe lowomuntu ongakhubekiyo ngenxa yami.”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 7:24"/>Sezihambile izithunywa zikaJohane uJesu waqala ukukhuluma labantu ngoJohane esithi: <char style="wj">“Laphuma lisiyabonani enkangala na? Umhlanga owazunguzwa ngumoya na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 7:25"/><char style="wj">Nxa kwakungenjalo, pho lalisiyabonani? Indoda eyayicecile na? Hatshi, labo abagqoka izigqoko ezidulayo bazitike ngezinto ezinhle basezigodlweni.</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 7:26"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kanti kuyini elaphuma lisiyakubona? Umphrofethi yini? Yebo, ngiyalitshela, omkhulu kulomphrofethi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 7:27"/><char style="wj">Lo nguye okulotshwe ngaye ukuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 7:27">
    <char style="wj">‘Ngizathuma isithunywa sami phambi kwakho,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 7:27">
    <char style="wj">esizalungisa indlela yakho phambi kwakho.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">7.27 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UMalaki 3.1</char>
    </note><verse eid="LUK 7:27"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 7:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela ukuthi kubo abazalwa ngabesifazane kakho omkhulu kuloJohane; ikanti lowo omncinyane kakhulu embusweni kaNkulunkulu mkhulu kulaye.”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 7:29"/>(Bonke abantu, kanye labathelisi, bathi sebewazwile amazwi kaJesu bavuma ukuthi indlela kaNkulunkulu yayilungile, ngoba babebhaphathizwe nguJohane. <verse eid="LUK 7:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 7:30"/>Kodwa abaFarisi lezazi zomthetho bayala injongo kaNkulunkulu ngabo, ngoba babengabhaphathizwanga nguJohane.)<verse eid="LUK 7:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 7:31"/>UJesu waqhubeka wathi, <char style="wj">“Pho ngingabafanisa lani abantu besizukulwane lesi? Bafanana lani?</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 7:32"/><char style="wj">Banjengabantwana behlezi emkambo bememeza abanye besithi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 7:32">
    <char style="wj">‘Salitshayela umhubhe,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 7:32">
    <char style="wj">kodwa kaligidanga,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 7:32">
    <char style="wj">salihlabelela ingoma yesililo,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 7:32">
    <char style="wj">kodwa kalililanga.’</char><verse eid="LUK 7:32"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 7:33"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngoba uJohane uMbhaphathizi weza engadli isinkwa njalo enganathi iwayini, lina lithi, ‘Uledimoni.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 7:34"/><char style="wj">INdodana yoMuntu yafika yadla, yanatha, laselisithi, ‘Nansi isidli lesidakwa, umngane wabathelisi lezoni.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 7:35"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ukuhlakanipha kuziveza ukuthi kuqondile ebantwaneni bakho bonke.”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:35"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ugcotshwa Ngumfazi Oyisoni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 7:36"/>Omunye wabaFarisi wanxusa uJesu ukuzakudla laye isidlo sakusihlwa, ngakho waya endlini yalowo mFarisi wahlala etafuleni. <verse eid="LUK 7:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 7:37"/>Kwathi owesifazane othile owayephila impilo yesono kulelodolobho esezwile ukuthi uJesu wayesidla endlini yomFarisi weza ephethe imbodlela yamakha, <verse eid="LUK 7:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 7:38"/>kwathi esemi ngemva kukaJesu ngasezinyaweni ekhala, wamanzisa inyawo zakhe ngezinyembezi. Wasezesula inyawo zikaJesu ngenwele zakhe, wazanga wasethela amakha kuzo.<verse eid="LUK 7:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 7:39"/>Kwathi lowomFarisi owayemnxusile ekubona lokho wazitshela wathi, “Aluba indoda le ibingumphrofethi, ibizakwazi ukuthi ngubani oyibambabambayo lokuthi umfazi lo uyisoni.”<verse eid="LUK 7:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 7:40"/>UJesu wamphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Simoni, kukhona engifuna ukukutshela khona.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 7:40">Wathi, “Ngitshela, mfundisi.”<verse eid="LUK 7:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 7:41"/>
    <char style="wj">“Amadoda amabili ayelesikwelede semali kumeboleki wemali. Oyedwa wayelesikwelede samadenari angamakhulu amahlanu, omunye esamatshumi amahlanu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 7:42"/><char style="wj">Bobabili babengelayo imali yokumbhadala, ngakho wasewesula umlandu wabo bobabili. Manje nguphi wabo ozamthanda okudlula omunye na?”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 7:43"/>USimoni waphendula wathi, “Ngibona kungathi ngulowo owesulelwa isikwelede esikhulu.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 7:43">UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Wahlulele kuhle.”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 7:44"/>Wasephendukela kowesifazane wathi kuSimoni, <char style="wj">“Uyambona na owesifazane lo? Ngifikile endlini yakho, kawungiphanga amanzi okugeza inyawo zami, kodwa yena uthambise inyawo zami ngezinyembezi zakhe, wazesula ngenwele zakhe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 7:45"/><char style="wj">Kawunganganga, kodwa owesifazane lo selokhu ngingenileyo lapha akemanga ukwanga inyawo zami.</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 7:46"/><char style="wj">Kawuthelanga amafutha ekhanda lami, kodwa yena uthele amakha ezinyaweni zami.</char> <verse eid="LUK 7:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 7:47"/><char style="wj">Yikho-ke ngiyakutshela ukuthi izono zakhe ezinengi sezithethelelwe, ngoba utshengise uthando olukhulu. Kodwa lowo othethelelwe okuncinyane uthanda kancinyane.”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 7:48"/>UJesu wasesithi kowesifazane, <char style="wj">“Izono zakho sezithethelelwe.”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 7:49"/>Ezinye izethekeli zasezibuzana zisithi, “Ungubani kanti yena lo oze athethelele izono na?”<verse eid="LUK 7:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 7:50"/>UJesu wasesithi kowesifazane, <char style="wj">“Ukukholwa kwakho kukusindisile; hamba ngokuthula.”</char><verse eid="LUK 7:50"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="LUK 8"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Womhlanyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 8:1"/>Ngemva kwalokho uJesu wahambahamba engena kuleli laleli idolobho lemizi, ememezela izindaba ezinhle zombuso kaNkulunkulu. Abalitshumi lambili babelaye, <verse eid="LUK 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 8:2"/>kanye labesifazane ababesiliswe emimoyeni emibi lemikhuhlaneni: uMariya (owayethiwa nguMagadalini) okwakuphume kuye amadimoni ayisikhombisa; <verse eid="LUK 8:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 8:3"/>uJowana umkaTshuza, umlawuli wendlu kaHerodi; uSusana labanye abanengi. Abesifazane laba babebasiza ngabakuswelayo.<verse eid="LUK 8:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 8:4"/>Kwathi sekubuthana ixuku labantu elikhulu labantu besiza kuJesu beqhamuka emadolobheni atshiyeneyo wabatshela lo umzekeliso: <verse eid="LUK 8:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 8:5"/><char style="wj">“Umlimi waphuma wayahlanyela. Wathi elokhu eyihaza inhlanyelo, eyinye yawela endleleni; yanyathelwa, izinyoni zemoyeni zayidobha.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 8:6"/><char style="wj">Eyinye yawela edwaleni, yathi isathi iyakhula yabuna ngoba yayingelabumanzi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 8:7"/><char style="wj">Eyinye inhlanyelo yawela phakathi kwameva, akhula kanye layo ayiminyezela.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 8:8"/><char style="wj">Eyinye inhlanyelo yawela emhlabathini ovundileyo. Yakhula yathela amabele, yanda ngekhulu.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 8:8">Wathi esetsho lokhu wamemeza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lowo olendlebe zokuzwa, kezwe.”</char><verse eid="LUK 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 8:9"/>Abafundi bakhe bambuza ukuthi umzekeliso lowo wawusitshoni. <verse eid="LUK 8:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 8:10"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Ulwazi lwemfihlo yombuso kaNkulunkulu seluphiwe lina, kodwa kwabanye ngikhuluma kubo ngemizekeliso, ukuze kuthi,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 8:10">
    <char style="wj">‘loba bekhangele, bangaboni;</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 8:10">
    <char style="wj">loba besizwa, bengaqedisisi.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">8.10 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 6.9</char>
    </note><verse eid="LUK 8:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 8:11"/>
    <char style="wj">Nansi ingcazelo yomzekeliso: Inhlanyelo iyilizwi likaNkulunkulu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 8:12"/><char style="wj">Labo abasendleleni ngabalizwayo, kodwa uSathane eze alihluthune ilizwi ezinhliziyweni zabo, ukuze bangakholwa basindiswe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 8:13"/><char style="wj">Labo abasokhetheni ngabemukela ilizwi ngentokozo nxa belizwa, kodwa kabalampande. Bayakholwa okwesikhatshana, kodwa kuthi ngesikhathi sobunzima bawe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 8:14"/><char style="wj">Inhlanyelo eyawela emeveni imele labo abezwayo, kodwa baqhubeke ngeyabo indlela bakhanywe yizinhlupheko zempilo, inotho kanye lezikholisisayo, bangabe besakhula baphelele.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 8:15"/><char style="wj">Kodwa inhlanyelo esemhlabathini ovundileyo imele labo abalenhliziyo enhle, elungileyo, abalizwayo ilizwi, baligcine bathi ngokubambelela bathele izithelo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 8:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isibane Phezu Kwesiqobane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 8:16"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kakho olumathisa isibane asifihle ngaphansi kwesitsha kumbe asibeke ngaphansi kombheda. Kodwa usibeka esiqobaneni ukuze labo abangenayo babone ukukhanya.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 8:17"/><char style="wj">Ngoba kakukho okufihliweyo okungayi kudazululwa, njalo akukho okuthukuziweyo okungayikwaziwa kumbe kuvezwe obala.</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 8:18"/><char style="wj">Ngakho nanzelelani ukuthi lilalela kanjani. Lowo olakho uzakwengezelelwa; lowo ongelakho lalokho athi ulakho uzakwemukwa.”</char><verse eid="LUK 8:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Unina KaJesu Labafowabo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 8:19"/>Unina kaJesu labafowabo beza ukuzambona, kodwa behluleka ukufinyelela kuye ngenxa yokuminyana kwabantu. <verse eid="LUK 8:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 8:20"/>Omunye wamtshela wathi, “Unyoko labafowenu bakulindele phandle, bafuna ukukubona.”<verse eid="LUK 8:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 8:21"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Umama labafowethu yilabo abalizwayo ilizwi likaNkulunkulu balenze.”</char><verse eid="LUK 8:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uthulisa Isiphepho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 8:22"/>Ngelinye ilanga uJesu wathi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Kasiyeni ngaphetsheya kwechibi.”</char> Basebengena esikepeni bahamba. <verse eid="LUK 8:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 8:23"/>Bathe belokhu behamba yena walala. Kwafika isiphepho echibini isikepe saqalisa ukugalula, baba sengozini embi.<verse eid="LUK 8:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 8:24"/>Abafundi bahamba bayamvusa besithi, “Nkosi, Nkosi, sesigalula bo!”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 8:24">Wavuka wawukhuza umoya kanye lamagagasi; isiphepho sadeda, kwasekuthula cwaka. <verse eid="LUK 8:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 8:25"/>Wababuza abafundi bakhe, wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungaphi ukukholwa kwenu?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 8:25">Babuzana ngokumangala lokwesaba bathi, “Kanti ungubani lo? Ukhuza kanye lomoya lamanzi kumlalele.”<verse eid="LUK 8:25"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukusiliswa Kwendoda Ephethwe Lidimoni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 8:26"/>Bagwedla isikepe baya emangweni wamaGerazini, okungaphetsheya kwechibi kusuka eGalile. <verse eid="LUK 8:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 8:27"/>Kwathi uJesu esehla okhunjini wahlangabezwa yindoda eyayiledimoni iqhamuka ngasedolobheni. Indoda le yayisilesikhathi eside ingavunuli zigqoko, ingahlali endlini, kodwa ihlala emathuneni. <verse eid="LUK 8:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 8:28"/>Yathi ibona uJesu yahlaba umkhosi yazilahla ezinyaweni zakhe iklabalala ngelizwi elikhulu isithi, “Ufuna ukungenzani, Jesu, Ndodana kaNkulunkulu oPhezukonke? Ngiyakuncenga, ungaze wangihlukuluza!” <verse eid="LUK 8:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 8:29"/>Ngoba uJesu wayeseyale umoya omubi ukuthi uphume kuleyondoda. Izikhathi ezinengi wawumbamba, kuthi loba ebotshwe ngamaketane ezandleni lezinyaweni njalo elindiwe, wayewaqamula amaketane idimoni limuse enkangala.<verse eid="LUK 8:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 8:30"/>UJesu wambuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ungubani ibizo lakho?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 8:30">Waphendula wathi, “NginguLigiyoni,” ngoba amadimoni amanengi ayengene kuye. <verse eid="LUK 8:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 8:31"/>Amncenga ukuthi angawalayi ukuthi ayewolokohlela emgodini ongelamkhawulo.<verse eid="LUK 8:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 8:32"/>Umhlambi omkhulu wengulube wawusidla khonapho eceleni koqaqa. Amadimoni amncenga uJesu ukuthi awavumele ukuyangena engulubeni, laye wawavumela. <verse eid="LUK 8:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 8:33"/>Amadimoni aphuma endodeni ayangena ezingulubeni, umhlambi wathi zimu usehlela eliweni lodonga wangena echibini wagalula.<verse eid="LUK 8:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 8:34"/>Labo ababezelusile bonela ukubona okwasekwenzakele babaleka bayabika edolobheni lemangweni wakhona, <verse eid="LUK 8:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 8:35"/>abantu basebeqonda khonale ukuyabona okwasekwenzakele. Bathi befika kuJesu bayifumana indoda okwakukhutshwe kuyo amadimoni ihlezi ezinyaweni zikaJesu, igqokile njalo ingqondo isibuyile; besaba kakhulu. <verse eid="LUK 8:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 8:36"/>Labo ababebonile kusenzakala batshela abantu ukuthi indoda eyayiphethwe lidimoni yasiliswa njani. <verse eid="LUK 8:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 8:37"/>Kwasekusithi bonke abantu bomango wamaGerazini bamcela uJesu ukuthi kasuke kubo ngoba babekhulelwa yikwesaba. Ngakho wangena esikepeni wahamba.<verse eid="LUK 8:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 8:38"/>Indoda leyo eyakhutshwa amadimoni yamncenga ukuthi ahambe layo, kodwa uJesu wala wathi, <verse eid="LUK 8:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 8:39"/><char style="wj">“Buyela ekhaya uyefakaza ukuthi uNkulunkulu ukwenzeleni.”</char> Yikho indoda yahamba yafakaza kulolonke idolobho konke uJesu ayeyenzele khona.<verse eid="LUK 8:39"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Intombazana Efileyo Lowesifazane Ogulayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 8:40"/>Kwathi uJesu esebuyile wahlangabezwa lixuku labantu elikhulu, ngoba bonke babemlindele. <verse eid="LUK 8:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 8:41"/>Indoda eyayithiwa nguJayirosi, umbusi wesinagogu, yeza yazilahla ezinyaweni zikaJesu, imncenga ukuthi eze endlini yayo <verse eid="LUK 8:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 8:42"/>ngoba indodakazi yayo eyodwa zwi, intombazana eyayileminyaka elitshumi lambili, yayisifa.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 8:42">Kwathi uJesu esesiya khona abantu baminyezela ingathi bazampatshaza. <verse eid="LUK 8:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 8:43"/>Khonapho kwakulowesifazane owayeseleminyaka elitshumi lambili esopha kodwa kungekho owayengamelapha. <verse eid="LUK 8:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 8:44"/>Weza ngemva kukaJesu wathinta umphetho wesembatho sakhe, masinyane nje ukopha kwahle kwaphela.<verse eid="LUK 8:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 8:45"/>UJesu wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngubani ongithintileyo?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 8:45">Kwathi ngoba bonke bephika uPhethro wathi, “Nkosi, abantu bayaminyezelana besondela kuwe.”<verse eid="LUK 8:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 8:46"/>Kodwa uJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Ukhona ongithintileyo; ngiyazi ukuthi amandla aphumile kimi.”</char><verse eid="LUK 8:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 8:47"/>Owesifazane esebone ukuthi uzacina eboniwe weza ethuthumela wazilahla ezinyaweni zakhe. Wachaza phambi kwabantu bonke ukuthi kungani wayemthintile uJesu lokuthi wasiliswa njani masinyane. <verse eid="LUK 8:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 8:48"/>UJesu wasesithi kuye, <char style="wj">“Ndodakazi, ukholo lwakho lukusilisile. Hamba ngokuthula.”</char><verse eid="LUK 8:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 8:49"/>Kwathi uJesu elokhu esakhuluma omunye weza evela endlini kaJayirasi umphathi wesinagogu, wafika wathi, “Indodakazi yakho isifile. Ungabe usamhlupha umfundisi.”<verse eid="LUK 8:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 8:50"/>UJesu wathi ekuzwa lokhu wathi kuJayirasi, <char style="wj">“Ungesabi, kholwa nje kuphela, izasiliswa.”</char><verse eid="LUK 8:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 8:51"/>Wathi esefikile endlini kaJayirasi, kavumelanga muntu ukuthi angene laye ngaphandle kukaPhethro, uJohane loJakhobe, kanye loyise womntwana lonina. <verse eid="LUK 8:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 8:52"/>Ngalesosikhathi abantu bonke babeqhinqa isililo bekhalela intombazana. UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Thulani, lingakhali. Kafanga kodwa ulele.”</char><verse eid="LUK 8:52"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="LUK 8:53"/>Bamhleka usulu uJesu ngoba besazi ukuthi intombazana yayisifile. <verse eid="LUK 8:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="LUK 8:54"/>Kodwa wayibamba ngesandla wathi, <char style="wj">“Mntanami, vuka!”</char> <verse eid="LUK 8:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="LUK 8:55"/>Umoya wayo wabuya, masinyane yasukuma yathi lothu! UJesu wasesithi kabamnike ukudla. <verse eid="LUK 8:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="LUK 8:56"/>Abazali bakhe bamangala, kodwa wabalaya ukuthi bangatsheli muntu ngalokho okwakwenzakele.<verse eid="LUK 8:56"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="LUK 9"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uthuma Abalitshumi Lambili</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 9:1"/>UJesu wabizela ndawonye abalitshumi lambili wabapha amandla lemvumo yokuthi baxotshe wonke amadimoni, belaphe lemikhuhlane, <verse eid="LUK 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 9:2"/>njalo wasebathuma ukuyatshumayela umbuso kaNkulunkulu lokuphilisa abagulayo, <verse eid="LUK 9:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 9:3"/>Wabatshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Lingathwali lutho kuloluhambo, loba udondolo, isikhwama, loba isinkwa, imali loba isigqoko sokuntshintsha.</char> <verse eid="LUK 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 9:4"/><char style="wj">Loba yiphi indlu elingena kuyo, hlalani kuyo lize lisuke kulelodolobho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 9:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 9:5"/><char style="wj">Nxa abantu bengalemukeli, sukani kulelodolobho lithintithe uthuli ezinyaweni zenu, kube yibufakazi bokubalahla.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 9:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 9:6"/>Basebesuka bangena imizi ngemizi, betshumayela ivangeli njalo besilisa abantu ezindaweni zonke.<verse eid="LUK 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 9:7"/>Ngalesosikhathi uHerodi umbusi wakuzwa konke lokho okwakusenzakala. Wakhathazeka kakhulu ngoba abanye babesithi uJohane wayesevusiwe kwabafileyo, <verse eid="LUK 9:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 9:8"/>abanye labo bathi u-Elija wayebonakele, kanti abanye njalo bathi omunye wabaphrofethi bekadeni wayesevukile waphila. <verse eid="LUK 9:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 9:9"/>Kodwa uHerodi wathi, “UJohane ngamquma ikhanda. Pho ungubani-ke lo engizwa izinto ezinje ngaye?” Wazama ukuthi ambone.<verse eid="LUK 9:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Unika Abantu Abazinkulungwane Ezinhlanu Ukudla</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 9:10"/>Abapostoli sebebuyile babika kuJesu ngakho konke ababekwenzile. Wasebathatha waya labo edolobheni elalithiwa yiBhethisayida beyibo bodwa, <verse eid="LUK 9:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 9:11"/>kodwa amaxuku abantu ezwa ukuthi ukhonale basebemlandela. Wabemukela wabatshela ngombuso kaNkulunkulu, wasilisa labo ababekuswela ukusiliswa.<verse eid="LUK 9:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 9:12"/>Emini abalitshumi lambili beza kuye bathi, “Wothi abantu bahambe ukuze baye emadolobheni lasemizini bayezidingela ukudla lezindawo zokulala ngoba lapha sisendaweni ekhatshana eyisikhala.”<verse eid="LUK 9:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 9:13"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Bapheni lina ukudla.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 9:13">Baphendula bathi, “Thina silezinkwa ezinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili kuphela, ngaphandle kokuthi sihambe siyothenga ukudla kwabantu bonke laba.” <verse eid="LUK 9:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 9:14"/>(Kwakulamadoda angaba zinkulungwane ezinhlanu khonapho.)</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 9:14">Kodwa wathi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Bahlaliseni phansi ngamaxuku abantu abangamatshumi amahlanu ngalinye.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 9:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 9:15"/>Benza njalo abafundi, wonke umuntu wahlala phansi. <verse eid="LUK 9:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 9:16"/>Ethatha izinkwa ezinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili wakhangela ezulwini, wabonga wazihlephula. Waseziqhubela abafundi ukuba bazabele abantu. <verse eid="LUK 9:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 9:17"/>Bonke badla basutha, abafundi basebebutha bagcwalisa izitsha ezilitshumi lambili imvuthu ezasalayo.<verse eid="LUK 9:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro Uvuma Ukuthi UJesu NguKhristu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 9:18"/>Ngesinye isikhathi uJesu wathi ekhuleka ekusithekeni, abafundi bakhe belaye, wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kanti abantu abanengi bathi ngingubani na?”</char><verse eid="LUK 9:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 9:19"/>Baphendula bathi, “Abanye bathi unguJohane uMbhaphathizi; abanye bathi ungu-Elija; kuthi abanye njalo bathi ungomunye wabaphrofethi bekadeni osephila njalo.”<verse eid="LUK 9:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 9:20"/>Wabuza bona wathi, <char style="wj">“Pho lina-ke? Lithi ngingubani?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 9:20">Waphendula uPhethro wathi, “UnguKhristu kaNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="LUK 9:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhuluma Ngokufa Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 9:21"/>UJesu wabaqonqosela ukuthi lokhu bangakutsheli muntu. <verse eid="LUK 9:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 9:22"/>Wasesithi, <char style="wj">“iNdodana yoMuntu kumele ihlupheke kakhulu, yaliwe ngabadala bebandla, abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho, njalo lokuthi kumele ibulawe, kuthi ngelanga lesithathu ivuswe kwabafileyo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 9:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 9:23"/>Wasesithi kubo bonke: <char style="wj">“Nxa ekhona ofisa ukungilandela kufanele azidele athwale isiphambano sakhe insuku zonke angilandele.</char> <verse eid="LUK 9:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 9:24"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lowo ofisa ukulondoloza impilo yakhe izamlahlekela, kodwa lowo olahlekelwa yimpilo yakhe ngenxa yami uzayiphephisa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 9:25"/><char style="wj">Kumsizani umuntu ukuzuza wonke umhlaba, kodwa alahlekelwe loba ancitshwe ubunguye bakhe na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 9:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 9:26"/><char style="wj">Lowo oyangeka ngami kanye lamazwi ami, iNdodana yoMuntu izayangeka ngaye nxa isifikile ngenkazimulo yayo langenkazimulo kaYise lezingilosi ezingcwele.</char><verse eid="LUK 9:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 9:27"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ngithi abanye abemi khonapha kabayikukuzwa ukufa bengakawuboni umbuso kaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 9:27"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhazimuliswa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 9:28"/>Emva kwensuku eziyisificaminwembili uJesu ekukhulumile lokho, wathatha uPhethro loJohane loJakhobe waya entabeni ukuyakhuleka. <verse eid="LUK 9:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 9:29"/>Wathi ekhuleka isimo sobuso bakhe saguquka lezigqoko zakhe zakhazimula njengokuphazima kombane. <verse eid="LUK 9:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 9:30"/>Amadoda amabili, uMosi lo-Elija, <verse eid="LUK 9:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 9:31"/>abonakala ecwebezela ngenkazimulo, ekhuluma loJesu. Babekhuluma ngokufa kwakhe okwasekusondele ukuthi kugcwaliseke eJerusalema. <verse eid="LUK 9:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 9:32"/>UPhethro labakhula bakhe babe lobuthongo kakhulu, kodwa sebephapheme, bayibona inkazimulo yakhe lamadoda amabili ayemi laye. <verse eid="LUK 9:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 9:33"/>Kwathi amadoda lawo esesuka kuJesu uPhethro wathi kuye, “Nkosi, kumnandi kithi ukuba lapha. Kasakhe izihonqo ezintathu, esakho, esinye esikaMosi lesinye esika-Elija.” (Wayengakwazi lokho ayekutsho.)<verse eid="LUK 9:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 9:34"/>Wathi esakhuluma, iyezi labuya labagubuzela, baba lokwesaba ekungeneni kwabo eyezini. <verse eid="LUK 9:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 9:35"/>Ilizwi labuya livela eyezini lisithi, “Le yiNdodana yami engiyikhethileyo; ilaleleni.” <verse eid="LUK 9:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 9:36"/>Ilizwi selikhulumile, uJesu bambona eseyedwa. Abafundi bakugcina ezifubeni zabo lokhu kabaze batshela muntu ngalesosikhathi ngababekubonile.<verse eid="LUK 9:36"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukusiliswa Komfana Owayelomoya Omubi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 9:37"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo sebehlile entabeni, wahlangabezwa lixuku labantu abanengi. <verse eid="LUK 9:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 9:38"/>Enye indoda exukwini yamemeza yathi, “Mfundisi, ngiyakuncenga, khangela indodana yami yiyo yodwa umntwana engilaye. <verse eid="LUK 9:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 9:39"/>Umoya uyamjuma abeseklabalala; uyamgiqa abhinqike abuye abhubhudle amagwebu emlonyeni. Usuhlezi udlala ngaye nje usufuna ukumbulala. <verse eid="LUK 9:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 9:40"/>Bengicele abafundi bakho ukuthi bawuxotshe, kodwa behlulekile.”<verse eid="LUK 9:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 9:41"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Oh, sizukulwane esingakholwayo, esixhwalileyo, ngihlale lani kuze kube nini ngilokhu ngilibekezelela na? Ilethe lapha indodana yakho.”</char><verse eid="LUK 9:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 9:42"/>Kwathi lapho umfana elokhu esalethwa kuye idimoni lambhuqa phansi ebhinqika. Kodwa uJesu wawukhuza umoya omubi, wamsilisa umfana wambuyisela kuyise. <verse eid="LUK 9:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 9:43"/>Bonke bamangala kakhulu ngobukhulu bukaNkulunkulu.</para>
  <para style="s1" vid="LUK 9:43">UJesu Ukhuluma Okwesibili Ngokufa Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 9:43">Kwathi wonke umuntu esamangele ngalokho uJesu ayekwenzile, wathi kubafundi bakhe, <verse eid="LUK 9:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 9:44"/><char style="wj">“Likulalele kuhle lokhu esengizalitshela khona: Indodana yoMuntu izanikelwa ezandleni zabantu.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 9:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 9:45"/>Kodwa kabezwisisanga ukuthi lokhu kwakusitshoni. Kwakufihliwe kubo, yikho kabakubambisisanga, kodwa besaba ukumbuza ngakho.<verse eid="LUK 9:45"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ngubani Ozabamkhulu Kulabanye?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 9:46"/>Kwaba lokuphikisana kubafundi ngokuthi ngubani kubo owayezabamkhulu kulabanye. <verse eid="LUK 9:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 9:47"/>UJesu eyazi imicabango yabo wathatha umntwana omncinyane wamisa eceleni kwakhe. <verse eid="LUK 9:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 9:48"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lowo owamukela lo umntwana omncane ngebizo lami wamukela mina, lalowo owamukela mina wamukela lowo ongithumileyo. Ngoba lowo onguye omncinyane kulani lonke phakathi kwenu lonke, nguye omkhulu kini lonke.”</char><verse eid="LUK 9:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 9:49"/>UJohane wathi, “Nkosi, sibone indoda ikhupha amadimoni ngebizo lakho sazama ukuyenqaba ngoba ingayisuye omunye wethu.”<verse eid="LUK 9:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 9:50"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Lingamaleli ngoba lowo ongamelani lani ukanye lani.</char>”<verse eid="LUK 9:50"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwaliwa ESamariya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 9:51"/>Kwathi isikhathi sesisondele ukuthi athathwe aye ezulwini, uJesu wazimisela ukuthi aye eJerusalema. <verse eid="LUK 9:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 9:52"/>Wasethuma izithunywa phambi kwakhe zaya eSamariya emzini othile ukumlungisela ukufika kwakhe; <verse eid="LUK 9:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="LUK 9:53"/>kodwa abantu bakhona kabamemukelanga ngoba wayesedlulela eJerusalema. <verse eid="LUK 9:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="LUK 9:54"/>Kwathi abafundi uJakhobe loJohane bekubona lokho bathi, “Nkosi, uyafuna na ukuthi sibize umlilo uvele ezulwini uzobabhubhisa?” <verse eid="LUK 9:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="LUK 9:55"/>Kodwa uJesu waphenduka wabakhuza <verse eid="LUK 9:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="LUK 9:56"/>Yikho yena labafundi bakhe basebesiya komunye umuzi.<verse eid="LUK 9:56"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ubunzima Bokulandela UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="LUK 9:57"/>Bathi belokhu behamba endleleni, enye indoda yathi kuye, “Ngizakulandela loba ungaze uye ngaphi.”<verse eid="LUK 9:57"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="58" style="v" sid="LUK 9:58"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Amakhanka alemilindi lezinyoni zemoyeni zilezidleke, kodwa iNdodana yoMuntu kayilandawo yokufihla ikhanda layo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 9:58"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="59" style="v" sid="LUK 9:59"/>Wathi kwenye indoda, <char style="wj">“Ngilandela.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 9:59">Kodwa indoda yaphendula yathi, “Nkosi, akuthi ngiqale ngihambe ngiyengcwaba ubaba wami.”<verse eid="LUK 9:59"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="60" style="v" sid="LUK 9:60"/>UJesu wathi kuyo, <char style="wj">“Yekela abafileyo bangcwabe abafileyo babo, kodwa wena hamba uyememezela umbuso kaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 9:60"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="61" style="v" sid="LUK 9:61"/>Kwathi omunye njalo wathi, “Ngizakulandela, Nkosi, kodwa akuthi kengiyevalelisa abakithi.”<verse eid="LUK 9:61"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v" sid="LUK 9:62"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kakho othi angabamba ikhuba elima athalaze emuva owufaneleyo umsebenzi oqondane lombuso kaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 9:62"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="LUK 10"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uthumela Abangamatshumi Ayisikhombisa Lambili</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 10:1"/>Ngemva kwalokhu iNkosi yakhetha abanye abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa lambili ukuba bamandulele baye kuwo wonke amadolobho lezindawo lezo ayesezazihambela. <verse eid="LUK 10:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 10:2"/>Wabatshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Isivuno sinengi, kodwa izisebenzi zimbalwa. Ngakho celani iNkosi yesivuno ukuthi ithumele izisebenzi ensimini yayo yokuvuna.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 10:3"/><char style="wj">Hambani! Ngilithuma linjengamazinyane ezimvu phakathi kwempisi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 10:4"/><char style="wj">Lingathwali isikhwama kumbe umxhaka loba amanyathela; njalo lingabingeleli muntu endleleni.</char><verse eid="LUK 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 10:5"/>
    <char style="wj">Nxa lingena endlini, qalani lithi, ‘Ukuthula akube kule indlu.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 10:6"/><char style="wj">Nxa kulomuntu woxolo lapho, ukuthula kwenu kakube kuye; nxa kungenjalo kuzabuyela kini.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 10:7"/><char style="wj">Hlalani kuleyondlu, lidle njalo linathe loba yini abalinika khona ngoba osebenzayo ufanele aphiwe iholo lakhe. Linganqumi ngezindlu lihlala lapha lalapha.</char><verse eid="LUK 10:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 10:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Nxa lifika edolobheni lamukelwe khona, dlanini lokho elikuphiwayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 10:9"/><char style="wj">Silisani abagulayo abayabe belapho, njalo libatshele ukuthi, ‘Umbuso kaNkulunkulu useduze kwenu.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 10:10"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa lingafika edolobheni lingemukelwa, yanini emigwaqweni yalo lithi,</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 10:11"/><char style="wj">‘Lalo uthuli lwedolobho lenu olunamathele ezinyaweni zethu siyaluthintithela kini. Kodwa yazini lokhu: Umbuso kaNkulunkulu ususeduze.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 10:12"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela, okweSodoma kuzakuba ngcono ngalelolanga kulokwalelodolobho.</char><verse eid="LUK 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 10:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kuwe Khorazini! Maye kuwe Bhethisayida! Aluba izimangaliso lezo ezenziwa kuwe zazenziwe eThire leSidoni ngabe kudala baphenduka begqoke izigqoko zamasaka bazithela ngomlotha.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 10:14"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kuzakuba ngcono okweThire leSidoni mhla wokwahlulela kulokuza kuwe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 10:15"/><char style="wj">Lawe, Khaphenawume, kambe uzaphakanyiselwa emazulwini na? Hatshi, uzatshona phansi uye eHadesi</char>.<verse eid="LUK 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 10:16"/>
    <char style="wj">Lowo olalela lina ulalela mina; lowo olahla lina ulahla mina; kodwa lowo ongalayo wala yena owangithumayo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 10:17"/>Abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa lambili babuya bethokoza bathi, “Nkosi, lamadimoni ayasithobela ngebizo lakho.”<verse eid="LUK 10:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 10:18"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngimbonile uSathane esiwa njengombane esuka ezulwini.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 10:19"/><char style="wj">Ngiliphile amandla okugxoba izinyoka lenkume lokunqoba wonke amandla esitha; kakukho okuzalilimaza.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 10:20"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lingathatshiswa yikuthi imimoya iyazithoba kini, kodwa thokoziswani yikuthi amabizo enu alotshiwe ezulwini.”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 10:21"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJesu egcwele intokozo ngoMoya oNgcwele wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyakudumisa, Baba, Nkosi yasezulwini lasemhlabeni, ngoba uzifihlile lezizinto kwabahlakaniphileyo labafundileyo wazambula ebantwaneni abancinyane. Yebo, Baba, ngoba lokhu kwakuyikuthanda kwakho okuhle.</char><verse eid="LUK 10:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 10:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Zonke izinto zethulwe kimi nguBaba. Kakho owaziyo ukuthi ingubani iNdodana ngaphandle kukaBaba, njalo kakho omaziyo uBaba ukuthi ungubani ngaphandle kweNdodana lalabo iNdodana ekhethe ukuba imveze kubo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 10:23"/>Wasephendukela kubafundi bakhe wathi kubo ngasese, <char style="wj">“Abusisiwe amehlo abona lokhu elikubonayo lina.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 10:24"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngiqinisile ukuthi abaphrofethi abanengi lamakhosi babefisa ukubona lokhu elikubonayo, kodwa kabakubonanga, lokuzwa lokhu elikuzwayo, kodwa kabakuzwanga.”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso WomSamariya Olesihawu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 10:25"/>Ngesinye isikhathi isazi somthetho saphakama samlinga uJesu. Sabuza sathi, “Mfundisi, ngingenzani ukuze ngizuze ilifa lempilo engapheliyo na?”<verse eid="LUK 10:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 10:26"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kubhalweni emthethweni, uwufunda njani?”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 10:27"/>Waphendula wathi, “ ‘Thanda iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho ngenhliziyo yakho yonke, langomphefumulo wakho wonke, langamandla akho wonke, njalo langengqondo yakho yonke’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.27 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 6.5</char></note>; njalo, ‘Thanda umakhelwane wakho njengoba uzithanda wena.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.27 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ULevi 19.18</char></note>”<verse eid="LUK 10:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 10:28"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Uphendule kuhle. Kwenze lokhu, uzaphila.”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 10:29"/>Kodwa wayefuna ukuzigeza, wasebuza kuJesu, wathi, “Kanti ngubani ongumakhelwana wami na?”<verse eid="LUK 10:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 10:30"/>UJesu waphendula ngokuthi: <char style="wj">“Indoda yayihamba iphuma eJerusalema isiya eJerikho, yaqabuka isihlaselwa ngabaphangi. Bayihlubula izigqoko zayo, bayitshaya basebehamba, beyitshiya iqalekile.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 10:31"/><char style="wj">Kwakulomphristi owayehamba ngaleyondlela, owathi eyibona indoda leyo waceza kwelinye icele.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 10:32"/><char style="wj">Wenza njalo lomLevi, wafika kuleyondawo wayibona indoda wakhekheleza wedlula.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 10:33"/><char style="wj">Kodwa umSamariya, wathi ezihambela wafika lapho indoda eyayikhona, wathi eyibona wayizwela usizi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 10:34"/><char style="wj">Waya kuyo, wabopha amanxeba ayo, wawathela amafutha lewayini. Waseyikhweza kubabhemi wakhe, wayisa endlini yezihambi, wayinakekela.</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 10:35"/><char style="wj">Ngosuku olulandelayo wakhupha inhlamvu ezimbili zamadenari wazinika umphathi wendawo. Wathi, ‘Mgcine, kuzakuthi nxa sengibuya ngizabhadala lezondleko eziyabe zisele.’</char><verse eid="LUK 10:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 10:36"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngubani pho kulaba abathathu ombona ukuthi wayengumakhelwane wendoda leyo eyahlaselwa ngabaphangi na?”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 10:37"/>Isazi somthetho saphendula sathi, “Ngulowo owaba lesihawu kuyo.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 10:37">UJesu wamtshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Hamba wenzenjalo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:37"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ekhaya LaboMatha LoMariya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 10:38"/>Kwathi uJesu labafundi bakhe besekuhambeni kwabo, wafika emzini okwakukhona owesifazane othiwa nguMatha, owamamukela ngesihle emzini wabo. <verse eid="LUK 10:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 10:39"/>Wayelodadewabo owayethiwa nguMariya, owahlala ezinyaweni zeNkosi elalele lokho eyayikukhuluma. <verse eid="LUK 10:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 10:40"/>Kodwa uMatha waphazanyiswa yikulungiselela konke okwakumele kwenziwe. Wabuya kuJesu wabuza wathi, “Nkosi, kawukhathali na ukuthi udadewethu ungitshiye ukuba ngenze ngedwa umsebenzi? Mtshele ukuthi angincedise!”<verse eid="LUK 10:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 10:41"/>INkosi yaphendula yathi, <char style="wj">“Matha, Matha, uhlutshwa njalo ukhathazeke ngezinto ezinengi,</char> <verse eid="LUK 10:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 10:42"/><char style="wj">kodwa kusweleka into eyodwa. UMariya ukhethe okungcono, okungasoze akwemukwe futhi.”</char><verse eid="LUK 10:42"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="LUK 11"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ufundisa Ukukhuleka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 11:1"/>Ngelinye ilanga uJesu wayekhuleka kwenye indawo. Wathi eseqedile, omunye wabafundi bakhe wathi kuye, “Nkosi, sifundise ukukhuleka, njengoJohane owafundisa abafundi bakhe.”<verse eid="LUK 11:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 11:2"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Nxa likhuleka, alibokuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 11:2">
    <char style="wj">‘Baba,</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">11.2 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">Eminye imibhalo ithi </char>
      <char style="fqa" closed="false">Baba wethu osezulwini</char>
    </note></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 11:2">
    <char style="wj">kalidunyiswe ibizo lakho,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 11:2">
    <char style="wj">umbuso wakho kawuze.</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">11.2 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">Eminye imibhalo ithi </char>
      <char style="fqa" closed="false">kawuze. </char>
      <char style="fqa" closed="false">Intando yakho kayenziwe emhlabeni njengasezulwini.</char>
    </note><verse eid="LUK 11:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 11:3"/>
    <char style="wj">Siphe ukudla kwethu kwansukuzonke usuku ngosuku.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 11:4"/>
    <char style="wj">Sithethelele izono zethu,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 11:4">
    <char style="wj">njengoba lathi sibathethelela bonke abasonelayo.</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 11:4">
    <char style="wj">Njalo ungasingenisi ekulingweni.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 11:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 11:5"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Akesithi omunye wenu ulomngane, aye kuye phakathi kobusuku athi, ‘Mfowethu, akungeboleke izinkwa ezintathu,</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 11:6"/><char style="wj">kulomngane wami ophakathi kohambo ozofihla ikhanda kwami, kodwa kangilalutho engingamupha lona.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 11:7"/><char style="wj">Besekusithi osendlini aphendule athi, ‘Ungangikhathazi. Umnyango usukhiyiwe njalo mina labantwabami sesilele. Ngingezake ngivuke ngikuphe loba yini.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 11:8"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela ukuthi loba ubengafuni ukuvuka amuphe isinkwa ngoba engumngane, kodwa ngenxa yokuphikelela kwendoda uzaze avuke amuphe konke akufunayo.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 11:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho ngithi kini: Celani lizaphiwa; dingani lizafumana; qoqodani lizavulelwa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 11:10"/><char style="wj">Ngoba wonke ocelayo uyaphiwa; lowo odingayo uyafumana; lalowo oqoqoda emnyango uzavulelwa.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 11:11"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngubani kini bobaba, okuthi nxa indodana yakhe icela inhlanzi yena ayiphe inyoka?</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 11:12"/><char style="wj">Loba icela iqanda ayiphe inkume na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 11:13"/><char style="wj">Nxa lina, elithi loba libabi likwazi ukupha abantwabenu izipho ezilungileyo, pho uYihlo osezulwini uzabapha ngokwengezwe kangakanani uMoya oNgcwele labo abacela kuye!”</char><verse eid="LUK 11:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu LoBhelizebhubhi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 11:14"/>UJesu wayexotsha idimoni elaliyisimungulu. Lathi idimoni seliphumile, indoda eyayiyisimungulu yakhuluma, ixuku labantu lamangala. <verse eid="LUK 11:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 11:15"/>Kodwa abanye bathi, “Ukhupha amadimoni ngoBhelizebhubhi inkosi yamadimoni.” <verse eid="LUK 11:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 11:16"/>Abanye bamlinga ngokumcela isibonakaliso esivela ezulwini.<verse eid="LUK 11:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 11:17"/>UJesu wayeyazi imicabango yabo wasesithi kubo: <char style="wj">“Umbuso ongabambananga uyadilika, lendlu engabambananga iyawa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 11:18"/><char style="wj">Nxa uSathane engabambananga, umbuso wakhe ungema kanjani na? Ngikutsho lokhu ngoba lithi mina ngikhupha amadimoni ngoBhelizebhubhi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 11:19"/><char style="wj">Nxa ngikhupha amadimoni ngoBhelizebhubhi, pho abalandeli benu bawakhupha ngobani? Ngakho, bazakuba ngabahluleli benu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 11:20"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa ngikhupha amadimoni ngomunwe kaNkulunkulu, kutsho ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu usufikile kini.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 11:21"/>
    <char style="wj">Nxa indoda eyisiqhwaga ihlome yaphelela, ilinde indlu yayo, impahla zayo zivikelekile.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 11:22"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kungahlasela umuntu olamandla kulayo ayehlule, uyayemuka izikhali ebikade izithembile, abesezehlukanisela impango.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 11:23"/>
    <char style="wj">Lowo ongemanga lami uphikisana lami, lalowo ongabuthi lami uyachithiza.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 11:24"/>
    <char style="wj">Lapho umoya omubi uphuma emuntwini, uyazula enkangala udinga ukuphumula, kodwa nxa ungakuswela, uyathi ‘Ngizabuyela endlini engaphuma kuyo.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 11:25"/><char style="wj">Uthi ufika, uthole leyondlu ithanyelwe yahlanzeka konke kumi kuhle.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 11:26"/><char style="wj">Ubusuhamba uyethatha eminye imimoya eyisikhombisa exhwale ukwedlula wona, ingene ihlale khona. Isiphetho salowomuntu sizakuba sibi kulasekuqaleni.”</char><verse eid="LUK 11:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 11:27"/>Kwathi uJesu elokhu esakhuluma lezizinto, owesifazane wamemeza exukwini wathi, “Ubusisiwe lowomama owakuzalayo wakondla.”<verse eid="LUK 11:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 11:28"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungenani, ababusisiweyo yilabo abalizwayo ilizwi likaNkulunkulu baliphile.”</char><verse eid="LUK 11:28"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isibonakaliso SikaJona</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 11:29"/>Kwathi amaxuku esanda uJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Lesi yisizukulwane esixhwalileyo. Sidinga isibonakaliso kodwa kasisoze sisiphiwe ngaphandle kwesibonakaliso sikaJona.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 11:30"/><char style="wj">NjengoJona owaba yisibonakaliso kwabaseNiniva, ngokunjalo iNdodana yoMuntu izakuba njalo kulesisizukulwane.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 11:31"/><char style="wj">INdlovukazi yaseNingizimu izavuka ekwahlulelweni kanye labantu balesi sizukulwane ibalahle ngoba yeza ivela emaphethelweni omhlaba izokuzwa inhlakanipho kaSolomoni kodwa manje lowo omkhulu kuloSolomoni usekhona lapha.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 11:32"/><char style="wj">Abantu baseNiniva bazasukuma kanye lalesi sizukulwane ngosuku lokwahlulelwa basilahle ngoba bona baphenduka ekutshumayeleni kukaJona, kodwa khathesi lowo omkhulu kuloJona uselapha.”</char><verse eid="LUK 11:32"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isibane Somzimba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 11:33"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kakho olumathisa isibane abesesibeka ekusithekeni kumbe ngaphansi kwesitsha. Kodwa usibeka esiqobaneni ukuze labo abangenayo babone ukukhanya.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 11:34"/><char style="wj">Ilihlo lakho liyisibane somzimba. Nxa amehlo akho elungile umzimba wakho wonke ugcwele ukukhanya. Kodwa nxa emabi, umzimba wakho lawo ugcwele ubumnyama.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 11:35"/><char style="wj">Qaphelani-ke ukuthi ukukhanya okuphakathi kwenu kakusibumnyama.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 11:36"/><char style="wj">Ngakho-ke, nxa umzimba wakho wonke ugcwele ukukhanya kungekho ingxenye esemnyameni, wonke uzagcwala ukukhanya njengokukhanya kwesibane kukukhanyisa.”</char><verse eid="LUK 11:36"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izixwayiso KubaFarisi Lezazi Zomthetho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 11:37"/>UJesu eseqedile ukukhuluma umFarisi othile wamnxusa ukuthi azokudla laye; wasehamba wayahlala etafuleni. <verse eid="LUK 11:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 11:38"/>Kodwa umFarisi wananzelela ukuthi uJesu kaqalanga ngokugeza engakadli, kwamangalisa.<verse eid="LUK 11:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 11:39"/>INkosi yathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Lina baFarisi ligezisa inkezo lomganu ngaphandle kodwa ngaphakathi ligcwele ubuhwaba lobubi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 11:40"/><char style="wj">Lina bantu abayiziwula! Lowo owenza ingaphandle kenzanga lengaphakathi na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 11:41"/><char style="wj">Ngakho-ke, mayelana lokungaphakathi kwenu, wobani lomusa kwabampofu, lapho-ke konke kuzabe sekuhlanzekile kini.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 11:42"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini baFarisi, ngoba lipha uNkulunkulu okwetshumi kweminti, lazozonke izithelo zesivande senu, kodwa lidele ukwenza okulungileyo kanye lokuthanda uNkulunkulu. Kumele likwenze konke okulungileyo, ukuthanda uNkulunkulu lokukhipha lokwetshumi.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 11:43"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini baFarisi, ngoba lithanda izihlalo eziqakathekileyo emasinagogweni njalo lithanda lokubingelelwa ezindaweni zokuthengisela.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 11:44"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini, ngoba linjengamathuna angakhelwanga, abantu abahamba phezu kwawo bengazi ukuthi akhona.”</char><verse eid="LUK 11:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 11:45"/>Omunye wezazi zomthetho wamphendula wathi, “Mfundisi, nxa usitsho njalo uyasithuka lathi.”<verse eid="LUK 11:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 11:46"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lani zazi zomthetho, maye kini, ngoba lethesa abantu ngemithwalo abangeke bayithwale, ikanti lani livele kalithi thika lokuyithwala.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 11:47"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini, ngoba lakha amathuna abaphrofethi, bona ababulawa ngokhokho benu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 11:48"/><char style="wj">Lifakaza ukuthi liyakuvuma lokho okhokho benu abakwenzayo; bababulala abaphrofethi, lina-ke selisakha amangcwaba abo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 11:49"/><char style="wj">Ngenxa yalokhu, uNkulunkulu wathi, ngokuhlakanipha kwakhe, ‘Ngizabathumela abaphrofethi labapostoli, abanye bazababulala abanye babaphathe ngochuku.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 11:50"/><char style="wj">Ngakho-ke, lesisizukulwana yiso esizathwala umlandu wegazi labaphrofethi bonke elachithwa kusukela ekudabukeni komhlaba,</char> <verse eid="LUK 11:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 11:51"/><char style="wj">kusukela egazini lika-Abheli kusiya egazini likaZakhariya owabulawa phakathi laphakathi kwe-alithari lendlu engcwele. Yebo, ngiyalitshela, isizukulwane lesi sizakwetheswa umlandu wakho konke.</char><verse eid="LUK 11:51"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 11:52"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini zazi zomthetho, ngoba seliyivalile intuba yolwazi. Lina ngokwenu kalingenanga, laphinda lavimbela labo abebefuna ukungena.”</char><verse eid="LUK 11:52"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="LUK 11:53"/>UJesu wathi esesuka lapho, abaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho baqala ukuphikisana laye kubi, bemthela ngemibuzo, <verse eid="LUK 11:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="LUK 11:54"/>bezama ukumgcona ngokunye ayengakutsho.<verse eid="LUK 11:54"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="LUK 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Izixwayiso Lenkuthazo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 12:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi sekubuthene ixuku lezinkulungwane zabantu, sebenyathelana, uJesu waqala ukukhuluma kubafundi bakhe esithi, <char style="wj">“Qaphelani imvubelo yabaFarisi, iyikuzenzisa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 12:2"/><char style="wj">Kakukho okufihliweyo okungayi kuvezwa obala, lokufihliweyo okungayikwaziwa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 12:3"/><char style="wj">Lokho okukhulume emnyameni kuzazwakala emini lithe bha, lalokho obukunyenyezela endlebeni ezindlini zangaphakathi kuzamenyezelwa phezu kophahla lwezindlu.</char><verse eid="LUK 12:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 12:4"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela bangane, lingabesabi labo ababulala umzimba kungabikhona okunye abangakwenza ngemva kwalokho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 12:5"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngizalitshengisa lowo okumele limesabe: Mesabeni lowo, othi esebulele umzimba, abe lamandla okuwuphosela esihogweni. Yebo, ngithi mesabeni.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 12:6"/><char style="wj">Intaka ezinhlanu kazithengiswa ngendibilitshi ezimbili na? Kodwa kayikho lanye yazo uNkulunkulu ayilibalayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 12:7"/><char style="wj">Ngempela, inwele zekhanda lakho zibaliwe. Lingesabi; lina liligugu ukwedlula intaka ezinengi.</char><verse eid="LUK 12:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 12:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela, lowo ongivuma phambi kwabantu, iNdodana yoMuntu layo izamvuma phambi kwezingilosi zikaNkulunkulu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 12:9"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lowo ongiphikayo phambi kwabantu uzaphikwa phambi kwezingilosi zikaNkulunkulu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 12:10"/><char style="wj">Njalo wonke umuntu okhuluma okubi ngeNdodana yoMuntu uzathethelelwa kodwa lowo ohlambaza uMoya oNgcwele akayikuthethelelwa.</char><verse eid="LUK 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 12:11"/>
    <char style="wj">Nxa limiswa phambi kwamasinagogu, phambi kwababusi labaphathi, lingazihluphi ngokuthi lizazivikela lisithini kumbe ukuthi lizakuthini,</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 12:12"/><char style="wj">ngoba uMoya oNgcwele uzalifundisa ngalesosikhathi lokho elifanele likutsho.”</char><verse eid="LUK 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wesinothi Esiyisiwula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 12:13"/>Omunye emphakathini wathi kuye, “Mfundisi, tshela umfowethu ukuthi angabele ilifa lami.”<verse eid="LUK 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 12:14"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ndoda, ngibekwe ngubani ukuba ngumahluleli kumbe umlamuli wenu?”</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 12:15"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Qaphelani! Limukani inhlobo zonke zobuhaga; isiqokoqela sempilo yomuntu kasikho ebunengini benotho yakhe.”</char><verse eid="LUK 12:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 12:16"/>Wasebatshela umzekeliso wathi, <char style="wj">“Insimu yenye indoda eyayinothile yaba lenala eyesabekayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 12:17"/><char style="wj">Yasinakana yathi, ‘Kambe ngenzeni? Angilandawo yokubeka amabele ami.’</char><verse eid="LUK 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 12:18"/>
    <char style="wj">Yasisithi, ‘Nanku engizakwenza. Ngizazidiliza iziphala zami ngakhe ezinkulu kulalezi, besengithela khona wonke amabele ami kanye lezinye impahla zami.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 12:19"/><char style="wj">Ngizazitshela ngithi, “Usulezinto ezinengi ezinhle njalo ezizakwanela iminyaka eminengi. Kholisa impilo, udle, unathe uthokoze.” ’</char><verse eid="LUK 12:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 12:20"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa uNkulunkulu wathi kuye, ‘Wena siwula ndini! Ngalobubusuku impilo yakho izathathwa. Pho ngubani ozazuza lokhu obusuzilungisele khona na?’</char><verse eid="LUK 12:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 12:21"/>
    <char style="wj">Yikho lokhu okuzakwenzeka kulowo ozibekela inotho kodwa enganothanga kuNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 12:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Lingakhathazeki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 12:22"/>UJesu wasesithi kubafundi bakhe: <char style="wj">“Ngakho ngilitshela ukuthi lingakhathazeki ngokuphila kwenu, ukuthi lizakudlani kumbe ngomzimba wenu, ukuthi lizagqokani.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 12:23"/><char style="wj">Impilo iyakudlula ukudla, lomzimba uyazedlula izembatho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 12:24"/><char style="wj">Khumbulani amawabayi, kawahlanyeli, kawavuni, kawalaso isiphala kodwa uNkulunkulu uyawapha ukudla. Manje lina liqakatheke okwedlula izinyoni!</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 12:25"/><char style="wj">Ngubani kini othi ngokukhathazeka angezelele ihola elilodwa empilweni yakhe na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 12:26"/><char style="wj">Njengoba lingeke liyenze linto encinyane kangaka, lizihluphelani na ngokunengi?</char><verse eid="LUK 12:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 12:27"/>
    <char style="wj">Ake libone ukuthi amaluba eganga akhula njani. Kawasebenzi njalo aweluki. Kodwa ngilitshela ukuthi laye uSolomoni ekucwebezeleni kwakhe kazange acece njengawo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 12:28"/><char style="wj">Nxa uNkulunkulu ececisa kanjalo utshani beganga, obukhona namuhla, kusasa sebuphoselwa emlilweni, kambe uzalicecisa kanganani na, lina bokukholwa okuncinyane!</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 12:29"/><char style="wj">Lingazihluphi ezinhliziyweni zenu ngokuthi lizakudlani kumbe lizanathani; lingakhathazeki ngalokho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 12:30"/><char style="wj">Ngoba umhlaba wabezizwe uxotshana lezinto ezinjalo, ikanti uYihlo uyazi ukuthi liyazidinga.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 12:31"/><char style="wj">Kodwa funani umbuso wakhe, zonke lezizinto lizaziphiwa lazo.</char><verse eid="LUK 12:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 12:32"/>
    <char style="wj">Lingesabi, mhlambi omncane, ngoba uYihlo uthandile ukulipha umbuso.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 12:33"/><char style="wj">Thengisani impahla yenu liphe abampofu. Zidingeleni izikhwama ezingagugiyo, inotho ezulwini engayikuphela, lapho okungasondeli khona isela loba impehlane engabhubhisi khona.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 12:34"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lapho okulenotho yakho khona, inhliziyo yakho layo ilapho.”</char><verse eid="LUK 12:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuhlala Ulindile</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 12:35"/>
    <char style="wj">“Gqokani lilindele inkonzo lezibane zenu zihlale zibhebha</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 12:36"/><char style="wj">njengamadoda elindele inkosi yawo ukuba ibuye edilini lomthimba ukuze kuthi nxa ifika iqoqoda aphange ayivulele umnyango.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 12:37"/><char style="wj">Kuzakuba kuhle kulezozinceku inkosi yazo ezazifica zilindile nxa ifika. Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi yona izagqokela ukubaphakela, bona bahlale etafuleni, yona ibaphakele.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 12:38"/><char style="wj">Kuzakuba kuhle kulezozinceku inkosi yazo ezazifica zilindile loba ingabe ifika ngomlindo wesibili loba owesithathu ebusuku.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 12:39"/><char style="wj">Kodwa zwisisani lokhu: Aluba umninindlu ubesazi ukuthi isela lizafika ngasiphi isikhathi ubengasoze ayekele indlu yakhe igqekezwe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 12:40"/><char style="wj">Lani hlalani lilindile ngoba iNdodana yoMuntu izafika ngesikhathi elingayilindelanga ngaso.”</char><verse eid="LUK 12:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 12:41"/>UPhethro wabuza wathi, “Nkosi, umzekeliso lo uwuqondise kithi kumbe ebantwini bonke na?”<verse eid="LUK 12:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 12:42"/>INkosi yaphendula yathi, <char style="wj">“Ngubani kambe ongumphathi othembekileyo, ohlakaniphileyo, othi inkosi yakhe imbeke ukukhangela izisebenzi zayo ukuba aziphe isabelo sazo sokudla ngesikhathi esifaneleyo?</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 12:43"/><char style="wj">Kuzakuba kuhle kuleyo nceku inkosi ezayifica isenza njalo ekuphendukeni kwayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 12:44"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, izakumbeka ukuthi aphathe yonke impahla yayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 12:45"/><char style="wj">Kodwa cabanga nxa inceku ingazitshela ithi, ‘Inkosi yami isiphuzile ukubuya,’ ibisiqalisa ukutshaya ezinye izisebenzi zesilisa lezesifazane, ibisisidla, inatha idakwe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 12:46"/><char style="wj">Inkosi yaleyonceku izabuya ngosuku engacatshangelwa khona langesikhathi inceku engasaziyo. Izayiqumaquma iyiphe indawo phakathi kwabangakholwayo.</char><verse eid="LUK 12:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 12:47"/>
    <char style="wj">Leyonceku ethi ikwazi okufunwa yinkosi yayo kodwa ingalindi kumbe ingalungisi lokho inkosi yayo ekufunayo izatshaywa okuzwayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 12:48"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lowo ongaziyo njalo owenza izinto eziholela ekubhujisweni uzatshaywa mbijana. Kulowo ophiwe okunengi, kuzafuneka okunengi kuye; lakulowo ogciniswe okunengi, kuzafuneka okunengi kulalokho.”</char><verse eid="LUK 12:48"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Hatshi Ukuthula Kodwa Ukwehlukana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 12:49"/>
    <char style="wj">“Ngilande ukuzalumathisa umlilo emhlabeni, ngize ngifise ukuthi ngabe uvele usungunguma!</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 12:50"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngiseselobhaphathizo okusamele ngilungene, kodwa ngikhathazekile kakhulu kuze kugcwaliseke lokho!</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 12:51"/><char style="wj">Licabanga ukuthi ngalanda ukuletha ukuthula emhlabeni na? Hatshi, zwanini, ngalanda ukuzehlukanisa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 12:52"/><char style="wj">Kusukela manje bazakuthi bebahlanu emulini behlukane, abathathu bexabana lababili, lababili bexabana labathathu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="LUK 12:53"/><char style="wj">Bazakwehlukana, uyise axabane lendodana, indodana ixabane loyise, unina lendodakazi, indodakazi ixabane lonina, uninazala axabane lomalukazana, umalukazana loninazala.”</char><verse eid="LUK 12:53"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuzwisisa Izikhathi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v" sid="LUK 12:54"/>Wathi exukwini labantu: <char style="wj">“Lithi lingabona iyezi liqhamuka entshonalanga liphange lithi, ‘Izulu lizakuna,’ lakanye line.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="LUK 12:55"/><char style="wj">Kuthi kungavunguza umoya weningizimu lithi, ‘Kuzatshisa,’ lakanye kube njalo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="LUK 12:56"/><char style="wj">Bazenzisi! Liyakwazi ukuchaza izibonakaliso zomhlaba lezomkhathi. Kungani pho lingakwazi ukuchaza isikhathi lesi esikuso na?</char><verse eid="LUK 12:56"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="LUK 12:57"/>
    <char style="wj">Kungani kanti lingaziboneli lina ngokwenu okuyikho okulungileyo na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="LUK 12:58"/><char style="wj">Nxa uhamba lalowo okumangalelayo lisiya kumahluleli, zama ngamandla ukuthi liqedelane lisesendleleni, funa akudonsele kumahluleli, lomahluleli abesekudlulisela enxuseni lona inxusa likuthele entolongweni.</char> <verse eid="LUK 12:58"/><verse number="59" style="v" sid="LUK 12:59"/><char style="wj">Ngiyakutshela, kawusoze uphume uze uhlawule kanye lohlamvana lokucina lwemali.”</char><verse eid="LUK 12:59"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="LUK 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Phendukani Kumbe Libhubhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 13:1"/>Bakhona ababelapho ngalesosikhathi abatshela uJesu ngamaGalile uPhilathu axubanisa imihlatshelo yawo legazi lawo. <verse eid="LUK 13:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 13:2"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kambe likhumbula ukuthi amaGalile lawo ayeyizoni kulamanye amaGalile ngoba ahlupheka kanjalo na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 13:3"/><char style="wj">Ngithi, hatshi! Kodwa, ngaphandle kokuba liphenduke lani lonke lizabhubha.</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 13:4"/><char style="wj">Kumbe labo abalitshumi lasificaminwembili abafayo baze bawelwe ngumphotshongo waseSilowami, licabanga ukuthi babonile okudlula bonke ababehlala eJerusalema na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 13:5"/><char style="wj">Ngithi, hatshi! Kodwa, ngaphandle kokuba liphenduke lani lonke lizabhubha.”</char><verse eid="LUK 13:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 13:6"/>Wasebatshela umzekeliso lo wathi, <char style="wj">“Indoda ethile yayilesihlahla somkhiwa uhlanyelwe esivinini sayo, yasisiyacinga izithelo kuwo, kodwa yaziswela.</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 13:7"/><char style="wj">Yasisithi kuleyondoda eyayigcina isivini, ‘Sekuyiminyaka emithathu ngilokhu ngisiza ngizofuna izithelo kulesisihlahla somkhiwa kodwa ngingatholi lutho. Sigamule! Senzani kambe siqeda ukudla emhlabathini?’</char><verse eid="LUK 13:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 13:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Indoda yaphendula yathi, ‘Nkosi, ake usiyekele nje okomnyaka owodwa, kengisihlakulele kuhle ngithele umvundiso.</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 13:9"/><char style="wj">Singathela ngomnyaka ozayo, kuzabe kulungile! Kodwa singangatheli, usungasigamula.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 13:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Owesifazane Oyisilima NgeSabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 13:10"/>Ngelinye iSabatha uJesu wayefundisa kwelinye isinagogu, <verse eid="LUK 13:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 13:11"/>khonapho kulowesifazane owangenwa ngumoya wamenza waba yisilima okweminyaka elitshumi lasificaminwembili. Wayegogekile esehluleka ukuhlala aqonde. <verse eid="LUK 13:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 13:12"/>Kwathi uJesu embona wambizela phambili wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Mama, usukhululwe ekugogekeni kwakho.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 13:13"/>Wasebeka izandla zakhe phezu kwakhe, masinyane nje owesifazane watshwaphuluka, waqonda, wasedumisa uNkulunkulu.<verse eid="LUK 13:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 13:14"/>Umphathi wesinagogu wacunuka ngoba uJesu wayesilise ngeSabatha, wathi ebantwini, “Ziyisithupha insuku zokwenza umsebenzi. Ngakho libobuya lizosiliswa ngalezonsuku, hatshi ngeSabatha.”<verse eid="LUK 13:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 13:15"/>INkosi yamphendula yathi, <char style="wj">“Lina bazenzisi! Kalizikhululi yini lonke lapha izifuyo zenu ngeSabatha esibayeni liyezinathisa na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 13:16"/><char style="wj">Manje-ke, owesifazane lo oyindodakazi ka-Abhrahama, obebotshwe nguSathane okweminyaka eminengi, elitshumi lasificaminwembili, lithi kangakhululwa yini ngeSabatha kulokho obekumbophile?”</char><verse eid="LUK 13:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 13:17"/>Wathi esekutshilo lokhu, bonke ababephikisana laye bayangeka, kodwa abantu babethokoza ngazozonke izinto ezimangalisayo ayezenza.<verse eid="LUK 13:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wentanga Yemastadi Lowemvubelo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 13:18"/>UJesu wasebuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Umbuso kaNkulunkulu ufana lani na? Kambe ngiwulinganise lani?</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 13:19"/><char style="wj">Unjengentanga yemastadi eyathathwa ngenye indoda yayihlanyela esivandeni sayo. Yamila yakhula yaba yisihlahla, izinyoni zemoyeni zahlala engatsheni zaso.”</char><verse eid="LUK 13:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 13:20"/>Waphinda wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiwufanise lani umbuso kaNkulunkulu na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 13:21"/><char style="wj">Unjengemvubelo eyathathwa ngowesifazane wayixubanisa lempuphu enengi, yabila yagcwala inhlama yonke.”</char><verse eid="LUK 13:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umnyango Omncinyane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 13:22"/>UJesu wasehamba engena emadolobheni lemizini efundisa, ejonge ukuya eJerusalema. <verse eid="LUK 13:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 13:23"/>Omunye wambuza wathi, “Nkosi, ngabalutshwana kuphela abazasindiswa na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 13:23">Wathi kubo, <verse eid="LUK 13:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 13:24"/><char style="wj">“Zamani ngamandla ukuthi lingene ngomnyango omncinyane, ngoba ngiyalitshela ukuthi abanengi bazazama ukungena kodwa bazakwehluleka.</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 13:25"/><char style="wj">Angavele aphakame umninindlu avale umnyango lizakuma phandle liqoqode lincenga lisithi, ‘Nkosi, sivulele umnyango.’</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 13:25">
    <char style="wj">Kodwa uzaphendula athi, ‘Kangilazi, kangazi njalo ukuthi livela ngaphi.’</char><verse eid="LUK 13:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 13:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Lapho lizakuthi, ‘Sadla lawe, sanatha sonke, njalo wafundisa emigwaqweni yakithi.’</char><verse eid="LUK 13:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 13:27"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa uzaphendula athi, ‘Kangilazi, njalo kangikwazi ukuthi livela ngaphi. Sukani kimi, lonke lina benzi bobubi!’</char><verse eid="LUK 13:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 13:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Kuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla kwamazinyo nxa selibona u-Abhrahama, u-Isaka loJakhobe labo bonke abaphrofethi embusweni kaNkulunkulu, kodwa lina ngokwenu lilahlelwe phandle.</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 13:29"/><char style="wj">Abantu bazavela empumalanga lasentshonalanga kanye lasenhla laseningizimu, bathathe izindawo zabo edilini lombuso kaNkulunkulu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 13:30"/><char style="wj">Ngempela bakhona labo abangabokucina abazakuba ngabokuqala, labangabokuqala abazakuba ngabokucina.”</char><verse eid="LUK 13:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uzwela IJerusalema Usizi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 13:31"/>Ngalesosikhathi abanye abaFarisi beza kuJesu bathi kuye, “Suka lapha uye kwenye indawo. UHerodi ufuna ukukubulala.”<verse eid="LUK 13:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 13:32"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Hambani liyotshela ikhanka lelo lithi, ‘Ngizawaxotsha amadimoni, ngisilise abantu, lamuhla lakusasa langosuku lwesithathu ngize ngiyiphethe indima yami.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 13:33"/><char style="wj">Loba kunjani kumele ngiqhubeke ngohambo lwami lamuhla lakusasa langelanga elilandelayo, ngoba ngempela kakho umphrofethi ongafela ngaphandle kweJerusalema!</char><verse eid="LUK 13:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 13:34"/>
    <char style="wj">Jerusalema, Jerusalema, wena obulala abaphrofethi, ubakhande ngamatshe labo abathunywe kuwe, sekukanengi ngiloyisa ukuqoqa ndawonye abantwabakho, njengesikhukhukazi siqoqa amatsiyane aso ngaphansi kwamaphiko aso, kodwa wawulokhu ungafuni!</char> <verse eid="LUK 13:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 13:35"/><char style="wj">Khangela, indlu yakho isitshiywe ilunxiwa. Ngiyalitshela, kalisayikungibona futhi lize lithi, ‘Ubusisiwe lowo obuya ngebizo leNkosi.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.35 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.26</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="LUK 13:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="LUK 14"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Endlini YomFarisi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 14:1"/>Ngelinye iSabatha uJesu wayakudla endlini yomFarisi owayedume kakhulu, babemkhangele kakhulu. <verse eid="LUK 14:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 14:2"/>Phambi kwakhe khonapho kwakulendoda eyayilesifo sikambizankulu, esivuvukisa izitho. <verse eid="LUK 14:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 14:3"/>UJesu wasebuza abaFarisi lezazi zomthetho wathi, <char style="wj">“Kusemthethweni yini ukusilisa ngosuku lweSabatha kumbe hatshi?”</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 14:4"/>Kodwa bathula. Ngakho waseyibamba indoda leyo wayisilisa wathi kayihambe.<verse eid="LUK 14:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 14:5"/>Wasebabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Nxa omunye wenu elendodana loba inkabi yakhe ewele emgodini ngeSabatha, kayikuphanga ayikhuphe masinyane na?”</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 14:6"/>Baswela ukuthi bathini.<verse eid="LUK 14:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 14:7"/>Wananzelela ukuthi izethekeli zazikhetha izindawo eziqakathekileyo etafuleni wasebatshela umzekeliso wathi: <verse eid="LUK 14:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 14:8"/><char style="wj">“Nxa omunye ekunxusa edilini lomthimba, ungaze wathatha indawo eqakathekileyo funa kunxuswe umuntu omkhulu kulawe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 14:9"/><char style="wj">Nxa kunjalo umalinxusa uzakuza athi kuwe, ‘Ake uxekele lo omunye isihlalo sakho.’ Uzabe usuyangekile ususiyahlala endaweni ephansi kakhulu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 14:10"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa unxusiwe, hlala endaweni ephansi kakhulu ukuze kuthi nxa umakunxusa efika kuwe athi, ‘Mngane, sukuma uye endaweni engcono.’ Lapho-ke, uzabe uphakanyisiwe phambi kwabo bonke abanxuswe kanye lawe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 14:11"/><char style="wj">Ngoba wonke umuntu oziphakamisayo uzakwehliswa, kuthi lowo ozehlisayo aphakanyiswe.”</char><verse eid="LUK 14:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 14:12"/>UJesu wasesithi emanxuseni, <char style="wj">“Nxa usenza idili emini loba kusihlwa unganxusi abangane bakho loba abafowenu kumbe izihlobo kumbe omakhelwane abanothileyo; ungenza njalo labo bangakunxusa, kuthi-ke lawe usuwenanisiwe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 14:13"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa usenza idili, nxusa abayanga, izilima, izigoga, iziphofu,</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 14:14"/><char style="wj">lapho uzabusiswa. Loba bengasoze bakwenanise lawe, uzakwenaniswa ekuvukeni kwabalungileyo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 14:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wedili Elikhulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 14:15"/>Kwathi omunye walabo abahlezi etafuleni laye esekuzwile lokhu, wathi kuJesu, “Ubusisiwe lowomuntu ozakudla edilini embusweni kaNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="LUK 14:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 14:16"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Umuntu othile wayesenza idili elikhulu ngakho wanxusa abantu abanengi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 14:17"/><char style="wj">Sekuyisikhathi sedili wathuma isisebenzi sakhe ukuyatshela ababenxusiwe ukuthi, ‘Wozani, konke sekulungile.’</char><verse eid="LUK 14:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 14:18"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa bonke baqala ukuxolisa. Owokuqala wathi, ‘Ngisanda kuthenga isivande ngakho kusamele ngiyesibona. Ngicela ungixolisele.’</char><verse eid="LUK 14:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 14:19"/>
    <char style="wj">Omunye wathi, ‘Khathesi nje ngisanda kuthenga izipani ezinhlanu zenkabi, ungifica ngivele ngisendleleni yokuyazihlola. Ngicela ungixolisele.’</char><verse eid="LUK 14:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 14:20"/>
    <char style="wj">Omunye njalo wathi, ‘Ngisanda kutshada nje khathesi ngakho angingeke ngize.’</char><verse eid="LUK 14:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 14:21"/>
    <char style="wj">Inceku yabuya yakubika konke lokhu enkosini yayo. Inkosi yathukuthela yasilaya inceku yayo yathi, ‘Hamba khathesi, uye ezitaladini lemikotweni yedolobho umeme abayanga, abagogekileyo, iziphofu labaqhulayo.’</char><verse eid="LUK 14:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 14:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Inceku yathi, ‘Nkosi, lokho okulayileyo sokwenziwe kodwa indawo isesekhona.’</char><verse eid="LUK 14:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 14:23"/>
    <char style="wj">Inkosi yatshela inceku yayo yathi, ‘Hamba uye emigwaqweni lasezindleleni zemaphandleni uze labo ukuze indlu yami igcwale.</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 14:24"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela kakho loyedwa walabo bantu ababenxusiwe ozalizwa idili lami.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 14:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umvuzo Wokuba Ngumfundi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 14:25"/>Abantu abanengi babehamba loJesu, wasephendukela kubo wathi: <verse eid="LUK 14:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 14:26"/><char style="wj">“Nxa umuntu esiza kimi, kodwa engeke azonda uyise lonina, umkakhe labantwana, abafowabo labodadewabo, kanye lempilo yakhe uqobo, ngeke abe ngumfundi wami.</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 14:27"/><char style="wj">Lowo ongathwali isiphambano sakhe angilandele ngeke abe ngumfundi wami.</char><verse eid="LUK 14:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 14:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Akesithi omunye wenu afune ukwakha umphotshongo. Kambe kazukuqala ahlale phansi abalise indleko ukuze abone ingabe ulayo yini imali yokuwuqeda na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 14:29"/><char style="wj">Ngoba engakha isisekelo, kodwa ehluleke ukusiqeda, wonke okubonayo uzamhleka,</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 14:30"/><char style="wj">esithi, ‘Indoda le yaqalisa ukwakha, kodwa yehluleka ukuqeda.’</char><verse eid="LUK 14:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 14:31"/>
    <char style="wj">Kumbe sithi inkosi ilungisela ukuya empini isilwa lenye inkosi. Kayizukuqala ihlale phansi yini ihluzisise engqondweni ingabe yona ngamabutho ayo azinkulungwane ezilitshumi ingaqondana laleyo elezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 14:32"/><char style="wj">Nxa ingeyikuma, izathuma amanxusa kuleyana isesekude icele uxolo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 14:33"/><char style="wj">Ngaleyondlela, loba ngubani phakathi kwenu ongadeli konke alakho ngeke abe ngumfundi wami.</char><verse eid="LUK 14:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 14:34"/>
    <char style="wj">Itswayi lilungile kodwa lingalahlekelwa yibumunyu balo, lingavuselelwa kanjani na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 14:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 14:35"/><char style="wj">Kaliwulungelanga lomhlabathi loba inqumbi yomvundiso kodwa liyalahlwa.</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 14:35">
    <char style="wj">Lowo olendlebe zokuzwa, kezwe.”</char><verse eid="LUK 14:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="LUK 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wemvu Elahlekileyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 15:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi kwasekubuthana kuye abathelisi lezoni ukuzokuzwa imfundiso yakhe. <verse eid="LUK 15:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 15:2"/>Kodwa abaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho bakhonona bathi, “Umuntu lo wemukela izoni adle lazo.”<verse eid="LUK 15:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 15:3"/>UJesu wasebatshela umzekeliso lo, wathi: <verse eid="LUK 15:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 15:4"/><char style="wj">“Ake kuthiwe omunye wenu ulezimvu ezilikhulu besekulahleka eyodwa kuzo. Kazukuzitshiya yini lezo ezingamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lasificamunwemunye khonale egangeni ayidinge leyo elahlekileyo aze ayithole na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 15:5"/><char style="wj">Kuthi lapho eseyitholile ayithwale emahlombe ngokuthokoza</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 15:6"/><char style="wj">aye layo ekhaya. Abesebiza abangane bakhe labomakhelwane athi, ‘Thokozani lami; sengiyitholile imvu yami ebilahlekile.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 15:7"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela ukuthi ngaleyondlela kuzakuba lokuthokoza ezulwini ngokuphenduka kwesoni esisodwa okudlula labobantu abalungileyo abangamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lasificamunwemunye abangakudingiyo ukuphenduka.”</char><verse eid="LUK 15:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wemali Elahlekileyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 15:8"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kumbe kuthi owesifazane elenhlamvu zesiliva ezilitshumi kulahleke uhlamvu olulodwa. Kalumathisi yini isibane, athanyele endlini, adingisise kuhle aze aluthole na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 15:9"/><char style="wj">Kuthi eselutholile abize abangane bakhe labomakhelwane, athi kubo, ‘Thokozani lami; sengilutholile uhlamvu lwami lwesiliva obelulahlekile.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 15:10"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela ukuthi ngaleyondlela kulokuthokoza phambi kwezingilosi zikaNkulunkulu ngokuphenduka kwesoni esisodwa.”</char><verse eid="LUK 15:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wendodana Yolahleko</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 15:11"/>UJesu waqhubeka wathi: <char style="wj">“Kwakukhona indoda eyayilamadodana amabili.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 15:12"/><char style="wj">Encinyane yathi kuyise, ‘Baba, ngipha esami isabelo selifa.’ Ngakho uyise wabehlukanisela impahla yakhe bobabili.</char><verse eid="LUK 15:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 15:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngemva kwesikhatshana indodana encane yabutha konke okungokwayo yasuka yaya elizweni elikhatshana, yafika khonale yayichitha inotho yayo ngempilo yokuxhwala.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 15:14"/><char style="wj">Isitshaye yachitha konke, kwaba lendlala enkulu kulolonke ilizwe, yasiswela kakhulu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 15:15"/><char style="wj">Yasisiyadinga umsebenzi komunye umuntu wakulelolizwe owayisa esiqintini sakhe ukuyagcina ingulube.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 15:16"/><char style="wj">Yabona kungcono kuyo ukuthi ixotshe iphango ngokudla okwakudliwa zingulube, kodwa kayizange iphiwe lutho langubani.</char><verse eid="LUK 15:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 15:17"/>
    <char style="wj">Kwathi lapho ingqondo yayo isicabanga kuhle, yathi, ‘Kambe zingaki izinceku zikababa ezidla zizezitshiye kodwa nanku mina ngifa ngendlala!</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 15:18"/><char style="wj">Ngizasuka ngibuyele kubaba ngifike ngithi kuye: Baba, ngenze isono phambi kwezulu lakuwe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 15:19"/><char style="wj">Kangisafanelanga ukuthiwa ngiyindodana yakho; ngenza ngibe njengomunye wezinceku zakho.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 15:20"/><char style="wj">Ngakho yaphakama yaya kuyise.</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 15:20">
    <char style="wj">Kodwa yathi isesebucwala uyise wayibona wayizwela isihawu; wagijimela kuyo indodana yakhe, wayigona, wayanga.</char><verse eid="LUK 15:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 15:21"/>
    <char style="wj">Indodana yathi kuye, ‘Baba, ngenze isono phambi kwezulu lakuwe. Kangisafanelanga ukuthiwa ngiyindodana yakho.’</char><verse eid="LUK 15:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 15:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa uyise wathi ezincekwini zakhe, ‘Phangisani! Lethani isembatho esihle ukwedlula ezinye limgqokise. Lifake indandatho emunweni wakhe, limgqokise lamanyathela ezinyaweni zakhe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 15:23"/><char style="wj">Beseliletha ithole elinonisiweyo lilihlabe. Asenzeni idili sithokoze.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 15:24"/><char style="wj">Ngoba indodana yami le yayisifile, kodwa isiphila njalo; yayilahlekile manje isifunyenwe.’ Waqalisa manje umkhosi wokujabula.</char><verse eid="LUK 15:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 15:25"/>
    <char style="wj">Sonke lesisikhathi indodana endala yayisensimini. Yathi isibanga endlini yezwa kuhlatshelelwa njalo kugidwa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 15:26"/><char style="wj">Yasibiza omunye wezinceku yambuza ukuthi kwakusenzakalani.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 15:27"/><char style="wj">Waphendula wathi, ‘Umfowenu usebuyile, ngakho uyihlo usemhlabele ithole elinonisiweyo ngoba ubuye ephilile, ephelele.’</char><verse eid="LUK 15:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 15:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Umnewabo wazonda kakhulu, wala ukungena ngekhaya. Uyise wasephuma esiya kuye ukuyamncenga.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 15:29"/><char style="wj">Kodwa waphendula uyise wathi, ‘Khangela! Iminyaka yonke le bengikusebenzela kanzima njalo kangizange ngeqe imilayo yakho. Kodwa kawuzange ungiphe lokulizinyane kodwa lokhu ukuthi lami kengithokoze labangane bami.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 15:30"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lokhu kuthi nxa indodana yakho le esitshaye yathintitha inotho yakho lezifebe, isibuyile ekhaya uyihlabele ithole elinonisiweyo!’</char><verse eid="LUK 15:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 15:31"/>
    <char style="wj">Uyise wathi, ‘Ndodana yami, uhlezi ulami sonke isikhathi njalo konke engilakho ngokwakho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 15:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 15:32"/><char style="wj">Kodwa bekufanele sithokoze sijabule ngoba umfowenu lo wayesefile, manje usephila njalo; ubelahlekile, usefunyenwe.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 15:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="LUK 16"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Womphathi Oliqili</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 16:1"/>UJesu watshela abafundi bakhe wathi, <char style="wj">“Kwakulendoda eyayinothile ilomphathi owetheswa icala lokuthi wayechithachithe inotho yayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 16:2"/><char style="wj">Yambiza yambuza yathi, ‘Kuyini lokhu engikuzwayo ngawe? Landisa kuhle ukuthi uhambisa njani izinto ngoba ungeke usaba ngumphathi njalo.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 16:3"/>
    <char style="wj">Umphathi wazibuza wathi, ‘Ngizakuthini? Inkosi yami isingithathela umsebenzi wami. Kangilamandla okugebha, njalo ngilenhloni zokucela.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 16:4"/><char style="wj">Ngiyazi engizakwenza ukuthi nxa ngilahlekelwa ngumsebenzi wami abantu bangamukele ezindlini zabo.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 16:5"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho yasibiza labo ababelezikwelede enkosini yayo munye ngamunye yathi, kowokuqala, ‘Isikwelede sakho enkosini yami singakanani?’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 16:6"/>
    <char style="wj">Wathi, ‘Ngamalitha amafutha e-oliva azinkulungwane ezine.’</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 16:6">
    <char style="wj">Umphathi wamtshela wathi, ‘Phangisa, thatha incwadi yakho yesikwelede ubhale izinkulungwane ezimbili.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 16:7"/>
    <char style="wj">Yasibuza owesibili yathi, ‘Wena ulesikwelede esingakanani?’</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 16:7">
    <char style="wj">Wathi, ‘Yimigodla yengqoloyi eyinkulungwane.’</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 16:7">
    <char style="wj">Yamtshela yathi, ‘Thatha incwadi yakho yesikwelede ubhale amakhulu ayisificaminwembili.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 16:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Inkosi yamncoma lowomphathi owayeliqili ngoba wayenze ukuhlakanipha. Ngoba abantu balumhlaba balezindledlana zabo zokuhlakanipha ekuphathaneni kwabo ukwedlula abantu bokukhanya.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 16:9"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela ngithi, sebenzisani inotho yomhlaba ukuzuza abangane ukuze kuthi nxa isiphelile lamukeleke ezindlini ezimi laphakade.</char><verse eid="LUK 16:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 16:10"/>
    <char style="wj">Lowo othembeke kokuncinyane uzakwethembeka njalo kokunengi, ikanti lowo ongathembekanga kokuncinyane angeke njalo athembeke kokunengi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 16:11"/><char style="wj">Ngakho-ke, nxa lingathembekanga ekuphatheni inotho yasemhlabeni, pho ngubani ongalithemba ngenotho yeqiniso na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 16:12"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa belingathembekanga ngempahla yomunye umuntu, ngubani kambe ozalipha impahla ibe ngeyenu na?</char><verse eid="LUK 16:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 16:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Kakulanceku engakhonza amakhosi amabili. Funa izonde enye kodwa ithande enye, kumbe izinikele kwenye yeyise enye. Ngezake likhonze uNkulunkulu lemali ngokufanayo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 16:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 16:14"/>AbaFarisi ababethanda imali bakuzwa konke lokhu, bamklolodela uJesu. <verse eid="LUK 16:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 16:15"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Yini elizigezayo emehlweni abantu kodwa uNkulunkulu uyazazi inhliziyo zenu. Lokho okuligugu ebantwini kuyisinengiso kuNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 16:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Eyinye Imfundiso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 16:16"/>
    <char style="wj">“UMthetho labaPhrofethi kwatshunyayelwa kwaze kwaba yisikhathi sikaJohane. Kusukela kulesosikhathi izindaba ezinhle zombuso kaNkulunkulu ziyatshunyayelwa njalo bonke abantu bazifuqela kuwo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 16:17"/><char style="wj">Kungaba lula ukuthi izulu lomhlaba kunyamalale kulokuthi kucitshe ichatha loMthetho elilodwa nje.</char><verse eid="LUK 16:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 16:18"/>
    <char style="wj">Loba ngubani olahla umkakhe athathe omunye umfazi uyafeba njalo lendoda ethatha umfazi owalahlwayo iyafeba.”</char><verse eid="LUK 16:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Indoda Enothileyo LoLazaro</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 16:19"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kwakulendoda enothileyo eyayigqoka izigqoko zombala oyibubende lezelembu lelineni, iphakathi kobutifitifi insuku zonke.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 16:20"/><char style="wj">Entubeni yomuzi wayo kwakuhlezi isiceli esasithiwa nguLazaro, sigcwele izilonda emzimbeni,</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 16:21"/><char style="wj">siloyisa ukudla lokho okwakukhithika etafuleni yalesosicebi. Izinja zazifika zikhothe izilonda zaso.</char><verse eid="LUK 16:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 16:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Kwafika isikhathi lapho isiceli esafa khona, izingilosi zasithwala zasisa eceleni lika-Abhrahama. Lesicebi laso safa, sabekwa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 16:23"/><char style="wj">Esihogweni lapho esasisitsha khona; savusa ubuso sabona u-Abhrahama ekude le, kuloLazaro eceleni kwakhe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 16:24"/><char style="wj">Sasesimemeza sathi, ‘Baba Abhrahama, ake ungihawukele uthume uLazaro agxamuze umunwe wakhe emanzini athambise ulimi lwami, ngoba ngisebuhlungwini emlilweni lo.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 16:25"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa u-Abhrahama waphendula wathi, ‘Ndodana, khumbula ukuthi ngesikhathi usaphila wazuza izinto zakho ezinhle kodwa uLazaro wemukela izinto ezimbi, khangela manje useduduzwa lapha, ikanti wena ususebuhlungwini.</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 16:26"/><char style="wj">Njalo ngaphandle kwakho konke lokhu, phakathi kwethu lawe kulodonga olukhulu, ukwenzela ukuthi labo abafisa ukuza ngapho besuka lapha behluleke, futhi kakho ongapho ongachaphela ngakithi.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 16:27"/>
    <char style="wj">Saphendula sathi, ‘Nxa kunjalo-ke, ngiyakuncenga, baba, thuma uLazaro endlini kababa,</char> <verse eid="LUK 16:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 16:28"/><char style="wj">ngoba ngilabafowethu abahlanu. Ayebaxwayisa ukuze labo bangezi kule indawo yobuhlungu.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 16:29"/>
    <char style="wj">U-Abhrahama waphendula wathi, ‘BaloMosi labaPhrofethi; kabalalele bona.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 16:30"/>
    <char style="wj">Sathi, ‘Hatshi, baba Abhrahama, kodwa nxa kusuka umuntu kwabafileyo aye kubo bazaphenduka.’</char><verse eid="LUK 16:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 16:31"/>
    <char style="wj">Wathi kuso, ‘Nxa bengalaleli uMosi labaPhrofethi, kabasoze bavume loba omunye angaze avuke kwabafileyo.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 16:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="LUK 17"/>
  <para style="s1">Isono, Ukholo, Umlandu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 17:1"/>UJesu wathi kubafundi bakhe: <char style="wj">“Izinto ezenza abantu benze isono zizakuba khona kodwa maye kulowomuntu ezizafika ngaye.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 17:2"/><char style="wj">Bekungaba ngcono kuye ukuphoselwa olwandle kubotshelwe imbokodo entanyeni yakhe kulokuba yena akhubekise omunye walaba abancinyane ukuthi enze isono.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 17:3"/><char style="wj">Ngakho lina ziqapheleni.</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 17:3">
    <char style="wj">Nxa umfowenu esenza isono, mkhuze, kuthi nxa ezisola, mthethelele.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 17:4"/><char style="wj">Nxa engakonela kasikhombisa ngosuku lunye, ebuye kuwe kasikhombisa esithi, ‘Ngiyaxolisa,’ mthethelele.”</char><verse eid="LUK 17:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 17:5"/>Abapostoli bathi eNkosini, “Yengeza ukholo lwethu!”<verse eid="LUK 17:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 17:6"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Nxa lilokukholwa loba kukuncinyane njengentanga yemastadi, lingathi kulesisihlahla somabhulosi, ‘Quphuka lapha uyowela olwandle,’ sizalilalela.</char><verse eid="LUK 17:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 17:7"/>
    <char style="wj">Kesithi omunye wenu ulesisebenzi, silima loba siselusa izimvu. Kambe kungenzeka yini ukuthi nxa isisebenzi singena sivela emasimini athi kuso, ‘Kulungile, hlala phansi udle’?</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 17:8"/><char style="wj">Kambe kayikuqala athi, ‘Lungisa ukudla kwami, ulungele ukungiphakela ngize ngidle, nginathe; ngemva kwalokho lawe usungadla, unathe’?</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 17:9"/><char style="wj">Angasibonga na isisebenzi ngoba senze lokho ebesikuyaliwe na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 17:10"/><char style="wj">Kunjalo lani nxa selenzile konke okuthiwe likwenze kufanele lithi, ‘Siyizinceku ezingafanelanga; sesenze kuphela lokho okungumlandu wethu.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 17:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Abalitshumi Abalobulephero</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 17:11"/>Ngalesosikhathi eseqonde ukuya eJerusalema, uJesu wahamba ngendlela esemngceleni phakathi kweSamariya leGalile. <verse eid="LUK 17:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 17:12"/>Wathi efika komunye umuzi, wahlangabezwa ngamadoda alitshumi ayelobulephero. Ema bucwala, <verse eid="LUK 17:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 17:13"/>amemeza ngelizwi elikhulu athi, “Jesu, Nkosi, sihawukele!”<verse eid="LUK 17:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 17:14"/>Wathi ewabona wathi kuwo, <char style="wj">“Hambani liyoziveza kubaphristi.”</char> Athi esahamba ahlambuluka.<verse eid="LUK 17:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 17:15"/>Omunye wawo wathi ngokubona ukuthi usesilile waphenduka, edumisa uNkulunkulu ngelizwi elikhulu. <verse eid="LUK 17:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 17:16"/>Wazilahla phansi ezinyaweni zikaJesu wambonga, yena wayengumSamariya.<verse eid="LUK 17:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 17:17"/>UJesu wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kanti kabahlanjululwanga bonke abalitshumi yini? Bangaphi abanye abayisificamunwemunye na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 17:18"/><char style="wj">Ubengekho yini obengabuya azoletha udumo kuNkulunkulu ngaphandle kwalo owezizweni na?”</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 17:19"/>Wasesithi kuye, <char style="wj">“Phakama uhambe; ukukholwa kwakho kukusilisile.”</char><verse eid="LUK 17:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuza Kombuso KaNkulunkulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 17:20"/>Ngesinye isikhathi uJesu ebuzwe ngabaFarisi ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu wawuzafika nini, waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Umbuso kaNkulunkulu kawuzi ngendlela yokucubungula kwenu ukuma kwezinto,</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 17:21"/><char style="wj">njalo abantu kabayikutsho bathi, ‘Nanku lapha,’ loba bathi, ‘Nanko laphaya,’ ngoba umbuso kaNkulunkulu uphakathi kwenu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 17:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 17:22"/>Wasesithi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Siyeza isikhathi lapho elizaloyisa khona ukubona olunye lwezinsuku zeNdodana yoMuntu kodwa kalisoze lilubone.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 17:23"/><char style="wj">Abantu bazalitshela bathi, ‘Nanguyana laphaya!’ kumbe, ‘Nangu lapha!’ Lingathatheki ngabo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 17:24"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngosuku lwayo iNdodana yoMuntu izakuba njengombane ophazima ukhanyise umkhathi kusukela ngapha kusiyafika ngale.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 17:25"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kumele iqale ihlupheke ezintweni ezinengi njalo ilahlwe yilesisizukulwane.</char><verse eid="LUK 17:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 17:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Njengoba kwakunjalo ensukwini zikaNowa, kuzakuba njalo ensukwini zeNdodana yoMuntu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 17:27"/><char style="wj">Abantu babesidla, benatha, bethathana njalo besendiselana kwaze kwafika usuku uNowa angena ngalo emkhunjini. Kwasekufika uzamcolo wababhubhisa bonke.</char><verse eid="LUK 17:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 17:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Kwakunjalo futhi ngezinsuku zikaLothi. Abantu babesidla, benatha, njalo bethenga, bethengisa, behlanyela njalo besakha.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 17:29"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngosuku uLothi aphuma ngalo eSodoma, umlilo lesalufa kwathululeka kuvela ezulwini kwababhubhisa bonke.</char><verse eid="LUK 17:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 17:30"/>
    <char style="wj">Kuzakuba njalo langosuku lapho iNdodana yoMuntu ifika.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 17:31"/><char style="wj">Ngalolosuku kakho ozakuthi ephezulu ophahleni lwendlu yakhe, impahla zakhe ziphakathi, ehle ukuyazithatha. Njalo kakho osensimini ozakuyathatha loba yini.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 17:32"/><char style="wj">Khumbulani umkaLothi!</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 17:33"/><char style="wj">Lowo ozama ukulondoloza impilo yakhe izamlahlekela, lalowo olahlekelwa yimpilo yakhe uzayilondoloza.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 17:34"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela, kuzakuthi ngalobobusuku abantu bebabili embhedeni omunye uzathathwa, kodwa omunye atshiywe.</char> <verse eid="LUK 17:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 17:35"/><char style="wj">Abesifazane ababili bazabe bechola elitsheni ndawonye; omunye uzathathwa omunye atshiywe.</char> [ <verse eid="LUK 17:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 17:36"/><char style="wj">Ababili bazabe besensimini; oyedwa uzathathwa omunye atshiywe.</char>]<char style="wj">”</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">17.36 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi kayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="LUK 17:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 17:37"/>Babuza bathi, “Ngaphi, Nkosi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 17:37">Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lapho okulesidumbu khona, kulapho okuqoqana khona amanqe.”</char><verse eid="LUK 17:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="LUK 18"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Womfelokazi Ophikelelayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 18:1"/>UJesu wasetshela abafundi bakhe umzekeliso ukubatshengisa ukuthi kumele bakhuleke kokuphela bangadinwa. <verse eid="LUK 18:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 18:2"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Kwelinye idolobho kwakulomahluli owayengamesabi uNkulunkulu njalo engakhathaleli muntu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 18:3"/><char style="wj">Kwakukhona umfelokazi kulelodolobho owayehlezi esiza kuye kokuphela emncenga esithi, ‘Akungincede ngalowo engixabana laye.’</char><verse eid="LUK 18:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 18:4"/>
    <char style="wj">Okwesikhathi eside umahluli wayesala. Kodwa wacina esithi, ‘Loba ngingamesabi uNkulunkulu njalo ngingakhathali ngomuntu,</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 18:5"/><char style="wj">kodwa ngenxa yokuthi umfelokazi lo usengijinge kakhulu sengizamlungisela ukuthi angaze abuya anginenge ngoba elokhu engilanda!’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 18:6"/>Njalo iNkosi yasisithi, <char style="wj">“Likuzwisise lokho okutshiwo ngumahluli ongalunganga.</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 18:7"/><char style="wj">Kambe uNkulunkulu kayikubalwela yini abakhethiweyo bakhe, abakhuleka kuye imini lobusuku? Uzabe elokhu ebanina yini?</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 18:8"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela, uzabalwela, njalo masinyane. Kodwa, nxa iNdodana yoMuntu isifika, izakufumana ukukholwa emhlabeni na?”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso WomFarisi LoMthelisi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 18:9"/>Kulabo ababezethemba ngokulunga kwabo beseyisa abanye, uJesu wakhuluma umzekeliso lo wathi: <verse eid="LUK 18:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 18:10"/><char style="wj">“Amadoda amabili aya ethempelini ukuyakhuleka, omunye engumFarisi njalo omunye engumthelisi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 18:11"/><char style="wj">UmFarisi wasukuma wakhuleka ngalokho ayeyikho khona wathi: ‘Nkulunkulu, ngiyakubonga ukuthi kanginjengabanye abantu, izigebenga, izixhwali, izifebe njalo kangifani lomthelisi lo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 18:12"/><char style="wj">Ngizila kabili ngeviki njalo nginikela okwetshumi okwenzuzo yami yonke.’</char><verse eid="LUK 18:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 18:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa umthelisi wema bucwadlana laye. Wesaba lokukhangela ezulwini kodwa wazehlisa kakhulu wathi, ‘Nkulunkulu, woba lesihawu kimi, ngiyisoni.’</char><verse eid="LUK 18:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 18:14"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela ukuthi indoda le, hatshi leyana enye, yabuyela ekhaya isilungisiwe phambi kukaNkulunkulu. Ngoba lowo oziphakamisayo uzakwehliswa, lozehlisayo uzaphakanyiswa.”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abantwana Abancinyane LoJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 18:15"/>Abantu njalo babeletha abantwana kuJesu ukuthi ababeke izandla. Abafundi bonela ukukubona lokhu babakhuza. <verse eid="LUK 18:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 18:16"/>Kodwa uJesu wabizela kuye abantwana wathi, <char style="wj">“Yekelani abantwana beze kimi, lingabavimbeli ngoba umbuso kaNkulunkulu ungowabanjengalaba.</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 18:17"/><char style="wj">Ngiqinisile ngithi kini, lowo ongayikwemukela umbuso kaNkulunkulu njengomntwana omncane kayikungena kuwo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umbusi Onothileyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 18:18"/>Umbusi othile wambuza wathi, “Mfundisi olungileyo, ngingenzani ukuze ngizuze ilifa lokuphila kwaphakade na?”<verse eid="LUK 18:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 18:19"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ungibizelani ngokuthi ngilungile na? Kakho olungileyo ngaphandle kukaNkulunkulu kuphela.</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 18:20"/><char style="wj">Uyayazi imilayo: ‘Ungafebi, ungabulali muntu, ungebi, ungaphi ubufakazi bamanga, hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">18.20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 20.12-16; UDutheronomi 5.16-20</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 18:21"/>Wathi umbusi, “Yonke le ngiyigcine kusukela ebutsheni bami.”<verse eid="LUK 18:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 18:22"/>UJesu esekuzwile lokho wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Usasilele into eyodwa. Thengisa konke olakho uphe abampofu, lapho-ke inotho yakho izakuba sezulwini. Ubusubuya ungilandele.”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 18:23"/>Wathi esezwe lokhu wadana kakhulu ngoba wayeyindoda eyayinothe kakhulu. <verse eid="LUK 18:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 18:24"/>UJesu wamkhangela wathi, <char style="wj">“Koba nzima kakhulu ukuthi isinothi singene embusweni kaNkulunkulu!</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 18:25"/><char style="wj">Ngempela kulula ukuthi ikamela lingene embotsheni yenalithi kulokuthi umuntu onothileyo awungene umbuso kaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 18:26"/>Labo abakuzwayo lokho babuza bathi, “Ngubani pho ongasindiswa?”<verse eid="LUK 18:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 18:27"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lokho okungenzekiyo emandleni abantu kuyenzakala kwakaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 18:28"/>UPhethro wathi kuye, “Sesadela konke esasilakho sakulandela!”<verse eid="LUK 18:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 18:29"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi kakho osetshiye ikhaya loba umfazi kumbe abafowabo loba abazali kumbe abantwana ngenxa yombuso kaNkulunkulu</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 18:30"/><char style="wj">ozakwehluleka ukuzuza ngokuphindwe kanengi esikhathini samanje lesikhathini esizayo, ukuphila okungapheliyo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhuluma Ngokufa Kwakhe Njalo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 18:31"/>UJesu wasebizela abalitshumi lambili eceleni wabatshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Sesisiya eJerusalema lapho konke okulotshwe ngabaphrofethi ngeNdodana yoMuntu sekusiya gcwaliseka.</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 18:32"/><char style="wj">Izanikelwa kwabeZizwe. Bazayihoza, bayithuke, bayikhafulele, bayibhule njalo bayibulale.</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 18:33"/><char style="wj">Ngosuku lwesithathu izavuka.”</char><verse eid="LUK 18:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 18:34"/>Abafundi kabazange bakuzwisise konke lokhu. Ingcazelo yakho yayifihlakele kubo yikho kabazanga ukuthi wayekhuluma ngani.<verse eid="LUK 18:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isiceli Esiyisiphofu Senziwa Sibone</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 18:35"/>UJesu esebanga eJerikho kwakulendoda eyisiphofu eyisiceli ihlezi eceleni kwendlela icela. <verse eid="LUK 18:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 18:36"/>Yathi isizwa kudlula ixuku labantu yabuza ukuthi kuyini okwakusenzakala. <verse eid="LUK 18:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 18:37"/>Bayitshela bathi, “UJesu waseNazaretha uyedlula khonapha.”<verse eid="LUK 18:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 18:38"/>Yamemeza yathi, “Jesu, Ndodana kaDavida, ake ungihawukele!”<verse eid="LUK 18:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 18:39"/>Labo ababehamba phambili bayikhuza bathi kayithule, kodwa yona yasimemeza ngamandla yathi, “Ndodana kaDavida ake ungihawukele!”<verse eid="LUK 18:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 18:40"/>UJesu wema wathi indoda leyo ilethwe kuye. Isifikile uJesu wayibuza wathi, <verse eid="LUK 18:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 18:41"/><char style="wj">“Ufuna ukuthi ngikwenzeleni?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 18:41">Yaphendula yathi, “Nkosi, ngifuna ukuthi ngibone.”<verse eid="LUK 18:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 18:42"/>UJesu wathi kuyo, <char style="wj">“Kuzuze-ke ukubona; ukukholwa kwakho kukusindisile.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 18:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 18:43"/>Masinyane yahle yabona, yasimlandela uJesu idumisa uNkulunkulu. Kwathi bonke abantu bekubona lokho, labo bamdumisa uNkulunkulu.<verse eid="LUK 18:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="LUK 19"/>
  <para style="s1">UZakhewu Umthelisi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 19:1"/>UJesu wangena eJerikho kodwa esedlula. <verse eid="LUK 19:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 19:2"/>Kwakulendoda eyayithiwa nguZakhewu; wayeyinduna yabathelisi njalo enothile. <verse eid="LUK 19:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 19:3"/>Wayefuna ukubona uJesu ukuthi wayengumuntu onjani, kodwa ngenxa yokuthi wayengumuntu omfitshane, wehluleka ngenxa yesiminyeminye. <verse eid="LUK 19:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 19:4"/>Wasegijimela phambili, wakhwela phezu komkhiwa wesikhamore ukuze ambone njengoba uJesu wayesiza ngaleyondlela.<verse eid="LUK 19:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 19:5"/>Kwathi uJesu esefikile kuleyondawo, wakhangela phezulu wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Zakhewu, yehla masinyane. Ngizakwethekelela endlini yakho lamuhla.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 19:6"/>Wasesehla uZakhewu masinyane wamamukela ngokuthokoza.<verse eid="LUK 19:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 19:7"/>Bonke abantu bakubona lokhu bangunguna besithi, “Useyekuba yisethekeli sesoni.”<verse eid="LUK 19:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 19:8"/>Kodwa uZakhewu wasukuma wathi eNkosini, “Khangela, Nkosi! Okwamanje senginika ingxenye yenotho yami kwabampofu njalo nxa ngike ngadlelezela omunye umuntu loba ngakuphi, ngizambhadala ngokuphindwe kane lokho engakuthathayo.”<verse eid="LUK 19:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 19:9"/>UJesu wasesithi kuye, <char style="wj">“Lamuhla insindiso isifikile kulindlu ngoba indoda le layo iyindodana ka-Abhrahama.</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 19:10"/><char style="wj">Ngoba iNdodana yoMuntu yalanda ukudinga lokusindisa lokho okwakulahlekile.”</char><verse eid="LUK 19:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wamamina Alitshumi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 19:11"/>Bathi besalalele lokhu, wabatshela omunye umzekeliso, ngoba wayesesondele eJerusalema, abantu sebecabanga ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu wawusuzahle uvele masinyane. <verse eid="LUK 19:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 19:12"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Indoda ethile yasesikhosini ngokuzalwa yaya elizweni elikhatshana isiyagcotshwa ukuba yinkosi andubana iphenduke.</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 19:13"/><char style="wj">Yasibiza izinceku zayo ezilitshumi yazinika imali engamamina alitshumi. Yathi, ‘Isebenziseni imali le ngize ngiphenduke.’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 19:14"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa labobantu ayezababusa babemzonda lumuntu, bathumela izithunywa ukuthi zimlandele ziyekuthi, ‘Kasimfuni lumuntu ukuthi abe yinkosi yethu.’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 19:15"/>
    <char style="wj">Lanxa kunjalo wagcotshwa waba yinkosi, waphenduka ekhaya. Wasebiza izinceku lezo ayezinike imali ukuze ezwe ukuthi zazithole nzuzo bani ngayo.</char><verse eid="LUK 19:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 19:16"/>
    <char style="wj">Owokuqala weza wathi, ‘Nkosi, imali yakho isizele amanye amadola alitshumi.’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 19:17"/>
    <char style="wj">Inkosi yayo yathi, ‘Wenze kuhle, nceku yami elungileyo! Ngenxa yokuthi uthembekile entweni encinyane, usuzabusa amadolobho alitshumi.’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 19:18"/>
    <char style="wj">Owesibili weza wathi, ‘Nkosi, imali yakho isizele amanye amadola amahlanu.’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 19:19"/>
    <char style="wj">Inkosi yayo yaphendula yathi, ‘Busa phezu kwamadolobho amahlanu.’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 19:20"/>
    <char style="wj">Kwasekusiza enye inceku yathi, ‘Nkosi, nansi imali yakho; bengiyigoqele ngelembu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 19:21"/><char style="wj">Bengikwesaba wena ngoba uyindoda elukhuni. Ucupha lapho ongathelanga khona njalo ubuye uvune lapho ongahlanyelanga khona.’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 19:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Inkosi yayo yaphendula yathi, ‘Ngizakwahlulela ngamazwi akho wena nceku exhwalileyo! Angithi ubukwazi ukuthi ngingumuntu olukhuni, ocupha lapho angathelanga khona lovuna lapho angahlanyelanga khona?</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 19:23"/><char style="wj">Kungani pho ungabekanga imali yami ebhanga ukuze kuthi ekubuyeni kwami ngiyithathe isilenzuzo na?’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 19:24"/>
    <char style="wj">Yasisithi kwababemi khonapho, ‘Mthatheleni lelo alalo liliphe lowo olalitshumi.’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 19:25"/>
    <char style="wj">Basebesithi, ‘Nkosi, angithi uvele uselalitshumi?’</char><verse eid="LUK 19:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 19:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Yaphendula yathi, ‘Ngithi kini, lowo olakho uzaphiwa okunye okunengi kodwa lowo ongelalutho, lalokho alakho uzakwemukwa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 19:27"/><char style="wj">Kodwa izitha zami lezo ebezingafuni ukuthi ngizibuse, ziletheni lapha lizibulalele phambi kwami.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 19:27"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukungena Ngobukhosi EJerusalema</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 19:28"/>UJesu esezitshilo zonke lezizinto wahamba wabandulela eqonda eJerusalema. <verse eid="LUK 19:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 19:29"/>Wathi esebanga eBhethifage kanye leBhethani entabeni eyayithiwa yiNtaba yama-Oliva wathuma abafundi bakhe ababili wathi kubo: <verse eid="LUK 19:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 19:30"/><char style="wj">“Yanini emzini ophambi kwenu, lizakuthi lingena kuwo libone inkonyane kababhemi ibotshelwe khonapho, engakaze igadwe muntu. ‘Ikhululeni liyilethe lapha.</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 19:31"/><char style="wj">Nxa kungaba lozalibuza ukuthi, Liyikhululelani na?’ kumele lithi, ‘INkosi iyayifuna.’ ”</char><verse eid="LUK 19:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 19:32"/>Labo ababethunyiwe bahamba njalo bathola kunjengoba ebetshilo. <verse eid="LUK 19:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 19:33"/>Besayikhulula inkonyane kababhemi, abanini bayo bababuza bathi, “Liyikhululelani na?”<verse eid="LUK 19:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 19:34"/>Baphendula bathi, “INkosi iyayifuna.”<verse eid="LUK 19:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 19:35"/>Bayiletha kuJesu, baphosela amajazi abo phezu kwenkonyane, bagadisa uJesu phezu kwayo. <verse eid="LUK 19:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 19:36"/>Wathi eseqhubeka, abantu bendlala amajazi abo endleleni.<verse eid="LUK 19:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 19:37"/>Esefikile eduze kwalapho indlela eyehla khona isuka eNtabeni yama-Oliva abafundi lexuku lonke lasuka ngokuthokoza ladumisa uNkulunkulu ngamazwi amakhulu ngenxa yemimangaliso yonke ababeyibonile, bathi:<verse eid="LUK 19:37"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 19:38"/>“Ibusisiwe inkosi ebuya ngebizo likaThixo!”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">19.38 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.26</char></note></para>
  <para style="b" vid="LUK 19:38"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 19:38">“Ukuthula ezulwini lodumo kweliphezulu!”<verse eid="LUK 19:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 19:39"/>Abanye abaFarisi exukwini bathi kuJesu, “Mfundisi, khuza abafundi bakho!”<verse eid="LUK 19:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 19:40"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyalitshela ngithi nxa bethula amatshe azamemeza.”</char><verse eid="LUK 19:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 19:41"/>Wathi esebanga eJerusalema ekhangele idolobho, walikhalela <verse eid="LUK 19:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 19:42"/>wathi, <char style="wj">“Nxa wena, wena ngokwakho, ubukwazi namhla lokho obekungakulethela ukuthula kodwa okwamanje kufihliwe emehlweni akho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 19:43"/><char style="wj">Zizafika insuku kuwe lapho izitha zakho zizakwakha umthangala zikuhonqolozele njalo zikuphahle inxa zonke.</char> <verse eid="LUK 19:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 19:44"/><char style="wj">Zizakusakazela phansi emhlabathini, wena kanye labantwana abaphakathi kwemiduli yakho. Kaziyikutshiya lalinye ilitshe phezu kwelinye ngoba kawusinanzelelanga isikhathi sokuza kukaNkulunkulu kuwe.”</char><verse eid="LUK 19:44"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu EThempelini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 19:45"/>Wasengena ethempelini wadudula ababethengisa khona <verse eid="LUK 19:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 19:46"/>esithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kubhaliwe ukuthi, ‘Indlu yami iyindlu yokukhuleka,’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">19.46 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 56.7</char></note> <char style="wj">kodwa lina seliyenze ubhalu lwabaphangi.”</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">19.46 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJeremiya 7.11</char></note><verse eid="LUK 19:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 19:47"/>Insuku zonke wayefundisa ethempelini. Kodwa abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho kanye labakhokheli ababephakathi kwabantu babezama ukumbulala. <verse eid="LUK 19:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 19:48"/>Kodwa kabayizuzanga indlela yokukwenza lokho ngoba abantu bonke babewakholwa amazwi akhe.<verse eid="LUK 19:48"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="LUK 20"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthandabuza Ngamandla KaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 20:1"/>Ngelinye ilanga kwathi efundisa abantu ethempelini, etshumayela ivangeli, abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho, kanye labadala bebandla beza kuye. <verse eid="LUK 20:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 20:2"/>Bathi, “Ake usitshele ukuthi uwathatha ngaphi amandla okwenza lezizinto. Ngubani okunike amandla la?”<verse eid="LUK 20:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 20:3"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lami ngizalibuza umbuzo. Ngitshelani,</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 20:4"/><char style="wj">ukubhaphathiza kukaJohane kwakuvela ezulwini loba ebantwini na?”</char><verse eid="LUK 20:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 20:5"/>Bahlanganisa amakhanda bathi, “Singathi, ‘Kwakuvela ezulwini,’ uzabuza athi, ‘Kungani lingazange limkholwe?’ <verse eid="LUK 20:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 20:6"/>Kodwa singathi, ‘Kwakuvela ebantwini,’ abantu bonke bazasikhanda ngamatshe ngoba bakholwa ukuthi uJohane wayengumphrofethi.”<verse eid="LUK 20:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 20:7"/>Ngakho baphendula bathi, “Kasikwazi ukuthi kwakuvela ngaphi.”<verse eid="LUK 20:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 20:8"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Lami kangizukulitshela ukuthi lezizinto ngizenza ngawaphi amandla.”</char><verse eid="LUK 20:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wabalimi Besivini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 20:9"/>Waseqhubeka ngokutshela abantu umzekeliso lo wathi: <char style="wj">“Indoda yahlanyela isivini yasiqhatshisa abanye abalimi, yasihamba okwesikhathi eside.</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 20:10"/><char style="wj">Ngesikhathi sokuvuna yathuma inceku yayo kubaqhatshi besivini ukuze bayiphe ingxenye yezithelo zesivini. Kodwa abalimi bayitshaya, bayixotsha ingaphathanga lutho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 20:11"/><char style="wj">Yathuma enye inceku kodwa laleyo bayitshaya bayiphatha kabuhlungu, bayixotsha ingaphathanga lutho.</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 20:12"/><char style="wj">Waphinda wathuma eyesithathu, bayilimaza bayiphosela phandle.</char><verse eid="LUK 20:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 20:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Umninisivini wasesithi, ‘Ngenzeni? Ngizathuma indodana yami engiyithandayo; mhlawumbe bazayihlonipha.’</char><verse eid="LUK 20:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 20:14"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa kwathi abaqhatshi besivini beyibona, bahlanganisa amakhanda ngaleyondaba. Bathi, ‘Le yindlalifa. Kasiyibulaleni, ilifa libe ngelethu.’</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 20:15"/><char style="wj">Basebeyikhuphela ngaphandle kwesivini, bayibulala.</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 20:15">
    <char style="wj">Kambe umninisivini uzabathini?</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 20:16"/><char style="wj">Uzakuza afike ababulale labo baqhatshi besivini, isivini leso asinike abanye abalimi.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 20:16">Abantu bathi bekuzwa lokhu bathi, “Sengathi lokhu kungaze kwafa kwenzeka!”<verse eid="LUK 20:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 20:17"/>UJesu wabathi nhlo, wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Pho kutshoni lokho okubhalwe ukuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 20:17">
    <char style="wj">‘Ilitshe elalahlwa ngabakhi</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 20:17">
    <char style="wj">seliyilona ilitshe lekhoneni?’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">20.17 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.22</char>
    </note><verse eid="LUK 20:17"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 20:18"/>
    <char style="wj">Wonke owela phezu kwalelolitshe uzachobozeka abe yizicucu, kodwa lowo eliwela phezu kwakhe uzahlifizwa.”</char><verse eid="LUK 20:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 20:19"/>Abafundisi bomthetho labaphristi abakhulu badinga indlela yokumbopha masinyane ngoba babesazi ukuthi wakhuluma umzekeliso lo eqonde bona. Kodwa babesesaba abantu.<verse eid="LUK 20:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthela KuKhesari</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 20:20"/>Bamthumela inhloli ezazizitshaya ezithembekileyo ukuze zimgolombe. Babefisa ukumbeka icala kokunye ayengakukhuluma ukuze bamedlulisele emandleni ombusi. <verse eid="LUK 20:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 20:21"/>Ngakho inhloli zambuza zathi, “Mfundisi, siyazi ukuthi wena ukhuluma njalo ufundisa okuqondileyo lokuthi kawubandlululi kodwa ufundisa indlela kaNkulunkulu ngeqiniso elipheleleyo. <verse eid="LUK 20:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 20:22"/>Kufanele yini ukuthi sithele imithelo kuKhesari loba hatshi?”<verse eid="LUK 20:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 20:23"/>Wabubona ubuqili babo wathi kubo, <verse eid="LUK 20:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 20:24"/><char style="wj">“Ngitshengisani idenari. Kulomfanekiso kabani lombhalo kabani kuyo?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 20:24">Baphendula bathi, “NgokaKhesari.”<verse eid="LUK 20:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 20:25"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngakho nikani uKhesari okungokukaKhesari, linike uNkulunkulu okungokukaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 20:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 20:26"/>Behluleka ukumbamba ngalokho akutshoyo lapho obala. Sebemangaliswe yimpendulo yakhe bathula zwi.<verse eid="LUK 20:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuvuka Kwabafileyo Lokwendiselana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 20:27"/>Amanye amaSadusi athi kakukho ukuvuka kwabafileyo eza kuJesu elombuzo. <verse eid="LUK 20:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 20:28"/>Athi, “Mfundisi, uMosi wasibhalela ukuthi nxa umfowabo wendoda angafa atshiye umfazi, kodwa bengelabantwana, umfowabo kumele amngene umfelokazi ukuze azalele umfowabo abantwana. <verse eid="LUK 20:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 20:29"/>Manje kwakulabafowabo abayisikhombisa. Owokuqala wathatha umfazi kodwa wafa engelamntwana. <verse eid="LUK 20:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 20:30"/>Owesibili <verse eid="LUK 20:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 20:31"/>njalo lowesithathu laye wamthatha, bonke boyisikhombisa benza njalo bafa bengatshiyanga bantwana. <verse eid="LUK 20:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 20:32"/>Ekucineni umfazi laye wafa. <verse eid="LUK 20:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 20:33"/>Pho-ke, ekuvukeni kwabafileyo uzakuba ngumkabani njengoba bonke boyisikhombisa babemthethe?”<verse eid="LUK 20:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 20:34"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Abantu balesisikhathi bayathatha njalo bayendiswa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 20:35"/><char style="wj">Kodwa labo abazabe befanele ukuba lengxenye kulesosikhathi lasekuvukeni kwabafileyo kabazukuthatha loba bendiswe,</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 20:36"/><char style="wj">njalo kabasayikufa ngoba sebenjengezingilosi. Bangabantwana bakaNkulunkulu, ngoba bengabantwana bokuvuka kwabafileyo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 20:37"/><char style="wj">Kodwa emlandweni wesixuku esasibhebha umlilo, uMosi laye wakuveza ukuthi abafileyo bayavuka, ngoba ubiza uThixo ngokuthi ‘uNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, uNkulunkulu ka-Isaka, loNkulunkulu kaJakhobe.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">20.37 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 3.6</char></note> <verse eid="LUK 20:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 20:38"/><char style="wj">KasuNkulunkulu wabafileyo, kodwa owabaphilayo, ngoba kuye bonke bayaphila.”</char><verse eid="LUK 20:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 20:39"/>Baphendula abanye abafundisi bomthetho bathi, “Utsho kahle Mfundisi!” <verse eid="LUK 20:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 20:40"/>Kasabanga khona owaba lesibindi sokumbuza eminye imibuzo.<verse eid="LUK 20:40"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UKhristu UyiNdodana Kabani Na?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 20:41"/>UJesu wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kungani besithi uKhristu uyiNdodana kaDavida na?</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 20:42"/><char style="wj">UDavida yena ngokwakhe uyakufakaza eNcwadini yamaHubo uthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 20:42">
    <char style="wj">‘INkosi yathi eNkosini yami:</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 20:42">
    <char style="wj">“Hlala ngakwesokunene sami,</char><verse eid="LUK 20:42"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 20:43"/>
    <char style="wj">ngize ngenze izitha zakho</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 20:43">
    <char style="wj">zibe yisinyathelo senyawo zakho.”</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">20.43 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 110.1</char>
    </note>
    <char style="wj">’</char><verse eid="LUK 20:43"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 20:44"/>
    <char style="wj">UDavida umbiza athi ‘Nkosi.’ Pho angaba yindodana yakhe njani?”</char><verse eid="LUK 20:44"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Iseluleko Ngabafundisi Bomthetho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 20:45"/>Kwathi bonke abantu besalalele, uJesu wathi kubafundi bakhe, <verse eid="LUK 20:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 20:46"/><char style="wj">“Limukani abafundisi bomthetho. Bathanda ukuhambahamba becece ngezembatho ezinde eziphephezelayo njalo bathanda ukubingelelwa emisikeni, futhi bathatha izihlalo eziphakemeyo emasinagogweni lezindawo zabahlonitshwa emadilini.</char> <verse eid="LUK 20:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 20:47"/><char style="wj">Bahuquluza izindlu zabafelokazi njalo bazibonakalisa ngokwenza imikhuleko emide. Abantu abanjalo bazajeziswa kabuhlungu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 20:47"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="LUK 21"/>
  <para style="s1">Umnikelo Womfelokazi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 21:1"/>UJesu wathi ekhangela wabona izinothi zifaka iminikelo yazo esitsheni somnikelo. <verse eid="LUK 21:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 21:2"/>Wabona njalo umfelokazi ongumyanga efaka okuzinhlamvana kwethusi okubili. <verse eid="LUK 21:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 21:3"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ngithi umfelokazi lo ongumyanga unikele okudlula bonke abanye.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 21:4"/><char style="wj">Bonke lababantu banikele izipho zabo ngokwenotho yabo, kodwa yena ebuyangeni bakhe ufake konke abelakho.”</char><verse eid="LUK 21:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubhidlizwa KweThempeli Lezibonakaliso Zokucina Kwesikhathi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 21:5"/>Abanye abafundi bakhe babekhulukhuluma ngokubalazwa kwethempeli ngamatshe amahle langezipho ezazinikelwe kuNkulunkulu. Kodwa uJesu wathi, <verse eid="LUK 21:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 21:6"/><char style="wj">“Mayelana lalokhu elikubona lapha, sizafika isikhathi lapho okungeyikutshiywa ilitshe phezu kwelinye; wonke azaphoselwa phansi.”</char><verse eid="LUK 21:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 21:7"/>Babuza bathi, “Mfundisi, izinto lezi zizakwenzakala nini? Njalo sizakuba yini isibonakaliso sokuthi sezizakwenzeka na?”<verse eid="LUK 21:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 21:8"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Qaphelani lingakhohliswa. Ngoba abanengi bazakuza ngebizo lami besithi, ‘Nginguye,’ njalo bathi, ‘Isikhathi sesisondele.’ Lingabalandeli.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 21:9"/><char style="wj">Nxa lisizwa ngezimpi lezikhukhulambuso, lingethuki. Lezizinto kuzamele zenzeke kuqala, kodwa isiphetho kasizukufika ngalesosikhathi.”</char><verse eid="LUK 21:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 21:10"/>Wasesithi kubo: <char style="wj">“Isizwe sizavukela isizwe, lombuso uvukele umbuso.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 21:11"/><char style="wj">Kuzakuba lokuzamazama komhlaba okukhulu, indlala lezifo ezindaweni ezinengi, izehlakalo ezesabekayo lezibonakaliso ezinengi zivela emkhathini.</char><verse eid="LUK 21:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 21:12"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa kungakenzakali konke lokhu bazalibamba, balihlukuluze. Bazalinikela emasinagogweni baliphosele lasezintolongweni njalo lizamiswa phambi kwamakhosi lababusi ngenxa yebizo lami.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 21:13"/><char style="wj">Lokhu kuzalenza libe ngofakazi kimi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 21:14"/><char style="wj">Kodwa bekani amaphaphu phansi, lingazihluphi ngokuthi lizazivikela lisithini.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 21:15"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngizalinika amazwi lokuhlakanipha ukuze angabikhona ezitheni zenu ozalehlula loba aliphikise.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 21:16"/><char style="wj">Lizanikelwa ngabazali, ngabafowenu layizihlobo labangane njalo abanye benu bazalibulala.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 21:17"/><char style="wj">Bonke abantu bazalizonda ngenxa yami.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 21:18"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kakuyikubhubha lanwele olulodwa emakhanda enu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 21:19"/><char style="wj">Bekezelani, lizasindiswa.</char><verse eid="LUK 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 21:20"/>
    <char style="wj">Lingabona iJerusalema isihonqolozelwe yizimpi lizakwazi ukuthi incithakalo isisondele.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 21:21"/><char style="wj">Lapho-ke akuthi labo abaseJudiya babalekele ezintabeni, abasedolobheni kabaphume, kuthi labo abasemaphandleni bangangeni edolobheni.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 21:22"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lesi yisikhathi sokujeziswa ukugcwalisa konke okwalotshwayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 21:23"/><char style="wj">Yeka ubulukhuni obuzakuba khona ngalezonsuku kwabesifazane abakhulelweyo labangabadlezane! Kuzakuba khona ukuhlukuluzeka okukhulu elizweni lolaka phezu kwabantu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 21:24"/><char style="wj">Bazakuwa ngenkemba babuthwe babe yizibotshwa zezizwe zonke. IJerusalema izagidagidwa ngabeZizwe kuze kugcwaliseke izikhathi zabeZizwe.</char><verse eid="LUK 21:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 21:25"/>
    <char style="wj">Kuzabakhona izibonakaliso elangeni, enyangeni lasezinkanyezini. Emhlabeni izizwe zizakuba phakathi kosizi lokudideka ngenxa yokuhuba lokukhaphaza kolwandle.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 21:26"/><char style="wj">Abantu bazaphela amandla ngokwesaba, behlutshwa yilokho okuzayo emhlabeni, ngoba izisekelo zasezulwini zizazanyazanyiswa.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 21:27"/><char style="wj">Ngalesosikhathi bazayibona iNdodana yoMuntu isiza ngeyezi ilamandla lenkazimulo enkulu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 21:28"/><char style="wj">Nxa lezizinto seziqala ukwenzakala manini liqine, liphakamise amakhanda enu, ngoba ukuhlengwa kwenu sekusondela.”</char><verse eid="LUK 21:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 21:29"/>Wabatshela umfanekiso lo wathi, <char style="wj">“Khangelani esihlahleni somkhiwa kanye lezinye zonke izihlahla.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 21:30"/><char style="wj">Nxa zihluma lizazibonela lani njalo lazi ukuthi ihlobo selisondele.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 21:31"/><char style="wj">Kanjalo-ke, nxa lingabona lezizinto sezisenzakala, lazi ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu ususondele.</char><verse eid="LUK 21:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 21:32"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, lesisizukulwane kasiyikudlula zize zenzakale zonke lezizinto.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 21:33"/><char style="wj">Izulu lomhlaba kuzedlula, kodwa amazwi ami kawayikwedlula lanini.</char><verse eid="LUK 21:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 21:34"/>
    <char style="wj">Nanzelelani funa inhliziyo zenu zithundubale ngokuzitika lokudakwa lokunqineka ngezinto zalimpilo, ngoba lolosuku luzalijuma njengomjibila.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 21:35"/><char style="wj">Ngoba luzafikela bonke labo abahlala kuwo wonke umhlaba.</char> <verse eid="LUK 21:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 21:36"/><char style="wj">Hlalani lilindile, likhulekele ukuthi liphephe kukho konke osekuzakwenzeka masinyane, lokuthi libe lamandla okuma phambi kweNdodana yoMuntu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 21:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 21:37"/>Insuku zonke uJesu wayefundisa ethempelini kuthi kusihlwa aphume ayechitha ubusuku eqaqeni olwaluthiwa yiNtaba yama-Oliva, <verse eid="LUK 21:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 21:38"/>njalo abantu bonke babesiza ekuseni kakhulu ukuzamuzwa ethempelini.<verse eid="LUK 21:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="LUK 22"/>
  <para style="s1">UJudasi Uvuma Ukunikela UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 22:1"/>UMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo owawubizwa ngokuthi liPhasika wawususondele, <verse eid="LUK 22:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 22:2"/>njalo abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho babedinga enye indlela yokumsusa uJesu, ngoba babesesaba abantu. <verse eid="LUK 22:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 22:3"/>USathane wasengena kuJudasi owayethiwa ngu-Iskariyothi, omunye wabalitshumi lambili. <verse eid="LUK 22:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 22:4"/>UJudasi waya kubaphristi abakhulu lezikhulu zabavikeli bethempeli wabonisana labo ukuthi amnikele njani uJesu. <verse eid="LUK 22:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 22:5"/>Bathokoza kakhulu, basebevuma ukumupha imali. <verse eid="LUK 22:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 22:6"/>Wavuma, wasemelela ithuba lokunikela uJesu kubo ngesikhathi kungelaxuku labantu.<verse eid="LUK 22:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isidlo Sokucina</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 22:7"/>Lwaselufika usuku lweSinkwa esingelaMvubelo okwakusenziwa ngalo umhlatshelo wewundlu lePhasika. <verse eid="LUK 22:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 22:8"/>UJesu wathuma uPhethro loJohane wathi, <char style="wj">“Hambani liyesilungisela ukuthi siyekudla iPhasika.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 22:9"/>Babuza bathi, “Ufuna siyelilungisela ngaphi?”<verse eid="LUK 22:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 22:10"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lizakuthi nje lingena edolobheni, lizahlangana lendoda iphethe inkonxa yamanzi. Liyilandele kuleyondlu ezangena kuyo,</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 22:11"/><char style="wj">beselisithi kumninindlu, ‘Umfundisi uyabuza uthi: Ingaphi indlu yezethekeli, lapho engingadlela khona iPhasika labafundi bami?’</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 22:12"/><char style="wj">Izalitshengisa ikamelo laphezulu elikhulu, elilungisiweyo. Yenzani amalungiselo khonapho.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 22:13"/>Bahamba bayafica izinto zimi njengokutshelwa kwabo nguJesu. Ngakho balilungisa iPhasika.<verse eid="LUK 22:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 22:14"/>Kwathi isikhathi sesifikile uJesu wahlala etafuleni labapostoli bakhe. <verse eid="LUK 22:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 22:15"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Bengitshiseka kakhulu ukudla iPhasika leli lani ngingakahlupheki.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 22:16"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngiyalitshela ukuthi kangisoze ngiphinde ngilidle njalo lize lizuze ukugcwaliseka embusweni kaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 22:17"/>Esethethe inkezo wabonga wasesithi, <char style="wj">“Kuthatheni lokhu likwabelane.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 22:18"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngiyalitshela ukuthi angiyikuphinda nginathe okwesithelo sevini umbuso kaNkulunkulu uze ufike.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 22:19"/>Wasethatha isinkwa, wabonga wasesihlephuna wabapha, wathi, <char style="wj">“Lo ngumzimba wami ophiwe lina; kwenzeni lokhu kube yisikhumbuzo sami.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 22:20"/>Ngaleyondlela, ngemva kokudla kwakusihlwa wathatha inkezo, esithi, <char style="wj">“Inkezo le iyisivumelwano esitsha egazini lami, elichithelwa lina.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 22:21"/><char style="wj">Kodwa isandla sakhe lowo ozanginikela sikanye lesami etafuleni.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 22:22"/><char style="wj">INdodana yoMuntu izahamba njengoba kumisiwe, kodwa maye kulowomuntu oyinikelayo.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 22:23"/>Baqala ukubuzana ukuthi kambe ngabe ngubani kubo owayezakwenza lokhu.<verse eid="LUK 22:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 22:24"/>Njalo kwaba lokuphikisana phakathi kwabo mayelana lokuthi ngubani kubo owayebonakala emkhulu kulabo bonke. <verse eid="LUK 22:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 22:25"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Amakhosi abeZizwe azitshengisela amandla awo kulabo ababusayo; leziphathamandla zakhona zibizwa ngokuthi Mcoli.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 22:26"/><char style="wj">Kodwa akumelanga libe njalo. Endaweni yalokho, lowo omkhulu kulani lonke kabe njengomncinyane kini lonke, lalowo obusayo abe nguye okhonza abanye.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 22:27"/><char style="wj">Kambe ngubani omkhulu kulomunye, lowo ohlezi etafuleni yokudla loba lowo ophakayo na? Kakusilowo osetafuleni na? Kodwa mina ngiphakathi kwenu njengalowo oliphakelayo.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 22:28"/><char style="wj">Liyilabo abame lami ebunzimeni bami.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 22:29"/><char style="wj">Ngakho ngiyalinika umbuso njengoba uBaba wanginika lami,</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 22:30"/><char style="wj">ukuze lidle njalo linathe etafuleni lami embusweni wami njalo lihlale ezihlalweni zobukhosi, lisahlulela izizwana zika-Israyeli ezilitshumi lambili.</char><verse eid="LUK 22:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 22:31"/>
    <char style="wj">Simoni, Simoni uSathane usecele ukulihlungula lonke njengengqoloyi.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 22:32"/><char style="wj">Kodwa sengikukhulekele wena Simoni, ukuthi ukholo lwakho lungaze lwawela phansi. Ubokuthi nxa usuphendukile uqinise abafowenu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 22:33"/>Kodwa waphendula wathi, “Nkosi, ngizimisele ukuhamba lawe entolongweni lasekufeni.”<verse eid="LUK 22:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 22:34"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyakutshela, Phethro, ukuthi iqhude lingakakhali lamuhla, uzaphika kathathu ukuthi uyangazi.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 22:35"/>UJesu wasebabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngize ngilithume lingelamxhaka, loba isikhwama kumbe amanyathela, kukhona yini elake lakusilela?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 22:35">Baphendula bathi, “Akubanga lalutho.”<verse eid="LUK 22:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 22:36"/>Wathi, kubo, <char style="wj">“Kodwa manje nxa ulesikhwama semali, sithathe, kanye lomgodla; njalo nxa ungelankemba, thengisa isigqoko sakho uyithenge.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 22:37"/><char style="wj">Kulotshiwe ukuthi, ‘Wabalwa ndawonye lezoni’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">22.37 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 53.12</char></note><char style="wj">; njalo ngiyalitshela ukuthi lokhu kumele kugcwaliseke kimi. Yebo, lokho okubhaliweyo ngami sekufika ekugcwalisweni kwakho.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 22:38"/>Abafundi bathi, “Khangela, Nkosi, nanzi inkemba ezimbili.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 22:38">Waphendula uJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Kwanele.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:38"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhuleka ENtabeni Yama-Oliva</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 22:39"/>UJesu wahamba njengenjayelo waya eNtabeni yama-Oliva, abafundi bakhe bamlandela. <verse eid="LUK 22:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 22:40"/>Esefikile kuleyondawo, wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Khulekani ukuze lingaweli ekulingweni.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 22:41"/>Watsheda kubo okwebanga lokuphosa ilitshe, waguqa phansi wakhuleka wathi, <verse eid="LUK 22:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 22:42"/><char style="wj">“Baba, nxa uthanda susa inkezo le kimi; kodwa akungabi yintando yami, kodwa kwenziwe eyakho.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 22:43"/>Ingilosi yabonakala kuye ivela ezulwini yamqinisa. <verse eid="LUK 22:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 22:44"/>Kwathi edabukile kakhulu, wakhuleka ngokutshiseka, izithukuthuku zakhe zangathi ligazi lithontela phansi.<verse eid="LUK 22:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 22:45"/>Wathi esephakeme ekukhulekeni wabuyela kubafundi bakhe wabafica belele, bekhathele ngenxa yosizi. <verse eid="LUK 22:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 22:46"/>Wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungani lilele na? Vukani likhuleke ukuze lingaweli ekulingweni.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:46"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uyabotshwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 22:47"/>Kwathi elokhu esakhuluma kwafika ixuku labantu, indoda ethiwa nguJudasi omunye wabalitshumi lambili, wayebahola. Wasondela kuJesu ukumanga, <verse eid="LUK 22:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 22:48"/>kodwa uJesu wambuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Judasi, uyayinikela na iNdodana yoMuntu ngokuyanga?”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 22:49"/>Kwathi abalandeli bakaJesu sebebona okwasekuzakwenzeka bathi, “Nkosi, sigalele yini ngenkemba zethu?” <verse eid="LUK 22:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 22:50"/>Omunye wabo wayigalela inceku yomphristi omkhulu, wayiquma indlebe yayo yokunene.<verse eid="LUK 22:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 22:51"/>Kodwa uJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kakufuneki lokhu!”</char> Waseyibamba indlebe yalowomuntu wamsilisa.<verse eid="LUK 22:51"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 22:52"/>UJesu wasesithi kubaphristi abakhulu, lezikhulu zabalindi bethempeli kanye labadala bebandla ababemlandile, <char style="wj">“Ngikhokhela umvukela yini lize liphethe izinkemba lenduku?</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="LUK 22:53"/><char style="wj">Zonke insuku bengilani emagumeni ethempeli, kodwa kalizange lingithinte. Kodwa lesi yisikhathi senu, lapho kubusa umnyama.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:53"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro Ulandula UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v" sid="LUK 22:54"/>Bamdumela, bamusa endlini yomphristi omkhulu. UPhethro wayemlandela ebucwala. <verse eid="LUK 22:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="LUK 22:55"/>Kodwa kwathi sebebase umlilo phakathi kweguma bahlala phansi ndawonye, uPhethro wahlala phansi labo. <verse eid="LUK 22:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="LUK 22:56"/>Intombazana eyisisebenzi yambona ehlezi khonapho ekukhanyeni komlilo. Yamkhangelisisa yathi, “Indoda le yayilaye.”<verse eid="LUK 22:56"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="LUK 22:57"/>Kodwa yena waphika wathi, “Ntombazana, kangimazi.”<verse eid="LUK 22:57"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="58" style="v" sid="LUK 22:58"/>Ngemva kwesikhatshana omunye wambona wathi, “Lawe ungomunye wabo.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 22:58">UPhethro waphendula wathi, “Ndoda, angisuye.”<verse eid="LUK 22:58"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="59" style="v" sid="LUK 22:59"/>Sekudlule phose ihola omunye wagcizelela wathi, “Ngeqiniso umuntu lo wayelaye, ngoba ungumGalile.”<verse eid="LUK 22:59"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="60" style="v" sid="LUK 22:60"/>Waphendula uPhethro wathi, “Ndoda, angikwazi okhuluma ngakho!” Elokhu esakhuluma, iqhude lakhala. <verse eid="LUK 22:60"/><verse number="61" style="v" sid="LUK 22:61"/>INkosi yatshibilika, yamkhangela yamuthi nhlo uPhethro. UPhethro waselikhumbula ilizwi iNkosi eyayilikhulumile kuye isithi: <char style="wj">“Iqhude lingakakhali lamuhla, uzangiphika kathathu.”</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:61"/><verse number="62" style="v" sid="LUK 22:62"/>Ngakho wasephumela ngaphandle wakhala kabuhlungu.<verse eid="LUK 22:62"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amabutho Ahoza UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="63" style="v" sid="LUK 22:63"/>Amadoda ayelinde uJesu aqalisa ukumhoza lokumtshaya. <verse eid="LUK 22:63"/><verse number="64" style="v" sid="LUK 22:64"/>Amvala amehlo athi kuye, “Phrofitha! Ngubani okutshayileyo?” <verse eid="LUK 22:64"/><verse number="65" style="v" sid="LUK 22:65"/>Amthuka ngezindlela ezinengi.<verse eid="LUK 22:65"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Phambi KukaPhilathu LoHerodi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="66" style="v" sid="LUK 22:66"/>Emadabukakusa inkundla yabakhokheli babantu, kanye labaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho yahlangana ndawonye, uJesu walethwa phambi kwabo. <verse eid="LUK 22:66"/><verse number="67" style="v" sid="LUK 22:67"/>Bathi, “Nxa unguKhristu sitshele.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 22:67">UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngingaze ngilitshele kalisoze lingikholwe,</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:67"/><verse number="68" style="v" sid="LUK 22:68"/><char style="wj">njalo nxa bengingalibuza belingeke liphendule.</char> <verse eid="LUK 22:68"/><verse number="69" style="v" sid="LUK 22:69"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kusukela khathesi iNdodana yoMuntu izahlala kwesokunene sikaNkulunkulu olamandla amakhulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:69"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="70" style="v" sid="LUK 22:70"/>Bonke babuza bathi, “Kutsho ukuthi-ke uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 22:70">Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Liqondile ukuthi ngiyiyo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 22:70"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="71" style="v" sid="LUK 22:71"/>Basebesithi, “Sisabudingelani obunye ubufakazi na? Sesikuzwe kuphuma kowakhe umlomo.”<verse eid="LUK 22:71"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="LUK 23"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 23:1"/>Ibandla lonke laseliphakama lamqhuba lamusa kuPhilathu. <verse eid="LUK 23:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 23:2"/>Basebemethesa icala besithi, “Indoda le siyifice ixhwalisa isizwe sakithi. Iphikisana lokuthela imithelo kuKhesari njalo izenza uKhristu, inkosi.”<verse eid="LUK 23:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 23:3"/>Ngakho uPhilathu wasembuza uJesu wathi, “Uyinkosi yamaJuda na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 23:3">
    <char style="wj">“Kunjengoba usitsho,”</char> waphendula uJesu.<verse eid="LUK 23:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 23:4"/>UPhilathu wasebikela abaphristi abakhulu kanye lexuku labantu wathi, “Kangiboni lutho lokwethesa umuntu lo icala.”<verse eid="LUK 23:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 23:5"/>Kodwa bagcizelela bathi, “Udunga abantu kulolonke elaseJudiya ngemfundiso yakhe. Waqalisa eGalile, usehambe wonke umango waze wazafika lapha.”<verse eid="LUK 23:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 23:6"/>Esezwe lokhu uPhilathu wabuza ingabe indoda leyo yayingumGalile na. <verse eid="LUK 23:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 23:7"/>Esezwile ukuthi uJesu wayengaphansi kombuso kaHerodi wamthumela kuHerodi owayeseJerusalema ngalesosikhathi.<verse eid="LUK 23:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 23:8"/>UHerodi wathi embona uJesu wathaba kakhulu ngoba wayevele etshisekela ukumbona. Ethathela kulokho ayekuzwile ngaye, wayelindele ukumbona esenza omunye umangaliso. <verse eid="LUK 23:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 23:9"/>Wamjinga ngemibuzo, kodwa uJesu akaze amphendula. <verse eid="LUK 23:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 23:10"/>Abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho labo babemi khonapho bemangalela ngokuthukuthela. <verse eid="LUK 23:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 23:11"/>UHerodi lamabutho akhe basebemchothoza njalo bamhoza. Bamgqokisa isigqoko esihle, basebembuyisela kuPhilathu. <verse eid="LUK 23:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 23:12"/>Ngalelolanga uHerodi loPhilathu babangabangane kodwa mandulo kwalokhu babeyizitha.<verse eid="LUK 23:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 23:13"/>UPhilathu wabizela ndawonye abaphristi abakhulu lababusi kanye labantu <verse eid="LUK 23:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 23:14"/>wathi kubo, “Lingilethele umuntu obekhuthaza abantu ukwenza umvukela. Sengimhlolile phambi kwenu, kodwa kangifumananga lutho kulokhu elimangalela khona. <verse eid="LUK 23:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 23:15"/>LoHerodi kafumananga lutho, ngoba usemphendukisile kithi; njengoba libona, kenzanga lutho olufanele ukuthi abulawe. <verse eid="LUK 23:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 23:16"/>Ngakho ngizamjezisa nje besengimkhulula.” [ <verse eid="LUK 23:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 23:17"/>Kwakumele akhulule isibotshwa esisodwa esiyabe sikhethwe ngabantu mhla wedili.]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">23.17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi kayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="LUK 23:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 23:18"/>Bamemeza ngalizwi linye bathi, “Msusele khatshana umuntu lo! Sikhululele uBharabhasi!” <verse eid="LUK 23:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 23:19"/>(UBharabhasi wayephoselwe entolongweni ngenxa yokuvusa isiphithiphithi edolobheni langenxa yokubulala.)<verse eid="LUK 23:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 23:20"/>Kwathi ngoba efuna ukumkhulula uJesu, uPhilathu waphinda wathi kabake bacabange njalo. <verse eid="LUK 23:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 23:21"/>Kodwa baqhubeka bememeza besithi, “Mbethele! Mbethele!”<verse eid="LUK 23:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 23:22"/>Waphinda wakhuluma labo okwesithathu wathi, “Ngani na? Umuntu lo wenze cala bani? Angiboni lutho kuye olungafanela isigwebo sokuthi abulawe. Ngakho-ke, ngizakuthi kajeziswe besengimkhulula.”<verse eid="LUK 23:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 23:23"/>Kodwa baklabalala beqinisa ukuba kabethelwe, lakanye ukugcizelela kwabo kwaphumelela. <verse eid="LUK 23:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 23:24"/>Ngakho uPhilathu wasemisa ukwemukela izifiso zabo. <verse eid="LUK 23:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 23:25"/>Wayikhulula indoda leyo eyayiphoselwe entolongweni ngenxa yesiphithiphithi lokubulala, eyiyo abayicelayo, wanikela uJesu kubo ukuthi benze intando yabo.<verse eid="LUK 23:25"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubethelwa Esiphambanweni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 23:26"/>Bathi sebemqhuba babamba uSimoni waseKhureni owayesuka emaphandleni, bamethesa isiphambano bathi kasithwale ngemva kukaJesu. <verse eid="LUK 23:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 23:27"/>Walandelwa ngabantu abanengi kakhulu, kanye labesifazane ababemkhalela bebubula. <verse eid="LUK 23:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 23:28"/>UJesu wanyemukula wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Madodakazi aseJerusalema, lingangikhaleli; zikhaleleni lina kanye labantwabenu.</char> <verse eid="LUK 23:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 23:29"/><char style="wj">Ngoba sizafika isikhathi lapho elizakuthi, ‘Babusisiwe abafazi abazinyumba, lezibeletho ezingazange zithwale kanye lamabele angazange amunyise!’</char> <verse eid="LUK 23:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 23:30"/><char style="wj">Lapho-ke</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="LUK 23:30">
    <char style="wj">‘bazakuthi ezintabeni, “Sembeseni!”</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">23.30 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UHosiya 10.8</char>
    </note></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="LUK 23:30">
    <char style="wj">Lakuwo amaqaqa bathi, “Welani phezu kwethu!” ’</char><verse eid="LUK 23:30"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 23:31"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngoba nxa abantu bezenza lezizinto lapho isihlahla simanzi, kuzakwenzakalani pho nxa sesomile?”</char><verse eid="LUK 23:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 23:32"/>Amanye amadoda amabili, onke ayeyizigebenga, lawo aqhutshwa kanye laye esiyabulawa. <verse eid="LUK 23:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 23:33"/>Bathi sebefike endaweni ethiwa luKhakhayi bambethela esiphambanweni kanye lezigebenga lezo, omunye ngakwesokunene kwakhe, omunye ngakwesokhohlo. <verse eid="LUK 23:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 23:34"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Baba, baxolele, ngoba kabakwazi abakwenzayo.”</char> Njalo basebesabelana izigqoko zakhe ngokutshaya inkatho.<verse eid="LUK 23:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 23:35"/>Abantu bema bakhangela, ababusi bona bamklolodela. Bathi, “Wasindisa abanye, laye kazisindise nxa enguKhristu kaNkulunkulu, oKhethiweyo.”<verse eid="LUK 23:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 23:36"/>Amabutho lawo eza amklolodela. Amnika iwayini elimunyu <verse eid="LUK 23:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 23:37"/>athi, “Nxa uyinkosi yamaJuda, zisindise.”<verse eid="LUK 23:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 23:38"/>Kwakulombhalo wokwazisa ngaphezulu kwakhe owawusithi:</para>
  <para style="pc" vid="LUK 23:38">Lo yiNkosi yamaJuda.<verse eid="LUK 23:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 23:39"/>Omunye wezigebenga owayelenga khonapho wamthuka wathi, “Kanti kayisuwe uKhristu? Zisindise wena kanye lathi!”<verse eid="LUK 23:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 23:40"/>Kodwa esinye isigebenga samkhuza sathi, “Kawumesabi na uNkulunkulu, njengoba ulesigwebo sinye laye. <verse eid="LUK 23:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 23:41"/>Thina sijeziswa ngokusifaneleyo ngoba sizuza lokho okufanele izenzo zethu. Kodwa umuntu lo kenzanga lutho olungalunganga.”<verse eid="LUK 23:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 23:42"/>Wasesithi, “Jesu, ungikhumbule nxa ungafika embusweni wakho.”<verse eid="LUK 23:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 23:43"/>UJesu wamphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyakutshela iqiniso ngithi, lamuhla uzakuba lami epharadise.”</char><verse eid="LUK 23:43"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukufa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 23:44"/>Kwasekuyisikhathi esingaba lihola lesithupha, ubumnyama bembesa lonke ilizwe kwaze kwaba lihola lesificamunwemunye, <verse eid="LUK 23:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 23:45"/>ngoba ilanga lema ukukhanya. Ikhetheni lethempeli ladabuka kabili. <verse eid="LUK 23:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 23:46"/>UJesu wamemeza ngelizwi elikhulu wathi, <char style="wj">“Baba, ezandleni zakho nginikela umphefumulo wami.”</char> Esekutshilo lokhu waphefumula okokucina.<verse eid="LUK 23:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 23:47"/>Induna yekhulu isibonile okwenzakeleyo yadumisa uNkulunkulu yathi, “Ngeqiniso lo ubeyindoda elungileyo.” <verse eid="LUK 23:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 23:48"/>Kwathi bonke abantu ababebuthene ukuzabona isiga lesi sebebonile okwakwenzakele, bababuhlungu, babalosizi, babuyela emizini yabo. <verse eid="LUK 23:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 23:49"/>Kodwa bonke ababemazi, kanye labesifazane abamlandela besuka laye eGalile, bema bucwala babukela okwakusenzakala.<verse eid="LUK 23:49"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukungcwatshwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 23:50"/>Kwakukhona indoda eyayithiwa nguJosefa, elilunga loMphakathi, eyindoda elungileyo njalo eqondileyo, <verse eid="LUK 23:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 23:51"/>owayengakuvumanga lokho abakuqumayo labakwenzayo. Yena wayevela edolobheni lakoJuda okwakuthiwa yi-Arimathiya, njalo wayelindele umbuso kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="LUK 23:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 23:52"/>Waya kuPhilathu wayacela isidumbu sikaJesu. <verse eid="LUK 23:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="LUK 23:53"/>Wasesethula wasigoqela ngelembu lelineni, wasibeka ethuneni elaligujwe edwaleni lingakaze lilale muntu. <verse eid="LUK 23:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="LUK 23:54"/>Kwakulusuku lokuLungiselela, iSabatha selizaqalisa.<verse eid="LUK 23:54"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="LUK 23:55"/>Abesifazane ababebuye loJesu esuka eGalile bamlandela uJosefa balibona ithuna lokuthi isidumbu sakhe salaliswa njani kulo. <verse eid="LUK 23:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="LUK 23:56"/>Basebebuyela ekhaya bayalungisa amagcobo lamakha. Kodwa baphumula ngeSabatha bethobela umlayo.<verse eid="LUK 23:56"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="LUK 24"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuvuka KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="LUK 24:1"/>Ngosuku lokuqala lweviki ekuseni kakhulu abesifazane bathatha amakha ababewalungisile baya ethuneni. <verse eid="LUK 24:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="LUK 24:2"/>Bafumana ilitshe ligiqiwe, lasuswa ethuneni, <verse eid="LUK 24:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="LUK 24:3"/>kodwa bathi bengena kabaze basithola isidumbu seNkosi uJesu. <verse eid="LUK 24:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="LUK 24:4"/>Bathi belokhu besathithibele ngakho, masinyane kwema eduze labo amadoda amabili egqoke izigqoko ezazikhazimula njengombane. <verse eid="LUK 24:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="LUK 24:5"/>Bethuka abesifazane bathi mbo phansi ngobuso, kodwa amadoda lawo athi kubo, “Lidingelani ophilayo kwabafileyo na? <verse eid="LUK 24:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="LUK 24:6"/>Kakho lapha; usevukile! Khumbulani ukuthi walitshelani eseselani eGalile: <verse eid="LUK 24:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="LUK 24:7"/><char style="wj">‘INdodana yoMuntu kumele inikelwe ezandleni zezoni, ibethelwe esiphambanweni kuthi ngosuku lwesithathu ivuswe njalo.’</char> ” <verse eid="LUK 24:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="LUK 24:8"/>Basebewakhumbula amazwi akhe.<verse eid="LUK 24:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="LUK 24:9"/>Kwathi sebebuyile bevela ethuneni, zonke lezizinto bazibikela abalitshumi lanye labanye bonke. <verse eid="LUK 24:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="LUK 24:10"/>KwakunguMariya Magadalini, loJowana, loMariya unina kaJakhobe labanye ababelabo abatshela abapostoli ngalokhu. <verse eid="LUK 24:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="LUK 24:11"/>Kodwa kababakholwanga abesifazane laba, ngoba amazwi abo ayengathi yikuwumana kubo. <verse eid="LUK 24:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="LUK 24:12"/>Kodwa uPhethro wasukuma wagijimela ethuneni. Walunguza wabona amaqhele elineni ethe qekele wodwa, wasebuyela emangele ukuthi kambe kwakwenzakaleni.<verse eid="LUK 24:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Endleleni Eya E-Emawusi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="LUK 24:13"/>Kwathi ngalelolanga ababili babo babehamba besiya emzini owawuthiwa yi-Emawusi, ongaba ngamakhilomitha alitshumi lanye usuka eJerusalema. <verse eid="LUK 24:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="LUK 24:14"/>Babekhulumisana ngakho konke okwakwenzakele. <verse eid="LUK 24:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="LUK 24:15"/>Bathi belokhu bekhuluma bebonisana ngazo lezizinto, uJesu yena ngokwakhe wabaxhuma wasehambisana labo; <verse eid="LUK 24:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="LUK 24:16"/>kodwa abaze bamnanzelela ukuthi nguye.<verse eid="LUK 24:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="LUK 24:17"/>Wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Likhuluma ngani kanti lilokhu liphakathi kohambo lwenu?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 24:17">Bema mpo, ubuso babo bubunile. <verse eid="LUK 24:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="LUK 24:18"/>Omunye wabo owayethiwa nguKlophasi wambuza wathi, “Kanti wena uyisihambi yini eJerusalema ukhanya ungazazi izinto ezenzakele kuzolezi insuku?”<verse eid="LUK 24:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="LUK 24:19"/>Wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Yizinto bani na?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="LUK 24:19">Baphendula bathi, “Mayelana ngoJesu waseNazaretha. Wayengumphrofethi; elomfutho ngokukhuluma langezenzo phambi kukaNkulunkulu lasebantwini bonke. <verse eid="LUK 24:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="LUK 24:20"/>Abaphristi abakhulu lababusi bethu bamnikela ukuba agwetshelwe ukufa, basebembethela; <verse eid="LUK 24:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="LUK 24:21"/>kodwa thina sasithembe ukuthi nguye owayezahlenga u-Israyeli. Futhi okunye yikuthi sekulusuku lwesithathu kulokhu kwenzakala konke lokhu. <verse eid="LUK 24:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="LUK 24:22"/>Phezu kwalokhu, abanye besifazane bethu basimangalisile. Bahambe ethuneni ekuseni kakhulu lamuhla, <verse eid="LUK 24:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="LUK 24:23"/>kodwa kabasifumananga isidumbu sakhe. Babuyile bazasitshela ukuthi babone umbono wezingilosi ezithe uyaphila. <verse eid="LUK 24:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="LUK 24:24"/>Kwasekusithi abanye babakhula bethu baya ethuneni bathola kunjengokuba abesifazane betshilo, kodwa yena kabamtholanga.”<verse eid="LUK 24:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="LUK 24:25"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Uthi liyizithutha ezinjani, njalo lilezinhliziyo ezithundubeleyo ekukholweni konke lokho okwakhulunywa ngabaphrofethi!</char> <verse eid="LUK 24:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="LUK 24:26"/><char style="wj">UKhristu wayengamelanga ahlupheke yini zonke lezi izinto andubana angene ebukhosini bakhe na?”</char> <verse eid="LUK 24:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="LUK 24:27"/>Wasesukela kuMosi kanye labaPhrofethi bonke wabachazela okwatshiwo emibhalweni mayelana laye.<verse eid="LUK 24:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="LUK 24:28"/>Bathi sebebanga emzini lowo ababesiya kuwo uJesu wenza ingathi wayesedlula. <verse eid="LUK 24:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="LUK 24:29"/>Kodwa bamncenga kakhulu bathi, “Hlala lathi ngoba sekusihlwa; usuku luphose selwedlule.” Wasengena ukuthi ayehlala labo.<verse eid="LUK 24:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="LUK 24:30"/>Wathi esehlezi labo etafuleni wathatha isinkwa wabonga, wasesihlephuna wasebaqhubela. <verse eid="LUK 24:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="LUK 24:31"/>Kwathi dlwe emehlweni abo, bamazi, yena wasenyamalala kubo. <verse eid="LUK 24:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="LUK 24:32"/>Babuzana bathi, “Konje inhliziyo zethu bezingatshiseki yini lapho abe ekhuluma lathi endleleni esivulela imibhalo na?”<verse eid="LUK 24:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="LUK 24:33"/>Bahle bathi lothu masinyane babuyela eJerusalema. Khonale bathola abalitshumi lanye kanye lalabo ababelabo bebuthene ndawonye <verse eid="LUK 24:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="LUK 24:34"/>besithi, “Kuliqiniso! INkosi isivukile kwabafileyo yabonakala kuSimoni.” <verse eid="LUK 24:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="LUK 24:35"/>Kwathi labo ababili balandisa ngalokho okwakwenzakele endleleni, lokuthi uJesu bamnanzelela njani lapho aze ahlephune isinkwa.<verse eid="LUK 24:35"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ubonakala KubaFundi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="LUK 24:36"/>Bathi belokhu besakhuluma ngakho lokhu, uJesu yena ngokwakhe wema phakathi kwabo wathi, <char style="wj">“Ukuthula kakube kini.”</char><verse eid="LUK 24:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="LUK 24:37"/>Bethuka besaba, bekhumbula ukuthi babebona ithonga <verse eid="LUK 24:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="LUK 24:38"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kungani lihluphekile, njalo kungani kulokuthandabuza ezingqondweni zenu?</char> <verse eid="LUK 24:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="LUK 24:39"/><char style="wj">Khangelani izandla zami lezinyawo zami. Yimi mina ngokwami! Ngithintani libone; ithonga kalilanyama lamathambo njengoba libona ukuthi mina ngilakho.”</char><verse eid="LUK 24:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="LUK 24:40"/>Esetshilo lokhu wabatshengisa izandla lezinyawo zakhe. <verse eid="LUK 24:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="LUK 24:41"/>Kwathi belokhu bengakholwa ngenxa yokuthaba lokumangala wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lilakho okokudla lapha na?”</char> <verse eid="LUK 24:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="LUK 24:42"/>Bamupha iqatha lenhlanzi exatshiweyo, <verse eid="LUK 24:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="LUK 24:43"/>wayithatha wayidla phambi kwabo.<verse eid="LUK 24:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="LUK 24:44"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lokhu yikho engalitshela khona ngiseselani ukuthi: Konke kumele kugcwaliseke okwalotshwa ngami eMthethweni kaMosi labaPhrofethi lamaHubo.”</char><verse eid="LUK 24:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="LUK 24:45"/>Wasebavula ingqondo zabo ukuze bakwazi ukuzwisisa imibhalo. <verse eid="LUK 24:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="LUK 24:46"/>Wabatshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Nanku okulotshiweyo: UKhristu uzahlupheka aphinde avuke kwabafileyo ngosuku lwesithathu,</char> <verse eid="LUK 24:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="LUK 24:47"/><char style="wj">njalo ukuphenduka lokuthethelelwa kwezono kuzatshunyayelwa ebizweni lakhe ezizweni zonke, kuqala eJerusalema.</char> <verse eid="LUK 24:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="LUK 24:48"/><char style="wj">Lingofakazi balezizinto.</char> <verse eid="LUK 24:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="LUK 24:49"/><char style="wj">Ngizalithumezela lokho uBaba akuthembisileyo; kodwa libohlala edolobheni lize liphiwe amandla avela phezulu.”</char><verse eid="LUK 24:49"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwenyukela Ezulwini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="LUK 24:50"/>Kwathi esebakhokhele waya labo eduze leBhethani waphakamisa izandla zakhe wababusisa. <verse eid="LUK 24:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="LUK 24:51"/>Uthe elokhu esababusisa, wabatshiya, wenyukiselwa ezulwini. <verse eid="LUK 24:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="LUK 24:52"/>Basebemkhonza, babuyela eJerusalema bethokoza kakhulu. <verse eid="LUK 24:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="LUK 24:53"/>Bahlala kokuphela ethempelini bedumisa uNkulunkulu.<verse eid="LUK 24:53"/></para>
  <chapter eid="LUK 24"/>
</usx>
